The show gives us a comical look at Sweden through the eyes of an American, but at the same time allows us to laugh at this fish out of water trying to function in a new, strange world.

title: West of the Badlands
description: An Eastern doctor is on the run from authorities in New York. Out west he comes to the aid of friends besieged by an outlaw gang known as the border legion. In the end, he is cleared of any wrong-doing back east.

title: Wildfire
description: Fanning has his men rustle horses and then blame it on a wild horse named Wildfire. Happy and Alkali arrive and immediately get into trouble with Fanning and his men.

title: A Father's Legacy
description: An inspirational story of faith, family and redemption. After years of searching for his father, a young man, on the run from the law, finds his way into the life of a secluded old man in the woods. As the days go by and secrets about their past are revealed, they realize they may not have been looking for each other but they were brought together for a reason.

title: A Tiny Ripple of Hope
description: Charismatic activist Jahmal Cole works tirelessly to build a better Chicago for the teens in his neglected community, even if it comes at the cost of his home, his family, and his safety.

title: Below The Fold
description: Two reporters uncover a harrowing new detail in a cold case, which leads them on an obsessive hunt for the truth.

title: Distancing Socially
description: Composed of a series of comical vignettes that share a telecommunications application as a common thread, Distancing Socially focuses on loosely connected human interactions - from food delivery to family drama - taking place virtually across a world in lockdown.

title: First Target
description: The Secret Service attempts to prevent an elaborately plotted assassination attempt on the President.

title: James Gregory: Food is Not Fatal
description: James Gregory, a Georgian suffering from Vertigo, is on a mission to spread the good news of "real butter," Paul-bearing strength, hotter summers, and endangered chicken legs.

title: Jungle
description: A group of friends join a guide for a trek into the Bolivian jungle, searching for an Indian village. The men soon realize that the jungle is a difficult place to be.

title: Lost at Christmas
description: In this feel-good festive romance, two strangers come together to try and get home for Christmas.

title: Nizhalgal
description: Three unemployed friends, stricken by poverty find it hard to make ends meet. They refuse to take their parents' advice to take up basic jobs; instead they strive hard to pursue their dreams at any cost.

title: On the Borderline
description: A young couple embark on a cross-country journey, only to run into trouble at the Texas/Mexico border.

title: The Art of Murder
description: An abused wife (Joanna Pacula) turns to another man and becomes the victim of a blackmailer.

title: The Breed
description: Vampires have lived among us, in relative peace, for hundreds of years. However, one blood-thirsty member of the undead is out to change that. In hot pursuit is a young cop and his new partner, a noble vampire intent on righting the wrongs of his kin.

title: The Pizzagate Massacre
description: A dark social satire inspired by the real life conspiracy theory known as Pizzagate. An amateur journalist and a far-right militiaman team up to expose the ugly truth behind rumors involving sex cults, a pizza place and the lizard people.

title: The Snow Queen: Magic of the Ice Mirror
description: After their victory over the Snow Queen, Gerda and Orm have given the trolls freedom. But as Orm's inflated stories catch up to him, the snow mates will slide into another icy adventure to protect the world from eternal winter.

title: The Stairs
description: An 11-year-old boy finds a mysterious staircase in the woods and disappears while on a hunting trip with his grandfather. 20 years later, a group of friends set off into the very same woods. That evening they come face to face with the same set of stairs. Worlds collide as some lose their lives and others step up to become heroes.

title: The Travel Bug
description: From the Pacific paradises of New Caledonia and the Cook Islands, through the jungles of Papua New Guinea, across to Mauritius and into the rainforests of Sumatra in search of orangutans, this is an epic season full of adventure! Throw in some luxury, culture, history, and spectacular landscapes and you have something for everybody.

title: Under the Tree
description: After moving back home, a man gets sucked into a dispute between his parents and their neighbors over an old and beautiful tree. What starts as a typical spat unexpectedly and violently reaches a boiling point, soon spiraling out of control.

title: Wind
description: In more than 140 years of competition, the United States has lost the America's Cup only once. WINDis the dramatic, fictional story of an upstart group of American challengers whose drive to win back sailing's top prize plunges them into a world where money, power, love and ambition are inextricably intertwined.

title: Avatara Purusha
description: Dharka and Brahma Jois Fight Over the Trishanku Mani in a battle of mantras and soon after Brahma Jois turns up dead. Prior to his Death in order to protect his family he deployed the Ashta Digbandhana and hides the Trishanku Mani in his house. Will Dharka find it?

title: Bedrooms & Hallways
description: Keith runs a male bonding group, which was meant to be macho fun, but acts as therapist as dreaded-unmanly emotional and even relational problems prove unavoidable. Openly gay Leo is delighted to find hunky, straight Brendan is a closet-bi and becomes his lover. Things risk ending ugly as it turns out Brendan's girlfriend is Leo's school ex and still able to seduce him.

title: Big Mommas: Like Father, Like Son (Extended Cut)
description: After witnessing a murder, FBI agent Malcolm Turner (Lawrence) and his stepson (Brandon T. Jackson) go deep undercover at an all-girl performing arts school.

title: Boonie Bears: The Wild Life
description: Vick and Bramble enter a competition at a new amusement park called Wild Life where visitors are able to transform into a variety of animals.

title: Casting By
description: "Casting By" places the spotlight on one of filmmaking's unsung heroes - casting director Marion Dougherty.

title: Christmas Break-In
description: Christmas Break-In is the story of Izzy, a spunky nine year-old who gets left at school on the last day before Christmas break. While her parents brave a blizzard to reach her, three bumbling crooks break into the school to hide out until the heat dies down. But when they take the school janitor hostage, Izzy will have to find a way to save him and teach the crooks a lesson.

title: Dead Ant
description: When the '80s one-hit-wonder glam-metal band Sonic Grave embarks on a road trip to Coachella in hopes of a comeback, their peyote trip pit stop in Joshua Tree incites a grisly attack, and they must "rock" themselves out of harm's way.

title: Diamond Trail
description: Reporter goes undercover.

title: Dickie Roberts: Former Child Star
description: Dickie Roberts is a 35-year old former child star. Now an out-of-work actor, Dickie is desperate to audition for a great role that could revitalize his career, but the part requires him to play a 'normal' guy. Problem is, Dickie is anything but normal.

title: Down the Wyoming Trail
description: Tex arrives on the Parker ranch on Christmas eve and is given the job of being Santa Claus. Also dressed as Santa Claus, Blackie robs Parker and kills a man.

title: Everyday Miracles
description: A reluctant faith healer tries to escape his troubles by working as a ranch hand for a widower and his daughter. Over time, he becomes a part of their family but soon his dreams are threatened when his past catches up with him.

title: Frontier Justice
description: Cattlemen and sheepmen are feuding over water-and-grazing rights. Between handing out trick matches and exploding cigars and being jailed on a frame-up, someone manages to expose the true culprits behind all the local problems.

title: Hakaider: The Extended Director's Cut (Original Japanese Version)
description: The darkest force of destruction is now the only hope for salvation! In the far future, peace and violence walk hand as a robot once pent on destruction becomes humanity's only hope for survival.

title: In Old Caliente
description: Rogers works for a Spanish aristocrat, who is robbed by his own son. When the son places the blame on incoming Americans, Rogers is intent on setting the record straight.

title: Kaalamellam Kaathiruppen
description: Rich boy Kannan hears Manimekalai sing in a temple and falls in love with her. But when all his attempts to befriend her only earn her wrath, he has to find a new way to impress her.

title: Lonely Boys
description: Broke and brokenhearted, best friends Jules and Saul stagger through a weekend desperately trying to hold onto their sanity – and each other.

title: Marshal of Cedar Rock
description: Rocky Lane takes on Henry Mason, a crooked railroad agent, who is swindling local landowners out of their property.

title: Mini Witch
description: A young and mischievous witch named Fuchsia enrolls in witch school to learn magic. Against her father's warning, Fuchsia befriends a human boy named Tommy and learns about his uncle's plans to destroy her school. It is up to Fuchsia and her new magical powers to save her town!

title: Peck's Bad Boy
description: Young boy Bill Peck adores his father and tries to be good, but the arrival of Bill's cousin Horace upsets Bill's plans. Horace's brattish ways result in Bill rather than Horace getting in trouble.

title: Rescue Dawn
description: During the height of the Vietnam war, American pilot Dieter Dengler (Christian Bale) is shot down and taken prisoner by the Vietcong. What followed was one of the most remarkable and harrowing experiences of the entire war. Steve Zahn co-stars.

title: Romola
description: In Renaissance Florence, Tito, a no-good young man pretending to be a scholar, wins the admiration of a blind man who has long looked for someone to finish his scholarly work.

title: Sherlock Holmes: Terror By Night
description: When the fabled Star of Rhodesia diamond is stolen on a London to Edinburgh train and the son of its owner is murdered, Sherlock Holmes must discover which of his suspicious fellow passengers is responsible.

title: Suddenly
description: There is to be an attempt on the life of the President as he passes through a small town.

title: The Argument
description: When a couple has an argument at a party, and neither will admit to being wrong, they decide to recreate the evening again and again in order to determine who was right. But this leads to even more confusion, and soon everyone is arguing.

title: The Red House (1947)
description: Pete and Ellen have reared Meg as their own since she was a baby. Now a teen, Meg convinces her friend Nath to come help with chores on the farm, since Pete has difficulty with his wooden leg.

title: The Sound of Scars
description: The story of three lifelong friends who overcame domestic violence, substance abuse, and depression to form Life of Agony, one of the most influential bands in its genre, led by the very first openly transgender singer.

title: The Wackiest Wagon Train in the West
description: Wagon master Callahan, wealthy married couple Carter and Daphne Brookhaven, dance hall girl Lulu McQueen, sweet young school teacher Betsy, and handsome engineer Andy are part of an 1880's wagon train headed to California. Unfortunately, thanks to their daffy guide Dusty, they are separated from the rest of the wagons, and the diverse bunch must take the westward journey on their own.

title: Thunaivan
description: Velayutham, a fervent devotee of Lord Murugan, marries Marahatham, a non-believer, and attempts to induce religious beliefs in her to help their child.

title: Thunder Trail
description: A wagon train is robbed by a gang of bandits who kill everyone but a pair of young brothers. Years later, the brothers join force to bring the bandits' leader to justice.

title: Todo por Lucy
description: Lucy and Ricky are the perfect imperfect couple. She is creative, professional but always getting in trouble. Ricky is squared mind engineer who dreams of becoming a stand-up comedian. Ricky wants to get married. Lucy is not ready. As a compromise they move in together. Their two worlds clashing will be a test that will prove that where there is love there will always be laughter.

title: Wagon Trail
description: The son of Sheriff Clay Hartley, of the frontier town Elder, has gotten into bad company and hangs out with an outlaw gang in which, Collins, owner of the Golden Rule Saloon, is the secret ...

title: Zebraman
description: A down-and-out school teacher receives the calling to become the real life personification of the television superhero, Zebraman.

title: As It Happened: Guadalcanal
description: US Marines strike back on their first attack of the Pacific War. In horrific conditions US Marines fight a six month campaign of attrition against the seemingly invisible Japanese.

title: As It Happened: Tarawa
description: Tarawa was the most strongly defended island in the Pacific which the Japanese boasted that a million Americans couldn’t take the island in one hundred years. On Tarawa the Marines faced their sternest test yet.

title: Dick Tracy Meets Gruesome
description: A crime thriller based on a comic strip by Chester Gould, in which Dick Tracy battles "The Claw".

title: Maze
description: Based on the incredible true story of the 1983 mass break-out of 38 IRA prisoners from the HMP Maze high security prison, one prisoner engineers the largest European prison escape since World War II.

title: Monarch
description: An injured King, Henry VIII, is forced to take refuge at a manor house. He must confront his mortality and the ghosts of his past. An intimate portrait of a monarch before this death. The debut feature for double BAFTA-nominated writer and director John Walsh makes ingenious use of a single location and a setting of one stormy night. Rated 4 stars by BBC Radio Times.

title: Nazis Strike
description: The official World War II US government account of Nazi international aggression leading up to the British and French declarations of war.

title: Sunset Serenade
description: Bad guys plot to trick a newly arrived Eastern girl out of a ranch which belongs to her infant ward. Roy, of course, saves the ranch for the girl.

title: Tank Girl
description: In 2022, Earth is struck by a comet, leading to a massive drought. Eleven years later a majority of the water left is kept in a reserve. Tank Girl (Lori Petty) is a member of a resistance group who steals whatever they want, by any means necessary. Being the enemies of the water reserve, their hideout is attacked and Tank Girl's boyfriend is killed and younger friend Sam is captured!

title: Team Hot Wheels The Origin Of Awesome
description: Meet Gage, Wyatt, Brandon and Rhett. Kids born to ride. Separate, they are seriously skilled racers, but together they become Team Hot Wheels! So ride along, as the boys discover their true inner racer, battle monster mayhem, confront Mutant Machines, navigate chaotic orange track, learn to work together and race to save their town! Don't settle for just awesome...watch The Origin of Awesome!

title: The Glorias
description: Based on Gloria Steinem's autobiographical book, "My Life on the Road," THE GLORIAS weaves a compelling, nontraditional tapestry of one of the most inspirational and legendary figures in modern history.

title: The Reef 2
description: Trained in the skills of sea power, Pi the fish can fight a shark, sink a squid or batter any random predator that ever threatens his friends and neighbors on the reef. Unfortunately, being the only hero in town can take its toll, especially when a group of sharks declares that the end of the reef is soon at hand.

title: The Twilight Saga: Breaking Dawn Part 1 Extended Edition
description: Experience THE TWILIGHT SAGA: BREAKING DAWN - PART 1 like never before with the extended edition, featuring over eight minutes of new and extended scenes added by Director Bill Condon.

title: The Who - Sensation The Story Of Tommy
description: This fascinating film, made with the total co-operation of the band, tells how The Who struggled to create the first Rock Opera, Tommy, and how its success changed their lives.

title: Till The Clouds Roll By
description: An all-star cast fills out this energetic biopic of Broadway pioneer Jerome Kern (Robert Walker)

title: Tyler Perry's Meet the Browns - The Play
description: This play brings together a family after hearing the news of a passed away family member. Coming together for the funeral will be harder than it sounds. Through all the drama and commotion they find love and know that there's nothing like family.

title: Words On Bathroom Walls
description: Diagnosed with a mental illness, a witty, introspective teen falls in love with a brilliant classmate who inspires him to open his heart and not be defined by his condition.

title: Bad Comments
description: The movie follows the life of Frank Orji with a vibrant acting career but who get his reputation tarnished following the release of an edited video online. This leads to excessive cyberbullying by online trolls. With the help of a hacker, his bodyguard and his personal assistant is able to track down these trolls and give them a tastes of their own medicine

title: Paranormal Activity: The Marked Ones
description: 17-year-old Jesse has been hearing terrifying sounds coming from his neighbor's apartment, but when he turns on his camera and sets out to uncover the source, he encounters an evil that won't rest until it's claimed his soul.

title: Stagecoach to Denver
description: Lambert has the stagecoach wrecked killing the Commissioner so his phony replacement can alter Coonskin's land survey. When Red Ryder exposes the survey hoax, Lambert has his stooge Sheriff put Red in jail.

title: The Wolf Of Wall Street
description: Leonardo DiCaprio delivers "the best performance of his career" as a young stockbroker hungry for a life of non-stop thrills, where corruption was king and more was never enough.

title: American Empire
description: Two men join forces to build a cattle empire, and battle rustlers, bad weather and each other.

title: County Fair, The
description: Aunt Abigail and her adopted daughter Sally are threatened with the loss of their home through foreclosure of a mortgage held by Solon Hammerhead.

title: East Side Kids
description: East Side Kids help a pal acused of murder.

title: Fire Alarm
description: Brown is a confident young firefighter. He and his buddy become interested in two girls, after saving their cat. He then fights a fire in the apartment building next door to his new girlfriend.

title: Flying Blind
description: A spy steals a secret military device, then hijacks an airliner to get away. The airliner crashes in the wilderness & the survivors are threatened by a raging forest fire.

title: Force of Nature
description: In this thunderous action-thriller, Mel Gibson, Emile Hirsch, and Kate Bosworth join forces to battle a deadly gang of thieves as a brutal hurricane engulfs the city.

title: Hard Luck
description: Two converging story lines involving corrupt cops ripping off drug dealers and serial killers are followed as former drug dealer Lucky, trying to go straight after doing a prison stint, gets entangled within by a series of bad breaks.

title: Heading for Heaven
description: Stuart Erwin plays a small-town real estate agent who owns much property which, for several generations, has failed to sell even while the town has grown.

title: Journey to Self
description: Journey to Self' is an intense story of friendship, sacrifice, empowerment and self-respect. Four childhood friends, Regina, Nse, Rume and Alex, receive news that another long time friend of theirs, Uche, has died.

title: Kodi Parakuthu
description: A mafia leader tries to kill policeman Sivagiri, who took down his illegal businesses, with the help of a lookalike. Later, Sivagiri discovers that the leader is responsible for his father's death.

title: Love, Sex, Religion
description: When high school sweethearts, Ace and Chizzy decided to become religious (devout Christians) and avoid sex, the future they were once certain off is threatened by their ability to remain celibate

title: Mr. Jones
description: 1933. An ambitious young journalist, Gareth Jones, travels to Moscow to uncover the truth behind Stalin's Soviet propaganda that pushes their "utopia" to the Western world. When he gets a tip that could expose an international conspiracy, Jones' life and the lives of his informants are at stake. Based on a true story that would later inspire George Orwell's seminal book Animal Farm.

title: Outlaw Express
description: Bradley and sidekick Sharpe are sent west to investigate the murders of pony express riders who are being killed to prevent the Spanish Land Grant papers going to Washington for registration.

title: Phantom in the House
description: A man is blamed for a murder that was actually committed by his wife.

title: Postal Inspector
description: Postal inspectors track down money stolen from a railroad car.

title: Raiders of the Border
description: Working undercover, Marshals Nevada and Sandy are looking for jewel smugglers along the border.

title: Rogue of the Range
description: Doran and the Sheriff have a scheme to bring in an outlaw gang. Doran is sent to prison so he and the gang leader Mitchell can break out. This gets him into the gang but he is in trouble when his secret is revealed.

title: Shadow Man
description: An intelligence operative discovers that no one is what they seem in the shadowy world of espionage.

title: Soledad
description: A lonely limousine driver named Victor lives an isolated existence until one evening he defends a client from being sexually assaulted by her prom date. A simple act of compassion sets off a series of tumultuous events leading to a road trip through the city of Angels, forcing Victor to confront a past he's long forgotten, a reminder that it only takes one night to change a life forever.

title: Souls of Sin
description: Unsuccessful gambler 'Dollar Bill' Burton lives in a crummy New York basement room with old friend Bob and a new roommate, friendly blues singer 'Alabama' Lee. But, tired of being broke, Dollar Bill gets more steady employment.

title: Tarzan and the Green Goddess
description: At his English manor, Lord Greystoke - aka Tarzan - recounts his recent adventures in Guatemala.

title: Texas Terror
description: Sheriff John Higgins quits and goes into prospecting after he thinks he has killed his best friend in shooting it out with robbers. He encounters his dead buddy's sister and helps her run her ranch.

title: The Dancing Pirate
description: The story of a Boston dance teacher who gets shanghaied by buccaneers who might make his next steps be off the plank!

title: The Gay Ranchero (1948)
description: Manzanita Springs ia a combination small airline and spa and Vance Brados wants it. He pays their mechanic to have the planes run out of fuel so his men can rob the gold shipments and kill the pilots.

title: The Great Fortune
description: Mirco Kuball: an ultra-wealthy, flamboyant, sophisticated and outspoken man who just happens to have Down's syndrome. This touching film explores an unexpected life. But, beneath the opulent showman, lies a man like any other, who realises that beyond shelter, food, and companionship, nothing else counts.

title: The Hairy Ape
description: Hank Smith, a brutish stoker on board a freighter, is appalled when Mildred Douglas, a society girl forced by circumstance to travel as a passenger, visits the stokehold and recoils at the filthy, sweating Hank.

title: The Jesus Trip
description: When the police discover that their motorcycles are concealing heroin, Waco (Robert Porter) and his motorcycle gang hides out in a desert convent.

title: The Trail Beyond
description: Rod Drew hunts for a missing girl and finds himself in a fight over a goldmine as well.

title: Touch of Pink
description: A gay Canadian living in London has his perfectly crafted life upset when his devoutly Muslim mother comes to visit.

title: Unacknowledged: An  Expose of the World's Greatest Secret
description: Dr. Steven Greer present brand new, top secret evidence supporting Extraterrestrial contact including witness testimony, classified documents, and UFO footage while also exploring the consequences of ruthlessly enforcing such secrecy.

title: Unnai Kodu Ennai Tharuven
description: A boy who is abandoned by his mother is raised by an army officer. He turns out to be a model patriot and joins the army, but his loyalties come under the scanner when he meets a girl and falls in love with her.

title: Voyage to the Prehistoric Planet
description: In 2020, after the colonization of the moon, the spaceships Vega, Sirius and Capella are launched from Lunar Station 7, set to explore Venus under the command of Professor Hartman, but an asteroid collides and explodes Capella.

title: Water Rustlers
description: Shirley Martin finds that Weylan has diverted the water from the valley and her cattle are dying. First she and her foreman Bob Lawson go to court. This fails when Weylan's men keep the ranchers from testifying.

title: Where the Truth Lies
description: Karen O'Connor, a young journalist known for her celebrity profiles, is consumed with discovering the truth behind a long-buried incident that affected the lives and careers of showbiz team Vince Collins and Lanny Morris.

In a small Pennsylvania town, a twenty-year-old woman comes of age and deals with the trials and tribulations of sex, drugs and adulthood. When she has a pregnancy scare, she realizes it's time to make some serious lifestyle adjustments.

title: 10 Tokyo Warriors: The Final Battle
description: Long ago, the land was in a state of chaos as the feudal lords waged territorial wars. In the midst of the bloodshed, a ferocious warrior, known as the Demon King, appeared and conquered all. It is now 400 years later.

title: Almost Had You
description: Two young lovers come from different economic classes leading to the parents of the man opposing the relationship. The man follows his heart and insists on going further with the lady. How is this going to end?

title: An American in Texas
description: An angry, crackling and defiantly disordered underclass of punk-rock kids, see their band Surgeon General's Warning (SGW) as their ticket out of small town Texas, as 1990 comes to a close.

title: Antwone Fisher
description: HD. Denzel Washington directed this true story of a Navy man who learns to confront his anger with the help of a psychiatrist.

title: Are They Here? UFOs Caught on Camera
description: Award winning Fox Television Special, which includes never before seen UFO footage. This collection of clips and videos shot all over the world shed light on the long debated presence of aliens on planet earth.

title: Arkansas
description: Kyle (Liam Hemsworth) and Swin (Clark Duke) live by the orders of an Arkansas-based drug kingpin named Frog (Vince Vaughn). When a series of mistakes sets them on a collision course with Frog, Kyle and Swin must eliminate Frog… or die trying.

title: Assignment Berlin
description: A California detective becomes the target of revenge when she is held responsible for the murder of the head of the Korean Mafia.

title: Big Mommas: Like Father, Like Son
description: HD. 'Big Momma' is dragged out of mothballs when FBI man Martin Lawrence must go undercover – in a girls school.

title: Braking For Whales
description: A dysfunctional brother and sister are forced to come to terms with each other and themselves over their recently deceased mother's final wish. Starring Tom Felton, Tammin Sursok, Wendi Mclendon-Covey, David Koechner, and Austin Swift.

title: California Split
description: When a casual gambler befriends a professional one, he begins to mirror his life, sending both deeper into the sleazy gambling world where the stakes keep getting bigger.

title: Capone
description: A ruthless businessman and bootlegger who ruled Chicago with an iron fist, Al "Fonzo" Capone (Tom Hardy) was the most infamous and feared gangster of American lore. At the age of 47, following nearly a decade of imprisonment, dementia rots Capone's mind and his past becomes present as harrowing memories of his violent and brutal origins melt into his waking life.

title: Captain Magal
description: Kavitha and Kalyan, a married couple, go to a hill station on a vacation. But their peace is shattered when strange things begin happening at the guest house they are staying in.

title: Chain
description: A man gets entangled in an extramarital affair with a mentally unstable woman and is given an ultimatum to get rid of his wife or face dire consequences.

title: Christmas in New York, A
description: In the vein of Love Actually, the story follows six different couples in a posh Manhattan hotel over the course of one night just before Christmas.

title: Cowboy
description: An idealistic tenderfoot Chicago hotel clerk is taken on a cattle-drive to Mexico by famous trail boss Tom Reece but discovers that cowboy life isn't what he expected.

title: CRSHD
description: On the last night of her college freshman year, Izzy tries to lose her virginity with the help of her two best friends – but their only hope is getting into an exclusive, invite-only "Crush Party."

title: Depth Charge
description: Commander Krieg, a seasoned Naval officer aboard the nuclear submarine USS Montana, is making a shocking bid for world peace. With the help of mercenaries, he engineers to take over the sub and its weapons in order to hold the world hostage.

title: Devil Within Her
description: A promiscuous showgirl's firstborn is cursed by a sinister dwarf. After a series of deaths she realizes that her son is possessed by the devil.

title: Double Eagle Ranch
description: Marc, a deadbeat writer, manipulates his recent ex-girlfriend, Lindsay, into accompanying him to spread his late grandmother's ashes at her mountain property. Marc's attempt to win her back goes awry when they discover the cabin has accidentally been double-booked by a happier couple.

title: Down 2 Come Up
description: Tyrone (Pastor Troy), is released from prison early and returns to his hood. While his girl, Anetra (Malan Boykin) stayed true, her brush with the King of Bankhead (Shawty Lo) threatens the couple's chance at rebuilding their lives.

title: Dr. Dolittle (1998)
description: HD. Animal logic makes a mess out of nutty pet doctor Eddie Murphy in this riotous updating of the classic 1967 family musical.

title: Eden Log
description: A man wakes up deep inside a cave. Suffering amnesia, he has no recollection of how he came to be here or of what happened to the man whose body he finds beside him. Tailed by a mysterious creature, he must continue through this strange and fantastic world.

title: Give Me Liberty
description: Medical transport driver Vic is late, but it's not his fault. Roads are closed for a protest, and no one else can shuttle his Russian grandfather and émigré friends to a funeral. The new route uproots his scheduled clients, particularly Tracy, a vibrant young woman with ALS. Their collective ride becomes a hilarious, compassionate, and intersectional portrait of American dreams.

title: Hila
description: A multimillionaire Dying grandma in search of her successor turned to total strangers for help pitching her grandchildren against themselves.

title: Hollow Scream
description: A narcissistic playboy entrepreneur with a dark past plays a new virtual reality game where he gets to be a serial killer. His genius brother discovers the dangerous truth behind the game and its creators.

title: Home for Harvest
description: A travel writer is surprised to be sent back to the hometown she left, heartbroken, years before. She meets a new man, until her ex shows back up and causes trouble. TV-PG

title: How to Eat Your Watermelon in White Company (and Enjoy It)
description: From Air Force pilot to civil rights activist to French novelist to Wall Street trader, this documentary charts the incredible journey of a man best known for Sweet Sweetback's Baadasssss Song – the controversial, self-produced film that sparked the Blaxploitation era – and illuminates an artist whose groundbreaking impact on film, politics and pop culture remains as relevant as ever.

title: I Wrote This For You
description: The edges of reality are blurred when a young man struggles to overcome a broken relationship.

title: In Order of Disappearance [English Subtitled]
description: Nils (Stellan Skarsgård), uncovers his son’s murderer, he begins to unravel. He embarks on a quest for revenge. Reminiscent of Tarantino and The Coen Brothers, Nils finds himself in a different world in order to bring his son’s murderers to justice.

title: Introducing the Kujus
description: The Kuju siblings are tricked by their youngest sister into visiting their village for a re-membrance of their late mother five years after her death. The loss of their matriarch left a gaping hole in the family due to her role as a unifying factor. The tension between the sib-lings was underestimated as they soon found out.

title: Jayeshbhai Jordaar
description: A non-confrontational Jayesh (Ranveer Singh) decides to defy his patriarchal family and flee with his pregnant wife Mudra (Shalini Pandey) to save their unborn daughter from feticide. A screwball, hilarious chase begins as Jayesh's father (Boman Irani) assembles all his might to nab them. Will this unlikely hero manage to create a safe and equal haven for his daughter?

title: Jo & Jo
description: If you think your family is messed up, wait till you meet the Palathara family! Baby Palathara is a happy go lucky homeo doctor who lives with his wife Lillikutty, daughter Jomol and younger son Jomon. In an interesting turn of events, a love letter finds its way to Palathara home and all hell breaks loos.

title: Man of Courage
description: John Wallace is a crusading district attorney. The mob boss George Dickson is his number one target. Dickson enjoys the protection of several crooked politicians.

title: March 17th
description: Two cousins go for an evening funtime that leads to both of them encountering an abuser who nearly rapes them. In an attempt to get away, they make a grevious mistake. How do they deny a murder that they are clearly responsible for.

title: Nadodi Thendral
description: Thangarasu, a goldsmith's son, and Poonkuruvi, a gypsy and poultry seller, fall in love during the era of British rule. However, Thangarasu soon attracts the affections of a young English lady.

title: Nandha
description: A court employee notices that influential people easily get away with all kinds of crimes while the poor bear the brunt. He takes the law into his hands to punish the culprits.

title: Nemesis
description: A car crash allows a prisoner to escape into the woods. While in pursuit of the fugitive, the recovery agent encounters the driver of the other vehicle and begins to suspect the stranger's involvement was not by chance.

title: No Time to Die
description: A mission to rescue a kidnapped scientist turns out to be far more treacherous than expected, leading Bond (Daniel Craig) onto the trail of a mysterious villain armed with dangerous new technology.

title: One Bad Turn
description: When a once loving and adorable wife decides to go a different route in what would be considered a perfect marriage.the consequences of her actions will leave behind a trail of lust,pain,betrayal and an emptiness beyond any imagination.

title: Poison Rose
description: This star-studded detective noir features John Travolta as a troubled private eye whose latest case forces him to confront dangerous men (Morgan Freeman), desirable women-and his own dark past.

title: Preacher
description: As our story inches closer to the finale, God's endgame for the universe begins to click into place. Trapped between heavenly prophecies, hellish prisons, and all-out nuclear war, Jesse, Tulip, and Cassidy make their bloody way to the Most High. Whether they can reach God in time – or whether all this carnage is part of His divine plan – will soon be revealed as Preacher barrels towards the end..

title: Puthiya Vaanam
description: Rajaratnam is adopted by DIG Pandidurai after his father, a police officer, is killed by a criminal, Govindan. Years later, he becomes a police officer himself and sets out to take revenge.

title: Red Dawn (2012)
description: A group of teenagers look to save their town from an invasion of North Korean soldiers.

title: Red Water
description: A group of oil workers being held hostage by a group of gangsters on a small oil rig are attacked by a freshwater bull shark.

title: Retaliation
description: Orlando Bloom stars in this taut thriller about a demolition worker seeking vengeance after he sees the man responsible for a traumatic childhood incident.

title: Revelation Trail
description: A frontier preacher's life is destroyed when a gruesome power consumes the land; he now must make the choice to give in to ruin, or find his purpose in the fight against the mysterious undead. Joined by the town lawman, the two men learn the extremes they're willing to go to in order to make it to the next day, as well as the depths people will go to when they truly believe in something.

title: Robin Hood of the Pecos
description: Carpetbagger Ballard, eager to confiscate valuable land in post-Civil War Texas by enforcing martial law and driving out the ranchers, tries to thwart Sheriff Corbin's efforts to rally the citizens.

title: Roll Red Roll
description: Go behind the headlines of notorious high school sexual assault to witness the social media-fueled "boys will be boys" culture that let it happen. With unprecedented access to police documents, exhibits and evidence, this documentary feature unflinchingly asks: "Why didn't anyone stop it?"

title: Saravana
description: Saravana falls in love with his best friend Krishna's sister, Sadhana. During the fight with rival thugs, he manages to save Sadhana, who watches her family perish before her eyes.

title: Terraces
description: Story of the various joys and crises of neighbors who share terraces in a high-rise apartment building.

title: The Escort
description: A professional escort falls in love with his client a lonely business woman who is entagled with her cheating ex Husband

title: The Final List
description: After getting engaged to the love of her life, Idara is in a dilemma as her father’s family refuses to support the marriage unless her fiancé, Imoh provides all the outrageous items listed for her traditional marriage rites; in this cultural satire about Nigerian cultural marriages.

title: The Legend of Swee' Pea
description: A "mystical understanding of the game" made Lloyd "Swee' Pea" Daniels a New York City basketball legend by the age of 16. Christened the "next Magic Johnson", his career effectively ended at age 21 after being shot 3 times in the chest after a tussle over $8 of cocaine. The Legend of Swee' Pea follows the twists and turns of fortune in the life of a basketball prodigy.

title: The Nanny Diaries
description: A college student (Scarlett Johansson) goes to work for an affluent but dysfunctional family.

title: The Nutty Professor II: The Klumps
description: Having done his best to keep Buddy buried in his subconscious, the portly Professor Klump (Eddie Murphy) is horrified to find him resurfacing in outbursts and threatening his marriage plans to colleague Denise Gains (Janet Jackson).

title: The World Is Not Enough
description: Bond takes position as bodyguard of British oil tycoon's daughter after a deadly mishap at MI6.

title: This Beautiful Fantastic
description: Set against the backdrop of a beautiful London garden, this contemporary fairy tale centers on the unlikely friendship between a reclusive young woman who dreams of writing children's books and a cranky widower. Facing eviction over her neglected garden, Bella (Jessica Brown Findlay) meets her grumpy, loveless, next-door neighbor (Tom Wilkinson), who happens to be an amazing horticulturalist.

title: Tombstone
description: Wyatt Earp and Doc Holliday team up at the O.K. Corral.

title: U-67
description: A crooked lawyer trying to cheat a young girl out of her inheritance tries to convince a sea captain to help him.

title: Uptown New York
description: Pat and Max are in love and share an intimate relationship. However, after Max receives his surgeon's diploma, his parents have arranged a marriage for him with a woman from a rich, good background.

title: Vetri Kodi Kattu
description: Sekhar and Muthuraman are duped by a conman who promises to give them visas to fly to Dubai. Realising that their families might get hurt, they decide to exchange their addresses.

title: Volcano
description: A family reunion goes awry when the housemaid is found dead and threats from an unknown killer puts all under house arrest. They will have to reveal each others dirty secrets or one of them dies every minute.

title: We Are Poets
description: The poignant tale of six remarkable British teenagers competing in a prestigious poetry competition in Washington D.C. From inner city Leeds to the American capital, this documentary charts the personal journeys of poets, hungry for change and full of fervour. Much more than just a hop across the pond; a resurrection of an ancient art form interwoven with inspiring snapshots of British youth.

title: West of Nevada
description: When a gang tries to rob Haldain, Jim and Walla Walla break it up. Haldain is carrying stuffed animals and Jim's suspicion that they are stuffed with gold is soon confirmed.

title: What if it Works?
description: Adrian, an irrepressibly chirpy tech nerd, has OCD. Grace, a beautiful street artist, has multiple personality disorder. It's a love story that seems impossible. But what if it works?

title: What Lies Within
description: What Lies Within chronicles 24 hours in the life of a happily married woman and her pregnant sister-in-law who are unwittingly thrust into the center of an incident that could have far reaching consequences on their lives and those of their loved ones.

title: When Love Happens Again
description: This unrelated sequel to “When Love Happens” continues with MO and Tope’s relationship in a safe place. Mo kicks off her own company, and her first account is with a billionaire, Demilade Adenuga. She has to travel to Washington DC for a merger she is putting together for Mr. Adenuga, leaving Tobe behind in Nigeria.

title: Wiper
description: A movie that educates on the disadvantages in youthful violence in africa. based on a true story.

title: 10 Minutes Gone
description: In this gripping thriller starring Bruce Willis, a safecracker (Michael Chiklis) wakes up from a traumatic head injury after a heist gone wrong and must find the traitor who set him up.

title: 200 Miles
description: The inspiring story of ultra-marathoner Eric Gelber unfolds as he attempts to run a record 200 miles around New York City's famed Central Park to raise both awareness and money for the Multiple Myeloma Research Foundation.

title: A Parisian Romance
description: A Parisian rake romances a parade of women and finally falls for the girl of his dreams.

title: A State of Mind
description: Three generations of Thomas men have all taken their own lives while battling depression. Darius Thomas must decide if he will face the beast head on, or crash right into his family's history.

title: American Driver
description: An American driver, Jack Curry takes a job driving Nigerian celebrities to the annual GIAMA Awards to impress his boss Kate. Along his journey he tries to become friends with actor Jim Iyke, who wants to be left alone.

title: April Showers
description: As Linda clocks 41, her hope of getting married finally disappears after several heartbreaking moments with men. She finally decides to get herself a baby from a one night stand with Greg, the son of a multi millionaire who's on a bet with his friends to get a woman under his duvet.

title: Bazaar
description: Kalki is an ardent follower of pigeon racing, which ultimately leads him to working for a mob boss who shares the same passion. Howevere, his dream of becoming a champion in the spot and his quest to win over the girl he loves wil eventually leave Kalki at a crossroads, and what happens next forms the crux of the story.

title: Black Belt: Kuro-Obi
description: In the year 1932, amidst political chaos, three young men are zealously engaged in karate training at the dojo of Eiken Shibahara. The Sensai's three students compete for the honor of becoming the new master.

title: Black Book
description: In the Nazi-occupied Netherlands during World War II, a Jewish singer infiltrates the regional Gestapo headquarters for the Dutch resistance.

title: Bonny And Clara
description: Two Petty Thieves (Bonny & Clara) get into trouble when they snatch a mysterious Briefcase which belongs to a notorious Gang Leader. Now they must run for their lives and also find a way to extract the content of the briefcase before Ebuka, the rightful owner catches up with them

title: Buddy Solitaire
description: Buddy Solitaire is a struggling comedian on the late night circuit. The only job he can get is teaching comedy to the mentally ill.

title: By Appointment Only
description: When a mother dies of heart failure in a doctor's office, the physician – feeling somewhat guilty because he couldn't save her – takes an interest in the woman's young daughter.

title: Chai Lai Angels: Dangerous Flowers
description: When the daughter of a Japanese karate master is kidnapped by terrorists for her knowledge of a hidden treasure deep on the ocean floor, five sexy undercover agents are enlisted to save the day.

title: Charlotte's Web
description: Miracles do happen! E.B. White's timeless children's story comes to life in this colorful animated musical.

title: CoComelon - Kids Songs and Nursery Rhymes
description: CoComelon is here to help preschoolers learn letters, numbers, animal sounds, colors, and more. The videos impart prosocial life lessons, providing parents with an opportunity to teach and play with their children as they watch together. Sing along to some of the popular nursery rhymes like Wheels on the bus, Mary had a little lamb, Twinkle Twinkle Little Star and more!

title: Code of Honor
description: Cardsharp Jack Cardigan decides to go straight when he meets Doris Bradfield, but is forced to use his talents on behalf of her dad, whose land-grant title has fallen into the hands of Jed Harden.

title: Colorado Kid
description: When Hines kills the Colonel for his money, the Colorado Kid is arrested and then found guilty of the murder.

title: Crave
description: Aiden craves a better life where he can escape his gruesome job as a crime scene photographer, meet the woman of his dreams, and save the world from evil. As Aiden's dark vigilante fantasies invade his reality, he'll soon learn that his imagination is on the verge of destroying the life he's risking everything for.

title: Crazy Grannies
description: This comedy/drama movie follows the hilarious adventures of three grandmas who decide to take a much-needed all-girls trip to a resort where they have the adventures of their lives.

title: Darling
description: A woman takes a job as a care taker in a strange old house known for unpleasant stories of forbidden occult practices and terrible rumors of morbid hauntings.

title: Daughters
description: Sold as a sex slave from a very young age by her father who couldn’t pay of his debts, Ella is groomed into a professional sex worker. Everything seems okay until One day she meets a new client , a very dangerous drug lord who brings back awful memories. Consumed by rage and anger she vows to kill him. Will she?

title: Dead Man Walking
description: In an Oscar-winning role, Susan Sarandon portrays Sister Helen Prejean, a spiritual woman who embarks on a dangerous quest with a convicted killer and the profound changes it makes in her life.

title: Desert Trail
description: Rodeo star John Scott and his gambler friend Kansas Charlie are wrongly accused of armed robbery. They leave town as fast as they can to go looking for their own suspects in Poker City.

title: Dirty
description: Two gangbangers-turned-cops try and cover up a scandal within the LAPD.

title: Disconnect
description: In the wired world of the 21st century, it's easy to establish connections with complete strangers, but convenience comes with a cost that affects every character in Murderball filmmaker Henry-Alex Rubin's gripping ensemble drama.

title: Down to the Sea
description: Played by Russell Hardie and Ben Lyon, the heroes battle over the affections of Ann Rutherford, whose father controls much of Florida's sponge industry.

title: Eating Our Way To Extinction
description: Narrated by Kate Winslet, this entertaining and surprising documentary will challenge the way you look at the food industry. What is the true cost of food? Who pays the price? Featuring shocking undercover footage and poignant first-hand accounts from indigenous people, this one-of-a-kind documentary will permanently change your perception of food and its connection to the future of our planet.

title: Edge Of The Axe
description: The rural community of Paddock County is being rocked by the crazed exploits of an axe-wielding psychopath, who stalks the night in a black trenchcoat and mask. As the victims pile up, the authorities attempt to keep a lid on the situation, whilst computer whizz-kid Gerald and girlfriend Lillian seek to unmask the killer before the town population reaches zero.

title: EIC: Outrage
description: 7 comedians rage on big issues: Demonetisation, Uniform Civil Code, Godmen, Global Warming and Cynicism in India in front of a 1000+ sold out audience.

title: EIC: Outrage
description: 7 comedians rage on big issues: Demonetisation, Uniform Civil Code, Godmen, Global Warming and Cynicism in India in front of a 1000+ sold out audience.

title: Escape Plan: The Extractors
description: In this explosive action saga, Sylvester Stallone, Curtis Jackson, and Dave Bautista play security experts who fight to rescue Breslin's girlfriend and a tech mogul's daughter from a formidable prison known as Devil's Station.

title: Europa Report
description: When unmanned probes suggest that a hidden ocean could exist underneath Europa's icy surface and may contain single-celled life, Europa Ventures, a privately funded space exploration company, sends six of the best astronauts from around the world to confirm the data and explore the revolutionary discovery.

title: GetAWAY
description: Maddie lands a small role in the student slasher-flick shooting at a camp this weekend, unaware it could be her last. A killer's on the loose shooting the grisly murders for his own twisted film. Maddie's the star and the slaughter is REAL!

title: Gorky Park
description: When three murder victims are discovered in Moscow's Gorky Park, Detective Renko (William Hurt) is determined to find the killer. But when the clues point toward the KGB, Renko is confronted by an intricate web of political deception and treachery.

title: Guns Akimbo
description: A guy relies on his newly acquired gladiator skills to save his ex-girlfriend from kidnappers.

title: Harry and Son
description: This character study centers on the agonies and delights of a widower and his artistically inclined son, who try to salvage their relationship after the father gets fired from his construction job.

title: Heart of the Home
description: Natalie and Kimiko are looking for a roommate. Miko moves in, and her bizarre behavior is quick to expose and escalate. Dark and twisted, Miko enjoys being the ultimate nightmare for anybody who encounters her.

title: Heist
description: A tenacious woman seeks answers from her husband by holding him hostage at the house. Things go overboard when the troupe is seized by two masked men, who discover a secret about the couple during a burglary.

title: Herbie Hancock: Possibilities
description: Ordinary music soars to extraordinary heights as gifted keyboardist Herbie Hancock joins forces with a variety of well-known music superstars to offer a completely original listening experience.

title: How I Live Now
description: Set in the near-future UK, Saoirse Ronan plays Daisy, an American teenager sent to stay with relatives in the English countryside. Initially withdrawn and alienated, she begins to warm up to her charming surroundings and strikes up a romance with the handsome Edmund (George MacKay). But on the fringes of their idyllic summer days are tense news reports of an escalating conflict in Europe. As the UK falls into a violent, chaotic military state, Daisy finds herself hiding and fighting to survive.

title: I Think I Love My Wife
description: HD. Chris Rock is a banker in a lackluster marriage who is tempted by a spicy woman in this comedy remake.

title: Joba
description: The faith of a childless Christian husband is tried, especially when all fingers points to him as the cause of their childlessness. He must protect his wife who is on a suicide mission whilst managing to keep the faith.

title: Joe Dancer 3 The Big Trade
description: Joe Dancer next case when a pizza delivery boy is thrown onto his car. Dancer soon discovers an interweaving story involving a Hollywood studio, a top star, and the porn biz

title: Just Before Dark
description: 10 years after she voluntered to be a surrogate mom for her sister who then denied her and the pregnancy, an embittered single mom has to fight to keep her daughter when her sister resurfaces, asking her for the child.

title: Kuriyan Jawan Bapu Preshaan
description: This film based on a person, who is surrounded by people, who always diverts father's thoughts, to doubt on his own daughter. But daughters prove everyone wrong and show that girls are not less than anyone.

title: Lake Placid: The Final Chapter
description: A rogue game warden breaks out her guns after the schemes of an obsessed poacher lands a group of high school students into the midst of the man-eating crocodile "nature preserve."

title: Lift
description: After viciously attacking a security guard, Sean's getaway is spoiled by a faulty elevator holding 5 strangers who now hold his future in their hands. Will they turn Sean into the police or offer him a chance at redemption?

title: Little Sweetheart
description: A thriller about a little girl who's spying on two strangers, blackmailing her brother and about to murder her best friend.

title: Lo and Behold, Reveries of the Connected World
description: Society depends on the Internet for nearly everything but rarely do we step back and recognize its endless intricacies and unsettling omnipotence. Presented by NETSCOUT, a leader in service assurance and cyber security, Werner Herzog explores our rapidly interconnecting online lives.

title: Love of my Life
description: A young man is held captive by a deranged surgeon and faced with the choice which can alter his life and the life of his loved ones forever.

title: Love Takes Flight
description: On a transcontinental flight from New York City to Los Angeles, Joan Lawson, the flight hostess, attracts the attention of a movie producer, Dave Miller, and he tries to persuade her to sign a movie contract.

title: Mixed Company
description: Joseph Bologna portrays a racially prejudiced basketball coach who is persuaded to adopt three (more!) kids of mixed ethnic backgrounds. Frustrated and angry at first, his feelings soon turn to love.

title: Miz Behaviour
description: A generous but condescending woman is forced to learn a lesson about real friendship.

title: Mr And Mrs Okoli
description: A delta parent visits their son in Lagos and ruin his relationship that he has built for two years. In attempt to make things right, they kidnapped his fiancée and return her to him by force.

title: Mummy, I'm A Zombie
description: In the sequel to Daddy, I'm A Zombie, the fate of the planet is again in Dixie's hands as she fights to end a battle between the living and the dead, while also balancing her popularity and campaigning for student council.

title: Namu, the Killer Whale
description: Robert Lansing and Lee Meriwether star in this warm and compelling family drama about a compassionate scientist who forms an unlikely friendship with a magnificent killer whale.

title: Oath of Vengeance
description: Fuzzy opens a store only to find that everyone buys on credit. The absence of cash is due to the range war between the cattlemen and the farmers started by Kinney.

title: Old Goats
description: Old Goats is the hilarious and heartfelt story of a trio of spirited senior citizens on a quest to make the most of their sunset years. Friends Bob, Britt and Dave are each confronting aging in his own unique fashion: Dave rebels against his wife's plans for their new retirement, hoarder Britt struggles with online dating, and lively ladies man Bob juggles a hyperactive social schedule.

title: On the Trail of Bigfoot: The Search
description: The second half of On the Trail of Bigfoot. The Search takes you deep into some of North America's densest forests in search of the legendary "Bigfoot". Joining teams around the country, documentarian, Seth Breedlove heads into remote regions investigators looking to prove the creature's existence by killing one. Along the way the On the Trail of team captures convincing audio, video & more!

title: Paradise Island
description: Ellen Bradford comes to the south sea island of Tonga to marry her fiancee and finds out he is a drunk. She also finds out that she is the only white woman on the island and, as such, has three men taking a deep interest in her.

title: Pinto Rustlers
description: Tom Evans is a young cowboy orphaned by a band of rustlers. Seeking revenge, Tom pretends to be a notorious ex-con and manages to worm his way into the gang in order to get the goods on the bunch.

title: Python
description: After a military plane crash near a small American town, a giant man-eating snake sets off on a killing spree. The locals must find a way to eliminate the snake, with the help of a scientist who knows about the snake and terminates it.

title: Raiders of the Seven Seas
description: A lusty pirate, Barbarossa (John Payne), escapes from a Spanish prison. With other inmates as crew, he captures a galleon – complete with a Spanish countess (Donna Reed).

title: Results
description: Divorced, rich, and utterly miserable, Danny [Kevin Corrigan] goes to the local gym, where he meets guru/owner Trevor [Guy Pearce] and irresistibly caustic trainer Kat [Cobie Smulders]. Their three lives are knotted, both professional and personally.

title: Ride Out For Revenge
description: A corrupt cavalry officer is put in charge of the Cheyenne migration from ancestral grounds to a reservation, but gold-hungry men try to dispossess the Indians from their land.

title: Run
description: Run is about a hardworking, uptight lady who lives a very boring and strictly regimented life.She goes running one night and witnesses a murder that puts her on the run and throws her life into chaos. She encounters all kinds of unsavoury characters and is thrown into situations that she has never been in, all in a bid to get back to her normal life.

title: Salt Of The Earth
description: Based on true story of a strike at a mine in New Mexico a story of prejudice and feminism.

title: San Fernando Valley
description: A ranch owner fires his ranch hands and brings in women to replace them. The owner's daughter wants the male hands back and comes up with a plan to do it.

title: Sniper 3
description: Sniper Thomas Beckett (Tom Berenger) is hired by NSA officials, William Avery (Denis Arndt) and Richard Addis (William Duffy) to perform a covert operation to eliminate a suspected terrorist. The terrorist turns out to be a friend of Beckett's and the real purpose of the mission turns out to be something other than what Beckett was told.

title: Son of Monte Cristo
description: In 1865, General Gurko Lanen is dictator of "Lichtenburg" in the Balkans. Rightful ruler Zona hopes to get aid from Napoleon III of France. The visiting Count of Monte Cristo falls for Zona and undertakes to help her.

title: Spinning Boris
description: This is the improbable but true story of three Americans hired against all odds to convince the Russian people to denounce Communism by spearheading Boris Yeltsin's bid for the Russian presidency.

title: Stalker
description: A fashion stylist finds herself being stalked by a man after her car breaks down in the countryside.

title: State Dept. File 649
description: U.S. Foreign Service officer matches wits with a Chinese warlord to try to save American citizens threatened with execution.

title: Suga Suga
description: A rich old man's love of philandering with younger women drives his wife and family to extremes.

title: Take a Giant Step
description: A young black man raised in a white neighborhood feels ill at ease and becomes delinquent.

title: The Amazing Transparent Man
description: A crazed scientist invents an invisibility formula. He plans to use the formula to create an army of invisible zombies.

title: The Doctor, The Tornado & The Kentucky Kid
description: It was the biggest race of 2005: the return of world championship motorcycle racing to US soil after an eleven year break. 2005 Laguna Seca, California. MotoGP hits the USA. Life, liberty and the pursuit of maximum speed.

title: The Love Letter
description: A bookstore manager in a small town finds an anonymous love letter and searches for the person who wrote it.

title: The Moment
description: Fearing she may be responsible, a mental patient tries to unravel the mystery behind her ex-lover's disappearance.

title: The Note
description: Following a tragic plane crash, newspaper columnist Peyton MacGruder discovers a note that was from one of the passengers onboard. She sets on a quest to find the person for whom it was intended, and discovers the life it will change is her own.

title: The One That Got Away
description: It may seem like an impossible feat to track down The One That Got Away, but in this time-traveling, experimental dating series hosted by Betty Who, six lucky Singles searching for their soulmate are given the chance to explore a lifetime of missed connections. One by one, people from our Singles’ past enter through The Portal to surprise them and take their shot at finding true love.

title: The Perfect Match (1987)
description: Tim and Nancy appear to have nothing in common, and from their first date their relationship looks destined for termination. But who needs something in common when they're in love.

title: The Silencing
description: A reformed hunter (Nikolaj Coster-Waldau) and a sheriff (Annabelle Wallis) are caught in a deadly game of cat and mouse when they set out to track a killer who may have kidnapped the hunter's daughter five years ago.

title: The Stay
description: When two couples rent a secluded house for a weekend getaway, they encounter an odd caretaker living on the property and become increasingly suspicious of his potentially sinister motives.

title: The Twilight Saga: New Moon - Extended Edition
description: The second film in the TWILIGHT franchise. Separated from Edward, Bella begins a friendship with werewolf Jacob Black (Taylor Lautner) that leads her even deeper into the supernatural.

title: The White Bus
description: An impassive young girl is taken from her suicidal London life, back to her home in North England on a bizarre bus trip. Seen through the poetic eye of the camera, this is a commentary of doomed British morbidity.

title: Twilight - Extended Edition
description: Bella Swan (Kristen Stewart) doesn't expect much when she moves to a small Washington town until she meets the mysterious and handsome Edward Cullen (Robert Pattinson), a boy who's hiding a dark secret: he's a vampire.

title: Unmasking the Idol
description: Secret agent, Duncan Jax, must form an elite strike force to stop the sale of atomic weapons to the Scarlet Leader, mankind's most evil and sadistic adversary.

title: Unwanted Guest
description: Ike, a Nigerian immigrant, has a great job, cool friends and the love of his beautiful American girlfriend, Nikki. But his world is turned upside down when he is surprised by a visitor from home. Ify, the wife he left behind.

title: World's Greatest Dad
description: In the wake of a freak accident, Lance suffers the worst tragedy and the greatest opportunity of his life. He is suddenly faced with the possibility of fame, fortune and popularity, if he can only live with the knowledge of how he got there.

title: Fences
description: Fences is directed by Denzel Washington from a screenplay by August Wilson, adapted from Wilson's Pulitzer Prize-winning play.

title: I Love You Both
description: A pair of co-dependent twins (Doug Archibald and Kristin Archibald) are charmed by the same guy (Lucas Neff) at a party. When they both start dating him, they must figure out which of them he likes better without upsetting their brother-sister bond.

title: Irish Jam
description: Upon discovering that their town is up for sale, crafty Irish villagers scheme to raise the money to prevent the buy-out. They hold a poetry contest with a tempting grand prize – the deed to their local pub. But what could happen when a duplicitous American rapper emerges as the best poet around?

title: Knock Off
description: A fashion designer who must join forces with a C.I.A. agent to combat terrorism.

title: Paper Girls
description: It's the day after Halloween in 1988 when four young friends accidentally stumble into an intergalactic battle and find themselves inexplicably transported to the year 2019. When they come face-to-face with their adult selves, each girl discovers her own strengths as together they try to find a way back to the past while saving the world of the future.

title: RIDE ON TIME
description: Ride On Time takes you backstage into the world of Japan's top boy bands - Johnny's. In this documentary series, we follow Johnny’s members and show you what their work is really like.

title: Super Fast
description: Undercover cop, Paul White joins Vin Serentos LA gang of illegal street racers. They are fast and furious and they plan to double cross crime kingpin Juan Carlos de la Sol who hides his cash in a downtown Taco Bell. The gangs outrageous plan is as daring as it is ridiculous but as Vin Serento says: It s not the car you drive... it is the driver who drives the car who is doing the driving.

title: Suzhal - The Vortex
description: Suzhal - The Vortex is a crime thriller that goes beyond the routine investigation and threatens to shake up the cultural societal fabric, when a crime hits a small town in India. Set against the backdrop of an unique micro-festival, ancient myths collide with the troubling present as we are drawn into the eye of the storm.

title: The Falling
description: This Spanish horror movie tells the story of three American teens on vacation in Spain who drive their RV into a tiny Spanish town where a large piece of Skylab has fallen and infected the town with a parasitic alien microbe.

title: The Oxford Murders
description: A woman is murdered in Oxford. Her body is discovered by two men, a prestigious professor and a young graduate student, who quickly realize that this is the first of a series of murders, all of which are announced by the murderer with strange mathematical symbols.

title: They Raid By Night
description: They Raid By Night

title: Tranquillo
description: Because of an appearing psychogenic Tinnitus a twenty-something youngster is forced to rethink his egoistic, urban lifestyle.

title: White Zombie
description: A young man turns to a witch doctor to lure the woman he loves away from her fiance, but instead turns her into a zombie slave.

title: Doorways
description: A woman from a parallel world enters present day earth through the "door" and befriends a doctor, who she takes on a life-threatening chase in a different universe.

title: EMANcipation
description: A great love turned into a violent terror. Dominik has lost it all: His wife, his son, his job, his house - even his pride. Without any money left and emotionally ruined he enters Berlin's first and only shelter for battered men. Trying to find out how it all went so horribly wrong.

title: Fritz the Cat
description: A hypocritical swinging college student cat raises hell in a satiric vision of various elements on the 1960's.

title: GT Serie 1
description: Global Adventure Trip

title: Louise By the Shore
description: On the last day of summer in a small seaside town, an older woman named Louise realizes that the last train has departed without her. She finds herself alone. As the weather turns for the worse, she must rely on her past to help her survive the present.

title: Muscle Shoals
description: Located alongside the Tennessee River, Muscle Shoals, Alabama has helped create some of the most important and resonant songs of all time. Overcoming crushing poverty and staggering tragedies, Rick Hall brought black and white together to create music for the generations. He is responsible for creating the "Muscle Shoals sound" and The Swampers, the house band at FAME Studios ...

title: My Beautiful Bride
description: A man tries to solve the mystery of his girlfriend's disappearance in this dreamlike, erotic tale of love, betrayal, and obsession inspired by the Brothers Grimm fairy tale "Hansel and Gretel".

title: Popi
description: A Puerto Rican widower struggles to raise two sons and give them a better life.

title: Re:MARS Explorations
description: Explore machine learning, automation, robotics, and space through the lens of luminaries-distinguished professors, leading CEOs, and head scientists.

title: Suicide Forest Village
description: From the Director of The Grudge. A group of friends unleash a curse after stumbling upon a mysterious box. To break the curse, they venture deep within Jukai Forest. It's said that the land holds a grudge where once you enter, you can never come out.

title: The Secret of Santa Vittoria
description: When villagers hear that the retreating Nazis will be coming through their town, they hide 1 million bottles of wine in an old Roman cave. When the SS arrive, they threaten death to anyone who withholds the wine.

title: The Zombie King
description: A man makes a pact with him to destroy the underworld and bring chaos to earth.

title: Up The Junction
description: Fragments of the life of three working-class women, and the people around them, in South London in the 1960s. Scenes in homes, streets, pubs, prison and their workplace cover family, friendship, romance, sex, and abortion.

title: Vanishing on 7th Street
description: In this horrifying thriller a strange blackout causes a city's population to vanish. As the days grow shorter a handful of survivors realize their only hope is to escape the haunted darkness. Starring Hayden Christensen.

title: Wilder Napalm
description: Two brothers, Wilder and Wallace Foudroyant (Arliss Howard and Dennis Quaid) have a lot in common. First, they can make flames roar into life just by thinking about them. And, second, they are in love with the same woman...Wilder's wife, Vida (Debra Winger).

title: Alienators
description: Revealed through footage compiled by The Civilian Department of Ufology, a privately owned research organization, two amateur ufologists decide to look into a woman's claim that aliens are watching her.

title: Dabangg 3 (Telugu)
description: Dabangg 3 is a high-voltage tongue-in-cheek story of a famous cop, Chulbul Pandey, an Uttar Pradesh cop who calls himself Robin Hood Pandey. Things take an unexpected turn when his past comes to haunt him as the face of the main antagonist of the film, Balli. Circumstances force Chulbul to take up the righteous path to protect his loved ones and family and do what is right in the eyes of the law.

title: Desperate Cargo
description: Gang of criminals hijacks a clipper ship with two girls on their way to the U.S.

title: Ella Cinders
description: Poor Ella Cinders is much abused by her evil step-mother and step-sisters. When she wins a local beauty contest she jumps at the chance to get out of her dead-end life and go to Hollywood, where she is promised a job in the movies.

title: Ghosts On The Loose
description: The East Side Kids try to fix up a house for newlyweds, but find the place next door "haunted" by mysterious men.

title: Half Baked
description: In this critically-panned cult classic stoner comedy, three New York City potheads band together to sell large quantities of marijuana in an effort to raise bail money for their friend when he’s arrested for accidentally killing a police horse.

title: Invisible Ghost
description: Bela turns into homicidal maniac.

title: JCVD
description: Jean-Claude Van Damme gets involved in a bank robbery with hostages situation and reflects about his life during it.

title: Kill For Me
description: Addison, a junior in college and also a member of a popular sorority on campus, becomes the primary suspect in the disappearance of her abusive quarterback boyfriend when the new girl, Hayden, kills him, expecting that Addison will now kill Hayden's abusive dad.

title: Levitated Mass
description: A documentary about a 340-ton boulder that was moved from a quarry in Riverside to LACMA and mounted atop a gigantic slot in the earth. Titled "Levitated Mass," it's the latest sculpture from controversial artist Michael Heizer.

title: Manhattan Merry-Go-Round
description: Gangsters take control of a record company and use toughguy tactics on unwilling performers.

title: Pain & Gain
description: When an ambitious group of personal trainers (Mark Wahlberg, Dwayne Johnson and Anthony Mackie) go after the American Dream, they get caught up in a criminal enterprise that goes horribly wrong.

title: Prince of Muck
description: Retired patriarch Lawrence MacEwen is beginning to live out his final days. As Laird of the Isle of Muck, it has been his mission to preserve the fragile society on this Scottish island, so it may pass to his son and future generations. Prince of Muck is a beautifully realised documentary about a man struggling to accept he no longer controls his son, his life, nor the isle he so loves.

title: Some Of My Best Friends Are
description: A dramatic expose of the lives of a group of gays who meet in a New York City bar on Christmas Eve.

title: The Gospel Live
genre: ['Arts, Entertainment, and Culture', 'Documentary', 'Music Videos and Concerts']
description: Hosted by Anthony Anderson (Barbershop, Hustle & Flow), The Gospel Live features live, soul-stirring performances by gospel superstars Mary Mary, Kelly Price, KiKi Sheard, Hezekiah Walker, Martha Munizzi and more! Also featuring all access red carpet interviews with celebrities including GRAMMY Award winner CeCe Winans and the all-star cast of the feature film The Gospel.

title: The Price of Coal: Part 1 - Meet the People
description: The workers of Milton Colliery prepare for a royal visit by H.R.H. Prince Charles.

title: Yedu Chepala Kadha
description: Ravi has weakness for women and gets into a physical relationship with ladies. One day, he falls in love with Bhavana. He has a heath issue, which requires blood. Why is he in a relationship with many women and what will happen to his love.

title: Young Buffalo Bill
description: Bill Cody and his pal Gabby fight off Indians sent by the Montez, who is trying to obtain an ancient Spanish land grant. Gabby is wounded, and the missing deed, written on a bandanna, is wrapped around his arm.

title: Amazonia - The Final Season
description: We are running out of time to preserve the Amazon rainforest. Urgent changes are needed to achieve this. The film, narrated by artist and activist Ben Harper, is a love poem that water dedicates to the rainforest as a declaration of its love. The transformation water goes through, from river to clouds and finally to rain, can teach us that change is possible.

title: Anchorman 2: The Legend Continues
description: Ron Burgundy is living in New York City with his wife Veronica Corningstone and son Walter. Everything changes when the boss fires Ron. His shot at redemption though comes in the form of the world's first 24-hour round the clock news channel.

title: Beneath The 12 Mile Reef
description: Fierce competition among sponge fishermen forces a Greek-American family to fish in the dangerous 12-mile reef area off the western coast of Florida.

title: Bikini Beach
description: A wealthy publisher wants to evict the surfers from the beach in favor of building a senior citizens' community.

title: Dying Laughing
description: Dying Laughing is a candid look inside the complicated and fascinating lives of some of the world's greatest stand-up comedians. A beautiful, funny and unique feature length documentary on the agony and the ecstasy of making people laugh.

title: Exiled
description: A friendship is formed between an ex-gangster, and two groups of hitmen - those who want to protect him and those who were sent to kill him.

title: Granny Nanny
description: A group of pensioners want to escape the boredom of their everyday life.

title: I Am Not Your Negro
description: With unprecedented access to James Baldwin’s original work, Raoul Peck completed a documentary film version of the novel Baldwin never finished – a radical narration about race in America that tracks the lives and assassinations of Baldwin’s friends Martin Luther King Jr., Malcolm X and Medgar Evers.

title: It's for Your Own Good
description: Three fathers who are also brothers-in-law make a pact to save their daughters from their boyfriends.

title: Let Go
description: Follows the intertwining stories of Walter Dishman, a melancholy parole officer struggling with the doldrums of married life, and three eccentric ex-convicts recently placed under his supervision.

title: Maanbumigu Maanavan
description: Shiva, a happy-go-lucky young man, helps two of his best friends get married, much to the dismay of their parents. When the woman is raped by Madan, Shiva and his friends seek to bring him to justice.

title: New Mexico
description: A cavalry captain has great difficulty keeping the peace between his tyrannical colonel and an Indian chief bent on revenge.

title: Nizhal Nijamagiradhu
description: Venkatchalam lives with his sister Indumathi, who hates men and vows to never get married. When Sanjeevi, Venkatchalam's friend, meets Indumathi, he falls in love with her.

title: Perfumes
description: Anne Walberg is a master in perfumes. She creates fragrances and sells her incredible gift to many companies. She is a diva, selfish and temperamental. Guillaume is her new driver and the only one who dares facing her. This is probably why she does not fire him.

title: The Appearance
