description: Mateho the Inquisitor (Jake Stormoen, "The Outpost") and his comrade (Kristian Nairn, "Game of Thrones") are summoned to investigate a series of mysterious murders and the alleged 'witch' accused of the horrific crimes.

title: The Cutting Edge
description: Action and romance take to the screen when a self-centered ex-hockey star (D.B. Sweeney) and a prima donna champion figure skater (Moira Kelly) become unlikely partners in pursuit of Olympic gold.

title: The Enigma of Arrival
description: A friendship falls apart after the disappearance of a girl.

title: The Foreigner
description: Michael Oblowitz directs Steven Seagal in this action film. Seagal portrays a secret agent named Cold who is hired to transport something from France to America. As he continues his travels, he finds he can trust no one, and that many people are out to do him harm in order to secure the contents of his package.

title: Tony n' Tina's Wedding
description: Two Italian families from different sides of the tracks are forced to come together when childhood sweethearts Tony and Tiny decide to get married after high school. Anything that can go wrong does, and the wedding rapidly gets out of hand.

title: White Bird in a Blizzard
description: Kat Connors' (Shailene Woodley) glamorous but strange mother Eve (Eva Green) vanishes. Kat is excited by her new freedom, distracted by the boy next door and the cop working the case. Disturbing facts surface and the mystery begins to haunt her.

title: Behind Some Dark Cloud
description: Jade, a seemingly aimless suburban 20 year old, spends her time writing and stripping while stalking a rumored Satanist. Through her adventures she uncovers a startling and tragic discovery, one that will make her face her biggest fear: growing up.

title: Guigo Offline
description: Guigo Offline

title: Microbe and Gasoline
description: Two young friends embark on a road trip across France in a vehicle they built themselves.

title: The Light of Western Stars
description: A woman from Boston buys a ranch near Mexico only to discover her land is being used by a band of outlaws to smuggle guns south of the border.

title: 86 Melrose Avenue
description: 86 Melrose Avenue is a drama about the chaotic clash between an eclectic group of people at a photography exhibit in LA. when taken hostage by a former soldier with PTSD

title: A View To A Kill
description: In pursuit of new computer super chips, Bond uncovers a plan which could destroy Silicon Valley and the West's computer industries.

title: At Night Comes Wolves
description: In this unnerving tale about misogyny and sexism comes a woman who is about to change the world forever. After Leah Shaffer leaves her manipulative husband, she learns that he used to be the leader of a cult which she is about to join.

title: Bad Witch
description: Xander is a witch whose abuse of black magic has led him to disaster after disaster. After trying to go clean of witchcraft, Xander befriends a young loner, helping Roland with bullies, girlfriends, and other teenage atrocities.

title: Bigger, Stronger, Faster
description: In the hopes of exploring American culture's increased obsession with winning, documentary filmmaker Christopher Bell examines the anabolic steroid use of his two brothers.

title: Bill & Ted's Excellent Adventure
description: Our non-heinous heroes Bill (Alex Winter) and Ted (Keanu Reeves) are in danger of flunking history! But when the righteous Rufus (George Carlin) arrives in a time-travelling phone booth, the dense dudes discover their destiny!

title: Breakable You
description: The film follows the Wellers, A dynamic New York City family as they come to terms with themselves and each other.

title: Bullied
description: 12 year old Charlotte commits the unthinkable when she stands up to Brenda the bully late one night.

title: Code Red
description: A Special Forces soldier is sent into Bulgaria when a chemical agent from WWII is uncovered that can reanimate the dead.

title: Coffee Defenders: a Path from Coca to Coffee
description: Johana, a coffee farmer, embarks on a journey with Alexandra, a reporter in search of a story. Along with a coffee seedling from Johana's plantation, they encounter persons and places throughout Colombia that, like Johana, overcame moments of war to now stand as living proof of the rebirth of an entire region as it transformed from coca to coffee. Dubbed version

title: De Viaje con los Derbez
description: Sin aceptar no como respuesta, Eugenio convence a su familia de tomar unas vacaciones juntos por primera vez en la vida. Aceptan dejarlo todo para acompañarlo por un mes a Marruecos. Juntos se embarcarán en una aventura loca y divertidísima.

title: Death Trip
description: Four friends take a cottage trip in the dead of winter. During their stay, they discover dark details about the neighboring cottagers. After one of the friends is found mutilated, the group worries they're being targeted by angry locals.

title: Diamonds Are Forever
description: Sean Connery returned as 007 to follow a diamond smuggling ring that ultimately leads to SPECTRE.

title: Dr. No
description: The film that introduced the world to Sean Connery as James Bond. 007 is sent to Jamaica to investigate the murders of two British operatives

title: Fiesta
description: Cholita, after a long absence in Mexico City, is returning home to take up her duties as head of the rancho and, as everyone expects, to marry her childhood sweetheart Jose.

title: For Your Eyes Only
description: In the race to beat the Russians to a missing communications device Bond finds himself involved with the Greek underworld.

title: From Russia with Love
description: Bond is back and he's paying the price for his previous adventure when SPECTRE lured him into a deadly trap to avenge the death of Dr. No. Will Bond's mission to find a Russian coding machine be his last?

title: Goldfinger
description: The third installment in the 007 series finds uberspy James Bond (Sean Connery) trying to thwart baddie Auric Goldfinger (Gert Frobe) and his elaborate gambit to corner the gold market by contaminating Fort Knox.

title: I Heart Shakey
description: After moving from a small town to Chicago, and missing the fine print in their rental contract, J.T. is forced to try and get rid of his lovable pooch, Shakey, and Chandler won't have it, and hatches a plan to keep Shakey and teach J.T. a valuable lesson about loyalty and the importance of keeping family together.

title: Idaho
description: A reformed bank robber, now a judge who shelters delinquent boys, is hung out to dry for a crime he didn't commit. Roy Rogers helps to clear the judge's name and puts the real crooks behind bars.

title: Jean of the Joneses
description: Chaos ensues after the estranged patriarch of the Jones family dies on their doorstep. When the paramedic who answers their 911 call tried to win over acerbic Jean Jones, his attempts are disrupted by old conflicts that come to a boil at the funeral.

title: K.G.F Chapter 2 (Hindi)
description: Vijendra Ingalgi, Son of Anand Ingalgi continues the story of KGF and Rocky in Chapter 2. Rocky survives the attack by Vanaram’s guards after killing Garuda. He is a hero and a saviour to the people of Narachi. While trying to fulfil his promise to his mother, he must face many obstacles in the form of Adheera, Inayat Khalil and Ramika sen.

title: K.G.F Chapter 2 (Kannada)
description: Vijendra Ingalgi, Son of Anand Ingalgi continues the story of KGF and Rocky in Chapter 2. Rocky survives the attack by Vanaram’s guards after killing Garuda. He is a hero and a saviour to the people of Narachi. While trying to fulfil his promise to his mother, he must face many obstacles in the form of Adheera, Inayat Khalil and Ramika sen.

title: K.G.F Chapter 2 (Malayalam)
description: Vijendra Ingalgi, Son of Anand Ingalgi continues the story of KGF and Rocky in Chapter 2. Rocky survives the attack by Vanaram’s guards after killing Garuda. He is a hero and a saviour to the people of Narachi. While trying to fulfil his promise to his mother, he must face many obstacles in the form of Adheera, Inayat Khalil and Ramika sen.

title: K.G.F Chapter 2 (Tamil)
description: Vijendra Ingalgi, Son of Anand Ingalgi continues the story of KGF and Rocky in Chapter 2. Rocky survives the attack by Vanaram’s guards after killing Garuda. He is a hero and a saviour to the people of Narachi. While trying to fulfil his promise to his mother, he must face many obstacles in the form of Adheera, Inayat Khalil and Ramika sen.

title: K.G.F Chapter 2 (Telugu)
description: Vijendra Ingalgi, Son of Anand Ingalgi continues the story of KGF and Rocky in Chapter 2. Rocky survives the attack by Vanaram’s guards after killing Garuda. He is a hero and a saviour to the people of Narachi. While trying to fulfil his promise to his mother, he must face many obstacles in the form of Adheera, Inayat Khalil and Ramika sen.

title: Licence to Kill
description: James Bond resigns from the Secret Service after a friend in the CIA (along with his new wife) is brutally murdered by drug lord Franz Sanchez. With a score to settle, Bond partners up with pilot Pam Bouvier and Sanchez's mistress.

title: Limerence
description: Rosemary, an aspiring painter and free spirit, moves to Venice, California where she falls for Tom, a charismatic gallery director. Their intense chemistry quickly evolves into a serious relationship that puts Rosemary to the test.

title: Live And Let Die
description: Roger Moore finds himself immersed in the world of heroin, voodoo and black magic in his debut as Bond.

title: Megamind
description: Packed with high-flying action and non-stop laughs, MEGAMIND puts a whole new hilarious twist on the superhero movie.

title: Mesa of Lost Women
description: A mad scientist named Arana is creating giant spiders and dwarfs in his lab on Zarpa Mesa in Mexico. He wants to create a master race of superwomen by injecting his female subjects with spider venom.

title: Moonraker
description: When a Moonraker space shuttle disappears the chase leads Bond into outer space.

title: Mother!
description: Jennifer Lawrence and Javier Bardem deliver unforgettable performances in Mother!, director Darren Aronofsky's praised opus. Experience the visually arresting psychological thriller that will leave your heart pounding and your mind blown!

title: Octopussy
description: Stolen art treasures lead to a plan that will see Europe fall to a Russian invasion unless Bond can stop it in time.

title: Paranormal Activity
description: After a young couple moves into what seems like a typical suburban "starter" tract house, they become increasingly disturbed by a presence that may be somehow demonic but is certainly most active in the middle of the night.

title: Petromax
description: Meera (Tamannaah) and her foster family of three, live in a bungalow and start to doubt that it's haunted. Meanwhile, prospective buyers, who visit the property claim there are ghosts in it. Four strangers strike a deal with the owner Shankar (Prem) to stay there for four nights to unravel the mystery. A series of confusions terrifies both the humans and ghosts alike.

title: Savage Dog
description: A story set in Indochina in 1959, a land beyond rule and a time without mercy and the birth of a legend.

title: Smart Alecks
description: Danny helps to capture a wanted criminal and receives a $200 reward. However, he has a falling out with the gang when they believe he should share the money with them.

title: Sonic the Hedgehog
description: Sonic is back on Planet Mobius, using his supersonic speedand teenage irreverence to thwart thecomedically despicable Dr. Robotnik. Sonic'sidolizing little buddy, Tails, tags along onevery fast-action, gag-driven adventure.

title: Stealing Cars
description: Billy Wyatt is a young man with tremendous promise, but a troubled past leads him to the Burnsville Camp for Boys. Billy must navigate his way through dangerous inmates and a cruel and punishing staff, but during it all, he learns to inspire others and find out the truth about himself in the process.

title: Syrup
description: Fresh out of school with a degree in marketing, "Scat" will do anything to prove that he has what it takes. Armed with a brilliant product concept that gives new meaning to the old saying "sex sells," he only has to convince his boss, the beautiful and mysterious "6," that it's an idea worth millions. The road to success isn't an easy one, even with a million dollar idea, and ...

title: The Adventures of Tartu
description: Stevenson, a British soldier fluent in Rumanian and German, goes undercover to sabotage a German poison-gas factory. He turns himself into Jan Tartu, a member of the Rumanian Iron Guard.

title: The Beast
description: A Soviet tank and its warring crew become separated from their patrol and lost in an Afghan valley with a group of vengeance-seeking rebels on their tracks.

title: The Big Cat
description: 1933. A city boy arrives in his late mother's birthplace to discover the locals have been pestered by drought, old fights and a cougar. He turns out to be pivotal in all of these.

title: The Bigamist
description: Harry and Eve Graham are trying to adopt a baby. The head of the agency senses Harry has a secret and does some investigating. He soon discovers Harry has done an unusual amount of traveling from his home in San Francisco to LA.

title: The Black Godfather
description: J.J., a rising star in the crime scene, is in the process of consolidating his power over the neighborhood. One of the only remaining obstacles is the heroin cartel is understandably reluctant to abandon such a lucrative market.

title: The Chocolate War
description: The Vigils are a gang of students at Trinity Catholic School...part of the tradition. They control the other boys by intimidation and the threat of violence.

title: The Living Daylights
description: Timothy Dalton's first outing as Bond sees him run into a covert Russian operation involving international drugs and arms deals.

title: The Man With the Golden Gun
description: Bond is assigned to retrieve a top secret solar power converter, but finds himself the target of the world's greatest professional assassin.

title: The Oak Room
description: When a drifter offers to settle an old debt with a grizzled bartender by telling him a story, the night's events quickly spin into a dark tale of mistaken identities, double-crosses and shocking violence.

title: The Quiet
description: Following the unexpected death of her father, a deaf and mute teenager moves in with her godparents, where she discovers the cruel behavior of their daughter may be indicative of a dark secret within the family.

title: The Spy Who Loved Me
description: An international crisis breaks out when a British submarine equipped with 16 nuclear warheads disappears. Agent 007 joins forces with a brainy female Russian spy to locate the vessel before the missiles can be launched at New York City.

title: Thunderball (4K UHD)
description: Terrorist mastermind Emilio Largo hijacks two nuclear weapons and has his sights set on a blackmail payday of global proportions – unless James Bond (Sean Connery) can stop him!

title: Tik Tik Tik
description: Dilip, a photographer, gets involved with a group of three supermodels on an international tour. Other models sent abroad seem to be dead, and when the cycle repeats, Dilip is suspected.

title: Undocument
description: Undocument bears witness to four journeys of love and loss, immigration and identity across three continents as one cinematic journey.

title: Vibes
description: Two psychics are hired to find the location of a lost Incan city Located somewhere in the Ecuadorian mountains, that is said to hide a great treasure.

title: Walking Tall
description: Based on true events from the life of Tennessee sheriff Buford Pusser, this film follows the sheriff who almost single-handedly removed corruption in his county with a four-foot-long wooden club, but at the cost of his personal and family life.

title: Wish You Were Here
description: Four friends lose themselves in a carefree holiday. Only three come back. Dave and Alice return home to their desperate for answers about Jeremy's mysterious disappearance. When Alice's sister Steph returns not long after, a nasty secret is revealed about the night her boyfriend went missing. But it is only the first of many. Who amongst them knows what happened on that fateful night in Cambodia?

title: You Only Live Twice
description: Bond goes to Japan to investigate the disappearance of American and Russian spacecraft.

title: Casino Royale
description: Based on Ian Fleming's first 007 novel, James Bond (Daniel Craig) must thwart a dangerous Russian spy who is funding global terrorists from winning a poker game worth millions. The 21st film in the most successful film series in cinematic history.

title: Come on, Cowboys
description: When the circus owner friend of the Mesquiteers is framed for counterfeiting by his unscrupulous partner, the trio pledges to maintain his interests and care for his young daughter.

title: Fading Gigolo
description: Murray (Woody Allen) talks his friend Fioravante (John Turturro) into becoming a gigolo as a way of making some much needed cash after an out-of-the-blue request from his dermatologist (Sharon Stone). With Murray acting as Fioravante's "manager," the duo quickly finds themselves caught up in the crosscurrents of love and money. Also stars Vanessa Paradis, Liev Schreiber and Sofía Vergara.

title: Give'em Hell Malone
description: A tough as nails private investigator (Malone) squares off with gangsters and their thugs to protect a valuable secret. Malone goes through hell to protect the information but he dishes some hell as well...

title: On Her Majesty's Secret Service
description: James Bond tracks arch-nemesis Ernst Blofeld to a mountaintop retreat where he's training an army of beautiful but lethal women. Along the way, Bond falls for Italian contessa Tracy Draco – and marries her!

title: One Step Behind the Seraphim
description: A group of freshmen in an orthodox college are introduced in a world of cons, pleasure and money, but they soon discover that's not the way one's life should be lead.

title: The Bat
description: Vincent Price stars in this thriller about a country estate that becomes the site of a murder. Writer/director Crane Wilbur helms this feature, with Agnes Moorehead, Gavin Gordon and Darla Hood as the cast. Which of them is The Bat? Watch and find out!

title: The Missing Lynx
description: A group of animals look for a way off of an eccentric billionaire's own personal Noah's Ark.

title: The White Knights
description: The head of an NGO Jacques Arnault is planning a high impact operation: to exfiltrate 300 orphans victims of Chadian civil war and bring them to French adoption applicants. Facing the brutal reality of war and the limits of humanitarian intervention, the NGO members start losing their convictions.

title: Trooper and the Legend of the Golden Key
description: Trooper, Tommy and their family have just moved to a new town, but they soon discover it's a small town with a mysterious legend; a legend of a Golden Key that could be worth one million dollars!

title: A Million Baby
description: Janet,a comfortable family woman who loves to give and help the needy falls victim of her own goodwill. A twist of circumstance lands her in the company of Morufu, Mama Oyinye and Johnny. The outcome would cause ripples of laughter.

title: Annie Hall
description: Woody Allen's hilarious comedy about a neurotic screenwriter and his erratic relationships with women - especially the love of his life, Annie Hall. Winner of four Oscars, including Best Picture and Best Actress (Diane Keaton).

title: Arbitration
description: The Arbitration"" tells the story of Gbenga and his employee Dara, who had an affair. After the affair ended and Dara left the company, she sued Gbenga and accused him of rape.An arbitration panel was constituted to find out the truth.

title: Benevolence
description: Ruth, a young woman is tenacious to hold on to her faith in God despite hard times, to keep her hope alive for a better tomorrow and insist on the kind love that she believes she deserves.

title: Bill & Ted's Bogus Journey
description: When an evil doer from the future sends robot twins of Bill & Ted to kill and replace the real deals, the guys wind up face to face with the Grim Reaper! Can the now-dead duo escape, defeat their evil twins, and win the Battle of the Bands contest?

title: Black Men Rock
description: When this family came together, it was a recipe for disaster that shook the foundations of their individual marriages

title: Black Swan
description: HD. Obsession drives a devoted ballerina (Oscar(R) winner Natalie Portman) to the brink of madness in this compelling masterpiece.

title: Call Me By Your Name
description: Amid the summer splendor of 1980's Italy, Elio and Oliver discover the heady beauty of awakening desire that will alter their lives forever.

title: Cameron's Closet
description: A young boy is befriended by an evil playmate who comes from inside the boy's closet.

title: Casey's Shadow
description: A funny and touching story for the whole family about an irascible, impoverished horse trainer Lloyd Bourdelle (Walter Matthau) and his three sons.

title: City of Dreams
description: A comedic look at Lagos and its residents inherent dreams and aspirations.

title: Corporate
description: Emilie, one of the Human Resources Managers at a multinational, has recently been chosen by her superior for her ruthlessness. She is traumatized by the tragic consequences of her actions.

title: Cutting Edge 3: Chasing the Dream
description: When world class skater Zack's (Lanter) chances to compete at ice-skating highest level are thwarted by an injury to his partner, he must find a new skater quickly or face the reality of not competing at all.

title: Death to summer
description: Dante spends his days hanging out at the factory, or with his skateboard or around corpses, but what he really cares about is his death metal band that he has with his friends. His comatose brother’s girlfriend Lucy comes to visit. Her presence causes chaos, confusion and hope.

title: Deep Cover
description: An undercover police is sent to investigate an inner circle of canny fraudsters.

title: Delta Force 2: The Colombian Connection
description: Chuck Norris is in peak form in this explosive action/adventure that brings back one of his most unforgettable characters, Delta Force Colonel Scott McCoy, for a daring mission to destroy a deadly drug cartel led by the ruthless Billy Drago!

title: Doctor Dolittle
description: HD. Rex Harrison doesn't just talk to the animals-he sings to them, doctors them and loves them all in this charming 1967 musical fantasy.

title: Double Strings
description: The perfect life of Jenny, who has a great job and a newly wedded husband is upended when she wakes up to the dead body of her husband. Facing accusation as the prime suspect in the murder, she starts to uncover dark secrets that puts her in the target of a criminal kingpin.

title: Dr. Dolittle 2
description: HD. Eddie Murphy is back as the doc who talks to the animals in this comedy sequel that has him playing matchmaker to a pair of bears.

title: Drawing Strength
description: Lami Washik an award winning architect with all the trappings of success but finds herself at crossroads with life where her Christian faith is questioned.

title: Duel at Diablo
description: James Garner and Sidney Poitier team up for this sweeping story of the bitter conflict between the Apache and the white man. Features stunning images of Utah's sun-blasted landscapes.

title: Easy Money
description: The discovery of money by three friends from a dying man unveils their true personality.

title: Feast of Love
description: An Oregon town is the backdrop for this tale of men and women touched by love's inescapable spell: From hopeless romantic Bradley (Greg Kinnear) to Harry (Morgan Freeman), a local professor with the wisdom and experience to guide those close to him.

title: For Old Times Sake
description: Andrew, a dance teacher is prepositioned by Catherine’s husband to begin an illicit affair with her for a fee. Andrew is torn between accepting the offer or listening to his conscience that tells him not to.

title: Go Back to China
description: When spoiled rich girl Sasha Li blows through half of her trust fund, she is cut off by her father and forced to go back to China and work for the family toy business.

title: Grapes on a Vine
description: Kyle is the art director at the High Museum in Atlanta Georgia. He wants two things in life, a male child and a van Gogh painting valued at 275,000. His wife Brandy cannot conceive so he plans a camping trip where he will have her killed and hung to make it look like a racially motivated killing so he can collect the 500,00 insurance policy which will enable him to get what he wants.

title: Groundhog Day
description: A nasty, self-centered (but hilarious) weatherman is forced to relive one strange day over and over again, until he gets it right.

title: I Am Michael
description: A gay-rights advocate (James Franco) shocks his boyfriend (Zachary Quinto), friends and family when he publicly renounces his homosexuality and marries a woman (Emma Roberts) in this controversial true story.

title: Inside Amy Schumer
description: The unapologetic Amy Schumer returns with another witty-gritty season, digging deep into gender stereotypes, erectile dysfunction and finger blasting, with cameos from A-listers Zach Braff, Paul Giamatti, Janeane Garafalo, and more.

title: Jeepers Creepers 2
description: As its 23 horrifying days of flesh-eating come to an end, the Creeper has embarked on its final voracious feeding frenzy while a terrified group of young athletes must come together to survive.

title: Julian Fellowes Presents Doctor Thorne
description: From the creator of Downton Abbey. Dr. Thorne lives a quiet life with niece Mary in Greshambury, home of the wealthy Gresham family. Unbeknownst to others, the Greshams have lost their fortune and matriarch Lady Arabella has a scheme to regain it via an arranged marriage with her son and an American heiress. However, her son plans to elope with Mary, which complicates Lady Arabella's plans.

title: Jumbled
description: A young girl in her early 30s who keeps her getting her heart broken eventually finds a suitable perfect ideal man for a relationship, only to find out that he may just be the worst of all men.

title: Juno
description: A self-sufficient teenage girl navigates her way through an unplanned pregnancy in her own unique style. Oscar winner for Best Original Screenplay.

title: King Invincible
description: King Invincible is a Nigerian epic film that tells a sprawling tale of love and war. A handsome warlord, Taari (Tope Tedela) is fast transitioning into a wolf due to the curse of the dogs that has been placed on him. He must immediately find the cure to this curse or be forever damned

title: Lagos Landing
description: A love story inspired by true events. JACQUILINE an uptight middle class French lady (Kayla Eva), joins a dating site in search of the perfect novel-like romance and adventure she's always imagined, and she connects with BAYO (Ramsey Nouah), a self-made young and rich lawyer from West Africa.

title: Lagos Real Fake Life
description: The film is based on true life sceneries, showing both true and fake lifestyles lived by some residents and visitors to the city of Lagos, Nigeria.

title: Laurie
description: What happens when Laurie finds what she had lost hope of ever finding in her patient, Andrew?

title: Let Karma
description: Driven apart by the stresses of life, a husband and wife must face their changing love. Will love triumph through the darkness?

title: Levi
description: When Levi, is diagnosed with a life-threatening medical condition, he decides to look for and get his childhood love interest (Somi), so they can finally be together before his death. However, Somi is already married, but Levi will not accept defeat.

title: Liars All
description: On New Year's eve in London, a provocative game spins out of control and ends in murder, the true killer elusive amidst conflicting testimony and hidden motives.

title: Lost In London
description: Okon and Bona are selected for an exchange programme in London and must decide whether they will return home after the programme or attempt to make it big in London.

title: Lotanna
description: A young man discovers that following the sudden death of his father, he has inherited his debt to a fearful loan shark called Don Cleff. Aided by an unbreakable resolve to succeed, his friends and his musical talent, he must find a way to solve this unfairly inherited problem or die trying.

title: Love Thy Neighbour
description: Fareed and Gbemi are determined to be better people by loving their neighbours as themselves but how much love will be for Lola their new neighbour.

title: Lovebirds
description: Two Nigerians in the Diaspora, Odion and Ivie, are deeply in love but their parents pose as obstacle. Their parents used to be very good friends, hence the closeness between both families, until a business agreement causes a rift between them

title: Loving Amanda
description: Loving Amanda is a romantic story about a young woman’s journey from brokenness to love, healing and redemption.

title: Mad about You
description: Dami, an A-list actor at the peak of his career and his fiancee, Nkechi, a sexy and highly sought after model who is also climbing the social ladder a little too fast. On the outside, they look like the perfect couple, the envy of all. Everyone wants to be them and everyone wants to be with them

title: Made in Chinatown
description: Goodfellas meets Ip Man when a young Chinese nobody sets out to become a Don in the Italian Mafia. He'll have to fight his way to the top to earn respect, find love, and discover his identity.

title: Made in Heaven
description: On the same night, they died and were on a queue to the Gate of Judgement, Angela was told to return to Earth. Richard escapes heaven to fight for Angela's love within seven days alongside his guardian angel

title: Makate Must Sell
description: Will a woman find true love in a world of duds? Constantly pressured by friends and family to tie the knot, Chioma must fight to make her own choices and follow her heart... regardless of what the world says.

title: Max Rules!
description: Three best friends spy on their families, sneak into each other's house, and organize elaborate pranks.

title: Meatballs
description: Wacky hijinks at a less-than-average summer camp.

title: Meet the In-Laws
description: When their respective parents oppose their union, a newly engaged couple learns that the reasons for pushback run deeper than just tribal differences.

title: Miracle On The Mountain: The Kincaid Family Story
description: A staunch professional executive and his wife coerce their two rebellious teens and their older sister and her boyfriend into taking a plane trip to celebrate their wedding anniversary in the mountains. The younger sister does not make it to the plane in time and the family leaves without her. Their small private plane then develops trouble and crashes in the isolated snowy mountains.

title: Missionary Man
description: A mysterious stranger rolls into town on a unique motorcycle. All he carries is the bible and a desire for justice. Past vengeance collides as Ryder rights an injustice from his past and liberates the small town from a malicious oppressor.

title: Moms' At War
description: It tells a story of two mothers who compete against themselves in other to ensure success in the lives of their children, in particular a scholarship competition

title: Mr. Wrong
description: A woman finds the seemingly perfect man to date, but soon regrets it.

title: New Money
description: A sales girl finds her dreams of becoming a fashion designer within reach when her absentee father leaves her his multi-billion dollar empire.

title: New York Undercover
description: This gritty drama focuses on the exciting and dangerous lives of two undercover New York policemen.

title: Not Without My Daughter
description: This compelling, true story follows an American woman and her young daughter trapped in Iran after her husband tricks her into visiting his homeland.

title: Okafor's Law
description: Okafor's Law states that once a man has had a woman, he can have her again at any time, and a believer in the law puts it to a test with past girlfriends over a 21-day period.

title: Paradise
description: Sarima, a beautiful woman, is tired of standing by her strict and busy husband, Wabiye. This pushes her  into the arms of another man, Kraft, who then betray her severely.

title: Payday
description: After an expensive night out, two flatmates become tangled in an overnight misadventure to recover their rent money so they can pay their dead landlord's daughter.

title: Riverhead
description: As winter creeps towards his home in rural Newfoundland, widower Patrick Whelan finds himself at odds with a young man who just returned home from the penitentiary and is determined to breathe new life into a long-standing blood feud. As violence erupts, Patrick is left plagued by guilt and fractured home life.

title: Roger Corman's Operation Rogue
description: Deep in the jungles of Southeast Asia, a terrorist organization has stolen materials to create a dangerous chemical bomb.

title: Scarred
description: Scarred is the story of a woman who finds joy and meaning to life in the eyes of a six year old.

title: Sergeant Tutu
description: Contents from a stolen bag motivates two crooked cops on an investigation that quickly goes down hill.

title: Seven Alone
description: A frontier family crosses the U.S. by wagon train, hoping for a better life in the Oregon Territory.

title: Seven and a Half Dates
description: A young woman, engrossed in her career, reluctantly yields to her father's plan to set her up on 10 dates to find a suitable husband.

title: Shaun Of The Dead
description: An aimless TV salesman (Simon Pegg) and his friend battle zombies.

title: Sincity
description: A busy couple try to reignite their love life with an impromptu weekend holiday, but their trip tests their relationship in unexpected ways.

title: Slow Country
description: A homeless teenage mother, who gets herself trapped in prostitution and drug trafficking for seven years in order to secure a good life for her son.

title: Social Media 101
description: Ada is a baker who puts up pictures/videos of her works. Emelda filters and photoshops everything she posts on social media. And, Gina, the married one, is restrained by her husband as to what she can post online.

title: Soft Work
description: Chief Ademuyiwa, an accomplished businessman with over eighteen companies, whose success is attributed to a code, but centered on a heist, is targeted at him by Dare Olusegun, an attractive conman.

title: Something Wicked
description: A widowed mother takes in her orphaned nephew, who is difficult to be with, as his mother struggles with the challenges of a failing business and balancing single parenthood.

title: Spoor
description: Janina Duszejko, an elderly woman, lives alone in the Klodzko Valley where a series of mysterious crimes are committed. Duszejko is convinced that she knows who or what is the murderer, but nobody believes her. Based on Olga Tokarczuk's (Nobel Prize Winner) novel 'Drive Your Plow Over the Bones of the Dead.'

title: Sunstroke
description: Academy Award winner Nikita Mikhalkov delivers an epic saga, a magnificent love story and portrait of Russia recalled during the glory days before its fall.

title: Surrender, Dorothy
description: When her daughter Sara (Davalos) unexpectedly passes away, Natalie (Keaton) retreats to the summer home where she and Sara used to visit. Time with her best friends and some of Sara's friends help her deal with her loss.

title: Swapped
description: Two couples decide to swap partners to see if they'll find the fulfillment that's missing in their marriages.

title: Sweet Smell of Success
description: In this blistering look at power and the press, a ruthless, all-powerful New York gossip columnist – J.J. Hunsecker – and a sleazy Broadway press agent – Sidney Falco (who panders to J.J.'s every whim) – cook up a smear campaign to ruin the career of the jazz musician who's in love with J.J.'s sister. From the novelette "Tell Me About It Tomorrow" by Ernest Lehman.

title: Tatu
description: In Tatu, we see the life of a mother and her attempt to salvage the idea of her only daughter being given away as a sacrifice for the atonement of sins

title: The Beast Within
description: The love story of a blind man and the woman who changes his life.

title: The Brady Bunch Movie
description: This film, directed by Betty Thomas, looks upon the original TV series on which it's based with both self-deprecating wit and wistful wonder.

title: The Call
description: Just as Woli is looking to make some quick cash to have a birthday celebration, he gets a call that has the potential to change his life.

title: The Chef's Wife
description: Marithe (Karine Viard) works in a training. One day, Carole (Emmanuelle Devos) arrives at the center, looking for new professional opportunities. She can no longer stand the pressure of working with her talented Michelin-starred chef husband, Sam (Roschdy Zem). When Marithe meets Sam, she can't help being attracted to him. She now has some very personal motives in helping Carole to start over��_

title: The Family Tree
description: A mother and wife stricken with memory loss allows a dysfunctional family a second chance at harmony and happiness.

title: The Hills Have Eyes (R)
description: HD. A family vacation takes a bloody detour thanks to cannibalistic mutants in this unrelenting remake of Wes Craven's 1977 cult horror film.

title: The Hills Have Eyes UNRATED
description: A reinterpretation of Wes Craven's 1977 suspenseful cult classic about a vacationing family who suddenly face a desperate battle for survival in the desert against bloodthirsty mutants.

title: The Honeymooners
description: Two best friends, bus driver Ralph Kramden and sewer worker Ed Norton, hatch a get-rich-quick scheme to get them out of Brooklyn and onto easy street.

title: The kinsman
description: Nneoma decides to return to Nigeria from Cotonou after losing her husband and two sons. Her devoted daughter in-law and late son's widow, Nadia, insist on following her back. In appreciation of Nadia's loyalty, Nneoma's sole desire and pursuit is to help Nadia get a good husband by playing cupid. A quest that takes them on a journey full of humour, drama and intrigue.

title: The Last Disco
description: It's 1979. The Disco was an escape from real life, a place to find love, and a moment to last forever in a dance. Except nothing can last forever, just like the dance that stops when the music ends. Frank is an ordinary guy, but when he stepped inside that Disco, he was special. One night, Frank believes that all of the answers to his problems will be solved when he wins the dance contest.

title: The Mod Squad
description: After being sent to jail, a trio of juvenile delinquents take a deal to become undercover cops to infiltrate a drug ring in the ultra-hip L.A. club scene.

title: The Owl And The Pussycat
description: Opposites can't help but attract in this outlandish pairing of a meek writer (George Segal) and a hot prostitute (Barbra Streisand).

title: The Sandlot
description: Youngsters will get a kick out of this kid's-eye-view story of what happens when a shy boy moves to a new neighborhood and becomes involved with a ragtag baseball team.

title: The Transporter
description: HD. A former Special Forces operative who runs a criminal delivery enterprise discovers he's carrying human cargo in this high-octane thriller.

title: The Twilight Saga:  New Moon
description: The second film in the TWILIGHT franchise. Separated from Edward, Bella begins a friendship with werewolf Jacob Black (Taylor Lautner) that leads her even deeper into the supernatural.

title: The Twilight Saga: Breaking Dawn - Part 1
description: In the fourth installment of The Twilight Saga, a marriage, honeymoon and the birth of a child bring unforeseen and shocking developments for Bella (Stewart) and Edward (Pattinson).

title: The Twilight Saga: Breaking Dawn Part 1 Extended Edition
description: Experience THE TWILIGHT SAGA: BREAKING DAWN - PART 1 like never before with the extended edition, featuring over eight minutes of new and extended scenes added by Director Bill Condon.

title: The Twilight Saga: Breaking Dawn Part 2
description: The birth of Bella and Edward’s child ignites forces that threaten to destroy them all as tensions build toward all-out war in the thrilling conclusion to the epic phenomenon.

title: The Twilight Saga: Eclipse - Extended Edition
description: It all begins...with a choice. In the third chapter of Stephenie Meyer's phenomenal Twilight series, Bella Swan is surrounded by danger as Seattle is hit by a string of murders and an evil vampire continues her quest for revenge.

title: The Twilight Saga: Eclipse - Extended Edition (Plus Bonus Feature)
description: The third film in the TWILIGHT franchise. Torn between Edward and Jacob, Bella must also confront a vengeful vampire and a string of grisly murders that terrorize Seattle.

title: The Twilight Saga: New Moon - Extended Edition
description: The second film in the TWILIGHT franchise. Separated from Edward, Bella begins a friendship with werewolf Jacob Black (Taylor Lautner) that leads her even deeper into the supernatural.

title: The Twilight Saga: New Moon - Extended Edition (Plus Bonus Features)
description: The second film in the TWILIGHT franchise. Separated from Edward, Bella begins a friendship with werewolf Jacob Black (Taylor Lautner) that leads her even deeper into the supernatural.

title: The Twilight Saga: The Complete Movie Collection
description: Passions ignite as vampires and werewolves clash in the immortal story of Bella, Edward, and Jacob. Experience the entire TWILIGHT saga with this thrilling 5-film collection. This bundle includes the following movies: Twilight, The Twilight Saga: New Moon, The Twilight Saga: Eclipse, The Twilight Saga: Breaking Dawn - Part 1, The Twilight Saga: Breaking Dawn Part 2.

title: The Wedding Party 2: Destination Dubai
description: Nonso continues his romance with Deirdre, the bridesmaid from London. While on a dinner date, Nonso proposes to Deirdre by accident and sets off a chain of events too powerful to stop. Deirdre's upper-crust British family are against the match, as are members of the Nigerian clan, but Deirdre's determination can't be contained, setting us on another colourful, chaotic journey to everlasting love.

title: There's Something About Metal
description: In Finland, metal music isn't just a sub culture, it's the mainstream. When monster rockers 'Baton Rogue Morgue', take us on a hilarious, white knuckle ride into their heavy metal lifestyle, we begin to understand why metal has such a grip on this nation.

title: Top Gun
description: High-flying adventure with barnstormer Tom Cruise falling for his beautiful instructor (Kelly McGillis), while he competes against fellow flyer Val Kilmer for the coveted 'Top Gun' award.

title: Trace
description: Uyi and Ivory Micheal are a newly-wed couple in a seemingly perfect marriage. After receiving a mysterious package which casts a shadow of doubt over their marriage, past secrets are brought to the surface and they must come to terms with these startling new revelations or risk being torn apart forever.

title: True Jackson, VP
description: True Jackson has a passion for fashion. She gets the chance of a lifetime when she's hired as the VP for a major fashion label. The problem? Her new coworkers are not too thrilled to have a 15 year old as their boss.

title: Twilight
description: The first film in the TWILIGHT franchise. Two hearts, two fates and two worlds - human and vampire - collide when Bella (Kristen Stewart) and Edward (Robert Pattinson) fall in love.

title: Twilight
description: Bella Swan (Kristen Stewart) doesn't expect much when she moves to a small Washington town until she meets the mysterious and handsome Edward Cullen (Robert Pattinson), a boy who's hiding a dark secret: he's a vampire.

title: Twilight - Extended Edition (Plus Bonus Feature)
description: The first film in the TWILIGHT franchise. Two hearts, two fates and two worlds - human and vampire - collide when Bella (Kristen Stewart) and Edward (Robert Pattinson) fall in love.

title: Twilight Saga: Eclipse
description: The third film in the TWILIGHT franchise. Torn between Edward and Jacob, Bella must also confront a vengeful vampire and a string of grisly murders that terrorize Seattle.

title: Tyler Perry's Meet the Browns - The Play
description: This play brings together a family after hearing the news of a passed away family member. Coming together for the funeral will be harder than it sounds. Through all the drama and commotion they find love and know that there's nothing like family.

title: Valkyrie
description: Tom Cruise (Mission Impossible) leads a distinguished cast in this gripping WWII drama. In this true story, senior Nazi party officials and top members of the German military enter into a conspiracy to assassinate Hitler and end WWII.

title: Vikings
description: Vikings follows the adventures of Ragnar Lothbrok the greatest hero of his age. The series tells the sagas of Ragnar's band of Viking brothers and his family, as he rises to become King of the Viking tribes. As well as being a fearless warrior, Ragnar embodies the Norse traditions of devotion to the gods, legend has it that he was a direct descendant of Odin, the god of war and warriors.

title: Whip It: Writer's Draft with Shauna Cross Featurette
description: Whip It is now available for Download! Join screenwriter Shauna Cross as she gives a beind the scenes look into the writing process for Whip It.

title: Whip It!
description: After years of indulging the ambitious dreams of her Texas mom by competing in beauty pageants, a sixteen year old misfit secretly joins the roller derby and discovers self-confidence, romance, and a new identity as a phenomenal league star.

title: White Men Can't Jump
description: Billy Hoyle and Sidney Deane are an unlikely pair of basketball hustlers. They team up to con their way across the courts of Los Angeles, playing a game that's fast, dangerous - and funny.

title: White Tiger
description: Great Patriotic War, early 1940s. After barely surviving a battle with a mysterious, ghostly-white Tiger tank, Red Army Sergeant Ivan Naydenov becomes obsessed with its destruction.

title: Will & Grace
description: The final season of Will And Grace is here! But dry your eyes and turn off the Gloria Gaynor as there's still bucket loads of laughs to enjoy before your favourite foursome ride off into the sunset.

title: Will & Grace ('17)
description: Eric McCormack, Debra Messing, Sean Hayes and Megan Mullally reprise their iconic roles as Will, Grace, Jack and Karen in the fabulous farewell season of "Will & Grace."

title: World War Z (Extended)
description: Former U.N. employee Gerry Lane is called upon to help stop the chaotic pandemic that has gripped populations around the world. He fights to keep his family safe, while searching for an answer to the outbreak.

title: Zero Hour
description: The heir to a retail empire returns home after his father passes to take over the family business, but faces a controversy involving money laundering and murder.

title: 1939: Westerplatte
description: September 1st, 1939. German battleship Schleswig-Holstein marks the start of World War II by firing on the garrison stationed at the Westerplatte peninsula in Poland.

title: Age of Treason
description: Bryan Brown as Falco, is a hard luck private investigator working the streets of Rome...in 69 A.D.! Falco and his partner Justus reluctantly accept an assignment to find the missing son of a prominent Roman Senator. Soon they are caught up in a deadly plot to control the future of the Roman Empire. Age of Treason presents the splendor and decadence of ancient Rome awash in mystery and intrigue.

title: Angels Crest
description: Thomas Dekker, Lynn Collins, Jeremy Piven, Kate Walsh & Mira Sorvino star in this powerful and moving drama about a town's struggle with guilt and innocence in the aftermath of a unthinkable tragedy.

title: ATypical Wednesday
description: A well-intentioned black man's weekly therapy visit makes a turn when a white kid is "left behind" at the therapist's office, they go on a misadventure to get him home.

title: Backstage with Katherine Ryan
description: For the first time ever, Katherine Ryan lifts the lid on what really goes on backstage at a stand-up show. She's put cameras everywhere to reveal the nerves, the gossip, the preparation, the excitement, the camaraderie and the clashes. This is a unique kind of stand-up show. Uncensored and unscripted, it's our nation's favourite comedians as you've never seen them before.

title: Blowfly Park
description: Kristian was once a talented hockey player. Now, he's a nobody. Then, after a night spent together, his buddy Alex goes missing. Kristian starts acting increasingly aggressive and irrational, getting mixed up with local kids, setting up shaky deals, looking to confront wrongdoers. Then, Alex is found dead...

title: Boonie Bears: The Big Top Secret
description: When a flood hits, Briar is washed away and ends up in the company of a traveling circus. Now his brother Bramble must embark on a grand journey to bring him home. Both of the Bear Brothers will need to learn the value of family in this wild adventure.

title: Close Up Kings
description: Close Up Kings follows the adventures of three best friends who happen to be some of America's best magicians. In each episode, Magick Bailey, Loki and Johnny Blaze travel from city to city, performing magic and accepting challenges to perform certain feats.

title: Emma's Chance
description: While fulfilling her community service hours at a horse rescue ranch, Emma forms an unlikely bond with an abused show horse who won't let anyone ride him. Gaining new skills and confidence, Emma hatches a plan to redeem herself and ultimately save the ranch she's grown to love.

title: End of Sentence
description: Frank Fogle embarks on a journey to honor his wife's last wish of spreading her ashes in a remote lake in her native Ireland and a promise of taking his estranged son, Sean, along for the trip.

title: Gunsmoke Ranch
description: Flagg is relocating flood victims to Gunsmoke Ranch. The Three Mesquiteers know Flagg to be a crook and try to warn them. They ignore the warning and improve the land only to find that it has been condemned for a new dam.

title: High Wild and Free
description: Producer/director Gordon Eastman takes his two sons on a journey to the wilds of British Columbia fishing, hunting, canoeing down miles of wild water, living with Indians and trapping beaver.

title: Horrid Henry: The Movie
description: Horrid Henry finds himself doing things he never ever thought he'd do, and then some.

title: Little Cigars
description: On the lam from her sadistic gangster boyfriend and his two henchmen, a gun moll becomes involved with a team of midgets who are, in reality, crooks.

title: Memorial Day
description: 13-year-old Kyle Vogel discovers the World War II footlocker belonging to his grandfather, Bud. Bud has never talked about the war, yet he finds himself striking a deal with his grandson: Kyle can pick any three souvenirs, and Bud will tell him the stories behind each one. Weaving Bud's complicated wartime past, along with Kyle's wartime future, these two men share parallel experiences in combat.

title: Shannon & Sophie
description: Celebrity Mother and Daughter, Shannon and Sophie are best friends and polar opposites, and together this diamond duo of Gene Simmons Family Jewels fame are navigating the everyday challenges of celebrity life while Sophie spreads her wings to leave the nest and Shannon flies closely and protectively behind.

title: Stella Dallas (1937)
description: Barbara Stanwyck is Stella Martin, a loud, vulgar factory-town girl who snares wealthy husband Stephen Dallas . When Stephen is offered a job in New York, Stella stays behind, knowing that she'll never be part of her husband's social circle. She pals around platonically with her old beau, the cheap and tasteless Ed Munn, a fact that drives yet another wedge between Stella and her husband. The final straw is daughter Laurel's birthday party, which is boycotted by the local bluenoses. Though she would like to remain part of her daughter's life, Stella knows that she and she alone is the reason that Laurel is shunned by the rest of the community.

title: The Cry of The Owl
description: A troubled young man retreats from the big city and his ex-wife for the tranquility of a small town. He is drawn into a relationship with a young woman whose boyfriend goes missing, leaving the new arrival as a suspect.

title: The Kingmaker
description: An extraordinary look into the controversial political career of Imelda Marcos, this documentary tells a cautionary tale of a powerful female leader whose questionable sense of reality divided a nation.

title: The Silent Mountain
description: A young Austrian soldier in World War I fights his way through the Alps to rescue his first love and escape the impending explosion that will rock the mountain.

title: The Worst Crime
description: In July 2002, Johnny Johnson was arrested and charged with the abduction and murder of 6-year-old Cassandra Williamson in Valley Park, Missouri. The effects of the crime continue to reverberate in the community. A decade after the capital murder trial, a juror described the killing as the worst possible crime. Does the worst possible crime warrant the worst possible punishment?

title: To Catch a King
description: In 1940, two Americans, Joe Jackson and Hannah Winter, attempt to thwart a plot to kidnap the Duke of Windsor during a visit to Windsor.

title: Unwanted
description: A lonely boy, who lives in Amsterdam with his refugee mother from Kosovo, keeps getting into trouble while yearning for her acceptance. But the traumas caused by the war, which his mother hides away from him, turn his world upside down.

title: War, Italian Style
description: On the eve of the Allied invasion, two American soldiers steal the Nazi offensive-strategy plans and are subsequently captured. But...donning the disguises of Hitler and an SS general, they fool their befuddled captor and escape.

title: West of the Divide
description: Ted Hayden impersonates a wanted man and joins Gentry's gang only to learn later that Gentry was the one who killed his father. He saves Virginia Winters' dad's ranch from Gentry and also rescues his long-lost brother Spud.

title: When's Your Birthday?
description: Some shady characters discover that a sad sack nightclub bus boy has the ability to predict outcomes of races and other events through astrology.

title: Billy the Kid Trapped
description: Stanton breaks Billy and his two friends Fuzzy and Jeff out of jail. He wants them free so three of his men can impersonate them for the robberies and murders he has planned.

title: Phenix
description: Paul is a country boy who grows up with a fascination for violence and justice. When he moves to the city and sees his friends and brother fall victim to gang attacks, a vigilante is born.

title: Scatter My Ashes at Bergdorf's
description: A documentary on the Manhattan department store with interviews from an array of fashion designers, style icons, and celebrities.

title: Starbuck
description: David Wosniak (Patrick Huard), a 42 year-old lovable but perpetual screw-up, finally decides to take control of his life.

title: Terror of Tiny Town
description: An evil gunslinging midget comes to terrorize the good little people of Tiny Town. The townspeople organize to defeat him, and zany antics ensue.

title: The Giant
description: Rikard is an autistic man who was separated from his mother. He thinks that he will get her back if he wins the Championship of pétanque. A giant is on his side.

title: 7 Chinese Brothers
description: Larry is an honest-to-a-fault, constantly inebriated slacker, who takes a job at the local Quick-Lube to support himself and his faithful dog Arrow and maybe hit on his new boss in the meantime.

title: Boys of the City (1942)
description: After their car breaks down, the Eastside Kids seek refuge in an old mansion inhabited by a judge. When the judge turns up dead, and the blame gets unfairly placed on one of their gang, it's up to them to find the real murderer.

title: Chop Shop
description: Chop Shop is set within the fractious, sexy world of a counter-culture hair salon. The misfits who enter Daniel's manic world find more than just a hair salon, they find a tight, dysfunctional, adoptive family working, fighting and partying under one roof.

title: Cold Skin
description: A young man arrives at a remote island to take a post of weather observer only to find himself defending the watchtower from deadly creatures which live in the island shores.

title: Daniel Isn't Real
description: Troubled college freshman Luke (Robbins) suffers a violent family trauma and resurrects his childhood imaginary friend Daniel (Schwarzenegger) to help him cope. Charismatic and full of manic energy, Daniel helps Luke to achieve his dreams, before pushing him to the very edge of sanity and into a desperate struggle for control of his mind – and his soul.

title: Fortress 2: Re-Entry
description: 7 years after the original Fortress movie, Brennick along with the rebels are captured and sent to a new, more sophisticated fortress prison, in outer space.

title: Godsend, The
description: When a strange woman has her baby at the Marlowe's house, then disappears, Kate Marlowe is forced to keep the baby, Bonnie. She loves the child, but when her own children are systematically killed, suspicion turns to Bonnie.

title: Happy Happy (English Subtitled)
description: Family is the most important thing in the world to Kaja. She is an eternal optimist in spite of living with a man who would rather go hunting with the boys.

title: Jesus Trejo: Stay At Home Son
description: Jesus Trejo's first one-hour special explores the Long Beach native's upbringing. From running his first marathon, to winning his first fight, "Stay at Home Son" paints the picture of a 1st generation Mexican-American.

title: Law of the Jungle
description: Nona Brooks, former member of a stranded theatrical troupe, earns a temporary living singing in a cafe in Duakwa, British Rhodesia, Africa.

title: Playback
description: A group of high school students digging into their town's dark past unearth a chilling secret, releasing an evil spirit that possesses its victims in this frightening thriller featuring Christian Slater.

title: Road to Perdition
description: TBD

title: Seaside (English Subtitled)
description: Seaside (Bord de Mer) is a film about Cayeux, a small beach town in France. Beautiful young Marie works at a pebble processing plant. Her boyfriend, Paul, a warehouse employee in winter and a lifeguard in summer.

title: Stagers
description: A unique property docu-soap that gives viewers privileged access to the world of home staging.

title: The Hard Corps
description: An Army veteran assembles a team of bodyguards to protect a former boxer. Complications arise when the boxer suspects his sister may be romantically involved with the bodyguard.

title: The Last of the Mohicans
description: As Alice and Cora Munro attempt to find their father, a British officer in the French and Indian War, they are set upon by French soldiers and their cohorts, Huron tribesmen led by the evil Magua.

title: The Perils of Pauline
description: The real life story of actress Pearl White during her rise to fame in silent serials.

title: The Road to Hollywood
description: Bing Crosby fans will be intrigued by this selection of scenes from early Crosby shorts woven together to create a fictional biography of one Hollywood's biggest stars. Director Bud Pollard appears as the narrator, while the king of the crooners sings such songs as 'One More Chance', and 'Wrap Your troubles in Dreams'.

title: This Is High School
description: A six-part series that gives audiences unprecedented access into the world of today's teenagers. Producers put 50 remote-controlled cameras in a typical secondary school - and let them run for eight weeks.

title: A Royal Night Out
description: On V.E. Day 1945, Princesses Margaret and Elizabeth defect their chaperones and sneak off for a wild evening in celebratory London.

title: American Maniacs
description: A terrifying story of six members of an evangelical Christian group who have been abducted in rural Kansas.

title: Brotherhood
description: Adam Buckley finds himself in the middle of a convenience store robbery during his last night as a pledge for a college fraternity. When the initiation ritual goes horribly wrong and everything starts falling apart, Adam is forced to choose between his new brothers or his ethics.

title: Chihuahua Too!
description: When the Fasteners inherit an old family vacation home, they soon realize it's being haunted by their ancestors dog, Sophie. Homer, their golden retriever, befriends Sophie and discovers that she is just looking for a family to love.

title: Chocolate (English Subtitled)
description: A young girl learns to fight from watching TV and the fighters at the boxing school next door. She sets upon a violent quest to collect payment for her ailing mother's medical expenses which ultimately leads her to her father, a member of the Yakuza.

title: Dead Man Running
description: Ex-Con Nick has a problem. One of the most vicious loan sharks in the city is cashing in on all his debts, and unfortunately, Nick is on his list. Given 24 hours to raise $100,000, Nick and his partner Bing embark on violent crime filled thrill ride to try and raise the cash before time runs out.

title: I Melt With You
description: When four 40-something college friends meet up for their annual reunion, things start to spiral out of control, and a pact they made as young men is revisited.

title: Race
description: A racing team stumbles onto a plot to destroy the peacekeeping Alliance, leading to a battle of survival with the fate of the universe hanging in the balance.

title: Scramble
description: After his girlfriend is kidnapped by an underground prostitution ring, Frank and his best friend Simon borrow ransom money, head out on a series of quests confronting ruthless gangsters and delivering dead bodies to save her.

title: Shapeshifter
description: Artist, producer, composer and multi-instrumentalist Luna Li (Hannah Bussiere Kim) that frames her debut album, Duality, with themes of belonging, community, and the rich generational inheritance of her Korean heritage. The visual narrative also explores themes of identity and kinship as fans watch Luna Li embark on an enchanting visit to a historic Korean hanbok atelier in LA's Koreatown.

title: Sher Shivraj
description: When Maharashtra was being crushed under the tyranical Adilshahi rule Lord Narsimha appeared to save them; this time in the form of Chhatrapati Shivaji Maharaj!

title: The Shut Ins
description: We catch up with Sharon Hill two years on. We meet hoarders Sue and Scott, and see how their obsessions cause tension between them and their loved ones.

title: All Stars
description: Two kids look to throw an ambitious dance show in order to save their struggling youth center.

title: Carrie
description: A sheltered high school girl unleashes her newly developed telekinetic powers after she is pushed too far by her peers.

title: Dad, I'm Sorry
description: The #1 box office hit of all time in Vietnam, Bo Gia (Dad, I'm Sorry), carries us into the soul of small-alley Saigon life through Ba Sang (Tran Thanh), a chronic meddler whose heart is too big for his own good. Flanked by a hyper-dysfunctional family, Ba Sang sacrifices day-to-day to preserve the tenuous balance between his bullying siblings and his rising YouTuber son.

title: Demon Warriors
description: A detective commits suicide in order to enter the spiritual realm between life and death. His purpose: to gain supernatural powers to combat and defeat a gang of demons controlled by the evil overlord Sadok.

title: Emergency
description: Ready for a night of legendary partying, three college students must weigh the pros and cons of calling the police when faced with an unexpected situation.

title: Eternally Yours
description: Anita Halstead, swept off her feet by magician Arturo, finds the results less than magical.

title: Flag Day
description: Jennifer Vogel's father John taught her so much about love and joy, but he also happened to be the most notorious counterfeiter in US history. Now, she struggles to rise above the wreckage of her past while reconciling the inescapable bond between them.

title: Half Magic
description: Explores themes of female empowerment through sex, work, and friendship. These women are able to come together through their frustration over male dominance and in fact use their newly formed sisterhood to lean on each other and understand that they must first learn to love themselves before doing anything else.

title: Heropanti 2
description: Tiger plays a computer genius and Tara is a self-made billionaire. The two fall in love but due to unforeseen circumstances they suddenly part ways. When they are reunited, action, drama and edge of the seat thrills follow as the world wants Tiger dead.

title: Hotele Lerallaneng (Hotel on the Koppies)
description: Jabu is a young novelist tormented by his personal demons of alcohol and drug addiction. After a stint in rehab, and maintaining three months sobriety, he returns to Johannesburg, South Africa to serve on the jury of a film festival. However, his main purpose is to rekindle his relationship with his son, Timmy.

title: Iain Stirling - Failing Upwards
description: BAFTA-winning comedian, “the voiceover of a generation” (Evening Standard) voice of ‘Love Island’ and co-creator & star of “zippy, gag-dense” (Guardian) ‘Buffering’, Iain Stirling explores topics including his inability to function in the most basic of public settings, the pressures of being in the public eye and that one time a man stole his shoes. Live from London’s Alexandra Palace Theatre.

title: James Dean
description: A dramatization of the story of legendary movie actor James Dean. The film's writer, William Bast, had roomed with Dean in the early '50s, when both were trying to break into films as actors.

title: Kick Like Tayla
description: A raw and unfiltered look into the life of AFLW player and boxing champion, Tayla Harris, as she confronts public and personal challenges, and channels her platform for good.

title: LOL: Last One Laughing Germany
description: It’s finally here: the third season of Germany’s most successful comedy game show LAST ONE LAUGHING. Ten great performers from the world of show business come together to undertake the ultimate challenge. They all want to let loose and have fun together, yet need to remain serious, because, as always: you laugh and you’re out.

title: Nightmare in Suburbia
description: The ratings-winning drama-documentary returns with mores hocking contemporaryBritish crimes and the police investigations that followed.

title: Quitters
description: A teenager's family falls apart, so he finds a better one.

title: Sports On Fire
description: Sports on Fire is a Canadian television documentary series, which explores the historical, political and social context of several important moments in sports history.

title: The Devil You Know
description: This true crime series offers a unique glimpse into the twisted world of the worst criminals on file. Riddled with shocking details, The Devil You Know gives access to the stories of the heartbroken victims and the heatless criminals they loved, offering a rare insight to the criminal mind.

title: The River Murders
description: While investigating a series of murders, a homicide detective becomes the prime suspect when the FBI uncovers his close personal ties to all the victims.

title: We Are The Giant
description: With remarkable access, We Are the Giant takes its audience inside the lives of six extraordinary people who grapple with the agonizing and universal dilemmas at the heart of all struggles for justice and freedom: whether to take up arms and fight, or to advocate change through peace and non-violence.

title: 1939: Westerplatte
description: September 1st, 1939. German battleship Schleswig-Holstein marks the start of World War II by firing on the garrison stationed at the Westerplatte peninsula in Poland.

title: A Stalker In The House
description: After an uncomfortable online date, Jen looks to avoid Mike. However, he has other ideas. Obsessed and dangerous, Mike does not intend to let Jen go so easily and she finds herself in a fight for her life.

title: Above the Clouds
description: When Charlie discovers her parents have hidden her real father from her, she does what any 18-year old would - recruits a homeless guy as her 'responsible adult' and sets off to Scotland on her provisional driving licence to go find him.

title: Almost Heaven
description: Mark Brady is the charismatic, alcohol-fuelled director of a fishing show that happens to star his temperamental ex-wife. While filming, he meets a feisty local fishing guide whom he is instantly attracted to. However, are his feelings strong enough to keep him away from the bottle and on the straight and narrow?

title: Americana
description: After returning from a 2 year rehab for alcoholism, an film editor returns to a movie project starring his sister but must once again face his demons when she turns up murdered.

title: Angel By Thursday
description: Two families struggling with scars of the past, find they are linked by a series of uncanny events, propelling them on a journey in search of forgiveness, healing and hope.

title: Autumn Wanderer
description: Charlie meets the woman of his dreams. Mysterious, beautiful, and passionate, her presence ignites a life changing adventure.

title: Bill W.
description: William G. Wilson is co-founder of Alcoholics Anonymous, a man included in TIME Magazine's "100 Persons of the 20th Century." Interviews, recreations, and rare archival material reveal how Bill Wilson, a hopeless drunk near death from his alcoholism, found a way out of his own addiction and then forged a path for countless others to follow...

title: Breed Apart, A
description: A picturesque tale of a famed mountain climber, hired to pilfer specimens of a new breed of Bald Eagles and his entanglement with a conservationist and a fishing supply store owner.

title: Canyonlands
description: 5 contest winners and their troubled guide embark on an overnight rafting trip down the Colorado in Utah. Camping for the night, they soon discover they aren't alone in the remote canyonlands, and struggle to survive in the maze of rugged canyons.

title: Crown Heights
description: In the wake of the 1991 Crown Heights riots in Brooklyn, a Hasidic Jewish man and an African American man band together to spread hope to the disillusioned youth of their embattled and racially divided community.

title: Dangerous Charter
description: The crew of a fishing boat discovers a deserted luxury yacht at sea with a dead body on board. They claim the yacht as salvage, not knowing that a drug smuggling ring has hidden $500,000 worth of heroin on the boat.

title: Eye of the Beholder
description: The Eye (Ewan McGregor) is an intelligence agent whose current assignment is to track Joanna Eris (Ashley Judd), a woman suspected of blackmailing a senior government official. But the Eye soon learns that Eris is far more than a blackmailer. As he follows her, he becomes fascinated with what he sees. Soon his surveillance becomes a deadly obsession.

title: Flint Tale
description: After an injury and losing her college basketball scholarship, a young woman returning home struggles to rebuild her life as she and her family in Flint, Michigan face internal turmoil and the aftermath of a deadly water crisis. The bonds of family are all they have left as they rebuild their lives, their town, and their hope for their future.

title: Gecko's Garage - Vehicle Cartoons for Kids
description: Watch fun educational cartoons for children with Gecko's Garage. There are loads of trucks for children here such as monster trucks, fire trucks, ice cream trucks, buses, and construction trucks. These Gecko learning videos for kids will help children learn colors, learn shapes, learn numbers, learn the alphabet, and much more.

title: Glorifying the American Girl
description: The rise of a showgirl, Gloria Hughes, culminating in a Ziegfeld extravaganza "Glorifying the American Girl".

title: Heroes in Blue
description: Gangster Moran gives Joe Murphy several thousand dollars to bet on a horse race, but after the horse wins and Joe takes off with the money. Gangster Moran seeks revenge.

title: Honeydew
description: A young couple is forced to seek shelter in the home of an aging farmer and her peculiar son, when they suddenly begin having strange cravings and hallucinations taking them down a rabbit hole of the bizarre. Introducing Sawyer Spielberg.

title: Jesse James' Women
description: Jesse James keeps so busy skirt-chasing that his outlaw career starts to suffer.

title: Man with Two Lives
description: A man is brought back from death at the same time a vicious criminal dies in the electric chair. However, the man's soul is now taken over by the electrocuted gangster, who embarks on a vengeful crime wave.

title: No Way Out
description: Trying to salvage a relationship, 2 couples go on a weekend camping trip only to find out that they aren't alone in the woods.

title: Not Since You
description: A romantic drama about a tight-knit group of college friends who graduated from NYU and reunite years later for a weekend wedding in Georgia.

title: Outpost
description: In war-torn Eastern Europe, a world-weary group of mercenaries discover a long-hidden secret in an abandoned WWII bunker.

title: Passchendaele
description: The lives of a troubled veteran, his nurse girlfriend and a naive boy intersect first in Alberta and then in Belgium during the bloody World War I battle of Passchendaele.

title: Pocket Full Of Game 2
description: It's been fifteen years since Porsha Garcia left New York City and the cold streets of East Harlem.

title: Sweet Country
description: Australian western set on the Northern Territory frontier in the 1920s, where justice itself is put on trial when an aged Aboriginal farmhand shoots a white man in self defense and goes on the run as posse gathers to hunt him down. Festival favorite of Venice, Toronto, and Sundance.

title: The Adventures of Snow White and Rose Red
description: While roaming the forest near their cottage, Snow White and Rose Red learn the woods are magical and begin to cross paths with characters they've only read about in their fairy tale book! As they embark on their adventures, the girls learn the importance of sisterhood, friendship, and kindness, and that life can be far from ordinary, if you just believe in a little magic.

title: The Body Beneath
description: A family of vampires takes over an estate known as Carfax Abbey. Since inbreeding is destroying the family line, they need new blood to keep the family going, so they set out to find new sources.

title: The Crickets Dance
description: Angie Lawrence, a southern attorney, becomes entranced with a lost diary that she hardly notices when Andrew Ruben McGrath, is assigned to share an office with her. They're just two people searching for the truth and hoping to find love

title: The Inspector General
description: A down and out is mistaken for the Inspector General when they believe he is traveling incognito. They worry that he might stumble onto their petty crimes and they plan to get rid of him.

title: The Looking Glass
description: After losing her mother, 13-year-old Julie comes to live with her grandmother. Julie struggles as she and her grandmother butt heads at every turn. The discovery of their shared talent enables Julie to find her her passion and, ultimately, happiness.

title: The Snows of Kilimanjaro
description: Writer Harry Street reflects on his life as he lies dying from an infection while on safari in the shadow of Mount Kilimanjaro.

title: Whatever It Takes
description: Two Los Angeles cops go undercover to investigate the distribution of steroids to wrestlers and bodybuilders.

title: Wrangler's Roost
description: The notorious outlaw Black Bart has reappeared and the Range Busters are sent to investigate. When they find that Black Bart is now a respectable citizen and that someone is impersonating him, they set a trap for the robber.

title: Wushu Warrior
description: China, 1862: Lord Lindsey rules the opium trade and enslaves the innocent. The only hope for the oppressed nation is a covert group of trained Wushu Warriors - The Red Lotus Society - who will fight to restore justice to its people.

title: 10 Cent Pistol
description: A story about two lifelong criminals who maneuver through the shady underbelly of Los Angeles in search of wealth, love and redemption.

title: Before I Go to Sleep
description: A woman wakes up every day, remembering nothing as a result of a traumatic accident in her past. One day, new terrifying truths emerge that force her to question everyone around her.

title: Beverly H.
description: Beverly H. is set in Beverly Hills, California. It focuses on Beverly Hightower, founder and CEO of Fortress Biotech and Dr. Robert Karsten "Dr. Bob" to his friends, her top scientist and creator of the first life extension drug.

title: Big Kill
description: A tenderfoot from Philadelphia, two misfit gamblers on the run, and a deadly preacher have a date with destiny in a boom town gone bust called Big Kill.

title: Brothers In Arms
description: The most dangerous outlaws in the New Mexico territory take their revenge on the bloodthirsty crew who murdered their kin in this fresh look at cowboys living large in the wild American West.

title: Change in the Air
description: When a secretive woman breezes into a quiet town, her subdued neighbors get swept up in curiosity over her ethereal presence.

title: Chloe
description: Becky’s lonely life is nothing like Chloe’s charmed one. One-time teenage friends, she now only watches Chloe through social media. When Chloe dies suddenly, Becky assumes a new identity and infiltrates the lives of Chloe's friends to find out why. As Sasha, she discovers the conflicting faces of Chloe, but is increasingly lost in her lies. Will she uncover the truth before she loses herself?

title: Chutney Popcorn
description: A woman. Her girlfriend. A sister. Her husband. Their baby.

title: Citizens of the World
description: Three men in their seventies decide to leave their neighborhood life in Rome and find somewhere to relocate abroad.

title: Dead End
