title: Transit
description: As a modern-day Paris is invaded by foreign troops, German refugee Georg flees to Marseille assuming the identity of a deceased writer. There he delves into the delicate culture of the refugee community, becomes involved in the lives of a mother and son, and meets the writer’s enigmatic wife Marie.

title: Twice Told Tales
description: Vincent Price hosts three chilling horror tales based on stories by Nathaniel Hawthorne.

title: Until September
description: Paris is set ablaze in this passionate romantic tale of a stranded American tourist (Karen Allen), a handsome young Frenchman (Thierry Lhermitte) and the magnetic, secret affair that binds them.

title: Up The Creek
description: Four of the worst of that worst university have been chosen to bring honor to the institution, and degrees to themselves in a collegiate whitewater raft race in which dirty work is the main event.

title: Wah Wah
description: Ralph Compton (Nicolas Hoult) witnesses the disintegration of his parents' marriage through adultery and alcohol set during the last gasp of the British Empire in Swaziland in 1969. When his father (Gabriel Byrne) remarries an American (Emily Watson), Ralph finds she is the only one who can truly understand his inner turmoil.

title: Western World
description: When US Marshal Moses White is called to the Wyoming Territory town of Dogwood Pass to track a known killer, he runs into more than he bargained for.

title: Where the Lilies Bloom
description: A young woman (Julie Gholson) struggles to keep her family together after her father's death in this deeply moving drama that also stars Harry Dean Stanton.

title: Wild Geese II
description: A lone surviving Nazi leader's secrets could destroy the careers of several prominent political figures.

title: With a Kiss I Die
description: Forced to live forever knowing her love died in her arms nearly 800 years ago, Juliet Capulet finds herself falling in love with a young woman and is once again forced to choose between love and her family obligation, haunted by her past mistakes.

title: Wraith
description: After living in an old mansion for almost 10 years a family suddenly discovers a ghost-like presence trying to communicate with them. The spirit wants to become part of the family. Will they let it?

title: Wyvern
description: Floating toward Beaver Mills, Alaska, is a glacier-an icy tomb for a prehistoric winged creature. Once released, it turns the small community into a feeding ground sending helpless residents into a fight for their lives.

title: 1 Million Happy Nows
description: Veteran soap opera star Lainey and her partner Eva are ready for their beach house retirement. Unfortunately, Lainey's early-onset Alzheimer's puts a strain on the couple's relationship, forcing them to rediscover what they mean to each other.

title: 2nd Date Sex
description: Hoping for better relationships after being emotionally destroyed by their exes, Laura and Ryan are trying to navigate dating. As they head out on their second date, it becomes obvious that neither of them has any idea what they're supposed to do.

title: Behind Some Dark Cloud
description: Jade, a seemingly aimless suburban 20 year old, spends her time writing and stripping while stalking a rumored Satanist. Through her adventures she uncovers a startling and tragic discovery.

title: Billy Boy
description: After the tragic murder of one of his close friends, angry teenager Billy's world unravels. But when he meets Jennifer and tries to move on, his future is jeopardized by the sins of his past, and Billy finds himself in grave danger.

title: Black Fist (1977)
description: To make money, a Los Angeles street-fighter goes to work for gangsters.

title: Blue Chips
description: A college basketball coach puts his high principles to the test when he is forces to break the rules to get the players he needs to keep his team competitive.

title: Bobbie Jo and the Outlaw
description: A stunning carhop who wants to be a country singer and her sweetheart who dreams he's Billy the Kid become involved in robbery and murder.

title: Butterfly Caught
description: Three beautiful aspiring actresses embark on a mission to break into the competitive Los Angeles acting scene, only to discover the road leading to stardom comes at a price.

title: Census Taker
description: When a census taker's questions probe too deep, a seemingly average couple kills him and hides the body.

title: Daniel Boone (1936)
description: In 1775, Daniel Boone settles Kentucky, despite menacing Indians and renegade whites.

title: Deacons For Defense
description: Marcus is a passive black family man in Bolalusa, Lousiana, who refuses to get involved in the civil rights movement. All that changes when he is arrested for trying to defend his daughter during a protest, triggering a desire to finally take a stand.

title: Delirium
description: A young man attempts to reach the doorstep of a legendary old house, reputed to be haunted, but when he doesn't return, the classmates who dared him must go in after him, discovering the truth about the house, and their friend's gruesome fate.

title: Diverge
description: The survivor of a deadly virus is given the chance to reclaim his lost life by stopping the man responsible for the disease.

title: Don't Talk to Irene
description: When Irene - the fattest girl in high school - gets suspended, she is assigned two weeks of community service at a retirement home. Following her passion for cheerleading, she enlists the seniors to audition for a talent-search reality show.

title: Earthling, The
description: This story follows a loner who spent his life exploring the world and avoiding his feelings. When he returns to his Australian birthplace, fate throws him together with young loner, an orphaned, city-bred boy with little hope even less self-reliance.

title: Fitzwilly
description: The laughs begin as Dick Van Dyke, an eccentric philanthropist's dutiful servant, resorts to thievery in order to keep his now-penniless employer living in style.

title: Gone Tomorrow
description: When his niece is kidnapped, a tormented ex-con, who once took the fall for his brother years ago, flees his parole to find her, tracking down an unraveling criminal syndicate. Now, he must once again sacrifice everything in the name of family.

title: Harry In Your Pocket
description: A highly professional team of pickpockets (James Coburn, Michael Sarrazin, Trish Van Devere and a scene-stealing Walter Pidgeon) roam through varying cityscapes in the U.S. and Canada, preying – with disturbing charm – upon the innocent.

title: High-Ballin'
description: Fear pervades the trucking industry as a viscous gang of hijackers are attacking independent drivers and stealing their rigs. A Stunt cyclist, his trucking buddy, and a busty female trucker take on the gang in a series of hair-raising escapades.

title: Man From Utah
description: In a horse-riding rodeo contest bad guys want John Weston to lose. When he doesn't go along they add some insurance: a poisoned needle just under his saddle.

title: Mothers and Daughters
description: Rigby Gray, a photographer, gets an unexpected positive pregnancy test which leads her to turn her lens inward and discover what motherhood means by studying other mother daughter relationships, including the strained relationship with her own mother.

title: Nana
description: She's the demon of Paris. Men lavish their wealth and attention on her but her appetites are insatiable. She risks everything for pleasure, leaving a trail of broken hearts as she revels in the ecstasy of forbidden love.

title: Piranhas
description: Based on the novel by Roberto Saviano (Gomorrah), PIRANHAS follows teenage Nicola and his friends who, reaching for a life lush with designer clothing and status, enter the violent, power-hungry culture controlled by the Neapolitan mafia. Includes English subtitles-user may need to turn subtitles on.

title: Raja Rajan
description: General Nagavelan desires to become the Chozha king and plans to kill Prince Rajarajan who hinders his path to the throne.

title: Retina
description: A young woman participates in a medical study. After a series of nightmares and unusual side effects, the line between dreams and reality is blurred.

title: Sarbjit
description: Biopic of Sarabjit Singh, a farmer residing at Bhikiwind, Punjab, near the Indo-Pak border, crossed the border after having a couple of drinks. However, he was mistaken to be an Indian spy and was sentenced to capital punishment.

title: Sergeant Dead Head
description: Girl-shy/accident-prone Sgt. Deadhead (Frankie Avalon) accidentally goes into orbit with a chimp and returns to Earth with an aggressive new personality.

title: Sunset Range
description: Grant hides stolen money in the luggage of Bonnie Shea who is moving west. Later when he and his men arrive to retrieve the money, they also kidnap Bonnie. This sends Reasonin' Bates and his cowhands on their horses.

title: The Flying Deuces
description: Oliver is heartbroken when he finds that Georgette, the inkeeper's daughter he's fallen in love with, is already married to dashing Foreign Legion officer Francois.

title: The Malta Story
description: Alec Guiness stars as Peter Ross, a World War II camera reconnaissance pilot, who crash lands in Matla with evidence that the Italians are building up forces for a major invasion of the island. Will Malta fall to the enemy?

title: The Savage Wild
description: A nature photographer and his crew film the wild land just below the Arctic Circle. The photographer then begins rasing timber wold cubs from infancy, intending to set them free after gaining their confidence.

title: The Tall Men
description: A challenged man is stalked by tall phantoms in business suits after he purchases a car with a mysterious black credit card.

title: Where's Chicky? - Around the World Pt.1
description: Nobody knows where Chicky is exactly. We just know he is cute and deeply naïve. In this compilation, follow Chicky as he visits some of the most recognizable landmarks all around the world!

title: Where's Chicky? - Around the World Pt.4
description: Nobody knows where Chicky is exactly, we just know he is cute and deeply naïve. In this compilation, follow Chicky as he visits some of the most recognizable landmarks all around the world!

title: Yongary Monster From The Deep
description: A monstrous creature creates destruction throughout Korea...before scientists discover that a refrigerant is the only weapon that can stop it.

title: Dance of the Phoenix
description: In modern-day China, a quiet, shy young female student named Meng Yuan works hard at her dream of becoming a leading practitioner of Chinese traditional medicine. But on one fateful day, she finds herself transported into the body of a woman named Feng Wu - who lives in a fantasy land where magic and martial arts rule the world.

title: Eggy
description: It's everyone's favorite time of year in the magical town of Puff! It's a time for best pals Eggy and Top Hat to hop around with their furry friends, and take part in exciting new adventures. But when the evil Crow Witch tries to ruin their big party, the animals put all their eggs in one basket and begin their hunt to save the town!

title: Ombatthane Dikku
description: Varadappa, a sawmill owner and rural don sends his trustworthy friend Vasudev to close a deal worth a lot of money with Loki, an associate of his in Bangalore. Vasudev's son Channakeshava finds out that his father has been missing since the deal.

title: 6 Pack Band - Ae Raju
description: Presenting to you Brooke Bond Red Label 6 Pack Band's fifth single, ‘Ae Raju’, and this time with Bollywood’s biggest heartthrob, Hrithik Roshan! Hrithik and the 6 Pack Band come together to defeat DEFEAT, and make this world a more welcoming place.

title: All The Old Knives
description: Two CIA agents and ex-lovers (Chris Pine and Thandiwe Newton) are brought back together years after a failed rescue attempt and forced to blur the lines between profession and passion in this deeply riveting tale of global espionage, moral dilemma and deadly betrayal.

title: Alpha Wolf
description: After a secluded long weekend in the idyllic countryside, husband and wife Virginia and Jack find their already strained relationship ripping at the seams when Jack transforms into a murderous werewolf.

title: Black Widows (2016)
description: In the bustling dating scene of Los Angeles, an innocent girl hopes to achieve the impossible: romance. But when she is raped by the man of her dreams, she and her friends band together to enact a seemingly harmless revenge plot.

title: Cómo Sobrevivir Soltero
description: Sebastian pays tribute to a previous girlfriend, trying to produce the movie that she inspired him to write. With the help of Natalia they seek to produce the film, but they cannot obtain the financing; for which they decide to pass the story to a theatrical montage. For this they look for a renowned actor who ends up becoming Sebastián's "best friend." This affects his relationship with Natalia.

title: Do, Re & Mi
description: Do, Re and Mi use music to help solve any problem in Beebopsburgh. Whether it’s singing a song to express big feelings or singing in unison to work together better in the Tweeting Games, this trio is ready for any challenge. Like how to make a bicycle built for two something that three friends can enjoy, or what to do when extra friends show up to a sleepover.

title: Guilty Minds
description: Guilty Minds is a legal drama about one family that is the paragon of virtue and the other, a leading law firm dealing with all shades of grey.

title: I Do, Or Die: A Killer Arrangement
description: When a teenage daughter realizes her traditional Romani parents have arranged a marriage for her, she must fight for her independence – and her life.

title: Jackrabbit
description: After his best friend Eric commits suicide, Simon finds a mysterious computer drive, which contains an encrypted message Eric left for him. With the help of a fringe hacker and an accomplished technician, Simon attempts to decipher it.

title: LA GORDA FABIOLA: MODEL 63
description: Health problems, overweight, children and the age difference in her marital relationship are the raw material for the humor of La Gorda Fabiola. She will share with us the secret behind her good health and her big heart, one of the largest and most resistant in Colombia.

title: Lost In The White City
description: When a young couple travels to Tel Aviv to rebuild their relationship, they meet an Israeli soldier who drives a wedge between their already fragile existence, all while political strife simmers around them.

title: Naradan
description: Naradan is a dramatic journey of Chandraprakash, a popular news anchor in the media world who is desperate to prove his worth.

title: The Naked Hills
description: After an unfullfilling life in farming, Tracy Powell (Wayne) leaves his wife Julie (Henderson) and newborn son to strike it rich in the gold rush of '49 in California. However, Tracy finds six years of failure, picking a plot of desert to mine gold and incurring the wrath of local dictator Willis Haver (Backus). This ends in an exciting and violent final confrontation, in which Powell barely survives to return home, but soon leaves again to pursue his obsession. This pattern continues for years, until he returns home for good a poor, broken man in his 60's. Despite his treatment of his wife and now grown son, they take him back with open arms. Wonderful film with Wayne in a rare leading role, and Backus in an usual villainous role.

title: Turbulence
description: A scuffle aboard a 747 bound for New York frees a murderer-in-transit, kills the pilot and puts a stewardess at the helm.

title: Who's Watching Oliver
description: Mentally unstable loner Oliver wanders the streets on a shocking and humiliating killing spree. But when he meets the eccentric and beautiful Sophia, Oliver thinks he's found an escape, while Sophia doesn't know the danger she's put herself in.

title: You are My Destiny
description: On-board a cruise ship bound for the Bahamas, two people from separate worlds have a chance encounter, transforming them into one another's destiny. The mousy and unassertive admin assistant, Chen Jia Xin meets the handsome, educated, and charming Wang Xi Yi heir to a large toiletries conglomerate.

title: Bittersweet Symphony
description: When musician Iris Evans lands a contract to score a Hollywood feature, her agent sends over composer Eleanor Roberts, an alcoholic with ruinous insecurities. As they work together, Iris finds her personal life getting increasingly more complicated.

title: Day Zero
description: Humanity is rapidly consuming Earth's fresh water supplies while removing nature's ability to replenish them. Explore the journey to when Earth's fresh water supplies will exhaust in service to modern comforts.

title: For Love & Country
description: Country music has always been Black music. For Love & Country examines the genre's past through the lens of a new generation of Black artists claiming space in Nashville, and transforming country music in the process.

title: I Do, But I Don't
description: Wedding planner Lauren Crandell's job is to work miracles on other people's weddings. Unfortunately, when troubleshooting her own life, she's hit a few snags. Now, as the wedding of the year approaches, Lauren finds her own aspirations on the line.

title: Las huellas de elBulli
description: This documentary is a guide that gathers the gastronomic legacy of Ferran Adrià and his team in kitchens in many countries such as Japan, in the hotel industry or in TV formats of global success - expanding the look towards other areas to show the influence that a small restaurant hidden in a remote cove of Girona even today exerts in art, economy, science or sport.

title: Laura Pausini - Pleasure to meet you
description: Laura Pausini: Pleasure to Meet You – it's the movie that retraces the Laura’s life in a wholly original way. Through never-seen-before footage of her real and fictional life, the artist shows us her essence, giving an honest and bold analysis of her life and how it could have been without that victory at Sanremo that, in 1993, changed her destiny forever.

title: Squishville - Cartoons For Kids
description: Get ready to follow Fifi, Cam, Winston, and Lola as they squish their way in and out of hilarious situations! Watch as your favorite squad takes on Squishville with a few of their squishiest friends like Jeanne, Sharie, Leonard, and Hans!

title: The Elizabeth Smart Story
description: When fourteen-year-old Elizabeth Smart was kidnapped from her bedroom in her suburban home, it created an unprecedented media frenzy. Now, with details never before revealed to the public, comes the true story of the young victim who never gave up hope.

title: The Innocents
description: Warsaw, December 1945: a young French Red Cross doctor is summoned to a local convent where she discovers several nuns in various states of pregnancy, facing an unprecedented crisis of faith as their fiercely private world clashes with harsh realities. Includes English subtitles-user may need to turn subtitles on.

title: The Wilds
description: Survival hangs in the balance for a group of teenage girls stranded on a deserted island, after the explosive discovery that whats happening to them is an elaborate social experiment. Season 2 ups the drama and keeps you guessing, with the introduction of more test subjects - a new island of teenage boys - who must also fight for survival under the watchful eye of the experiments puppet master.

title: 7 Splinters In Time
description: Investigating a murder, a detective is shocked to discover that the victim has a body identical to his own. As he discovers multiple versions of himself, he comes to the terrifying realization that not all of them are friendly.

title: After She Wakes
description: After a tragic death, a narcoleptic mother and her young daughter develop terrifying sleep disruptions as they attempt to cope with their ongoing grief. These nightmares quickly become too disturbing when they manifest into a terrifying reality.

title: American Romance
