description: Inside the Circle is a quirky romantic dramedy that tells the story of a girl who believes in relationships and marriage, and who falls for a comic book and superhero-loving man who does not share her same beliefs.

title: Triple Seat
description: A young, happy couple`s life gets turned upside down when the guy receives a call from an unknown woman who claims to be in danger. A new take on the classic love triangle, Triple Seat brings to you a light-hearted story about wireless love.

title: All Roads Lead to Rome
description: Maggie is an uptight, single mother and college writing teacher from New York City. In an effort to reconnect with her troubled teen daughter Summer, she decides to embark on a journey to a Tuscan village that she frequented in her younger days.

title: Neville Shah Going Downhill
description: In this show, Neville narrates stories about his struggles with his age, being orphaned, adulthood, death, depression, divorce and suicide. This isn’t the only thing that doesn’t make it a regular stand up special. He leaves his audience bereft of hope, mostly because he hadn't gone to therapy that week. It’s dark, it’s poignant, it’s melancholic but it’s hilarious.

title: Power of 1
description: When a pop artist takes a stand against government policies, he is drawn into a political game he didn't bargain for.

title: Poyo Poyo Video Calls
description: Since the virus, it's hard to meet your friends in person and spend time together. So today, Pororo and Tayo decide to hangout through facetime! They are going to share how they've been doing and more! Let's facetime with Tayo and Pororo!

title: Silent Rain (English Subtitled)
description: Yukisuke is attracted to a girl Koyomi, who runs a small stand of taiyaki pastry that he often buys. Koyomi is hospitalized, however, by a car accident on a rainy day after they go out together, and wakes up with short term memory loss, where she cannot remember anything beyond the present day. Yukisuke tries to live close to her as before but the lack of collective memory starts to stagger him.

title: The Danny Thomas Show
description: Originally titled "Make Room for Daddy," this classic sitcom follows a NYC nightclub entertainer (Danny Thomas) as he hilariously juggles his career and family life.

title: A Hero
description: Rahim is in prison because of a debt he was unable to repay. During a two-day leave, he tries to convince his creditor to withdraw his complaint against the payment of part of the sum. But things don't go as planned…

title: JHIMMA
description: 7 women from different age groups and different socio-cultural backgrounds come together on a vacation with a tour company to ENGLAND. During the course of this trip these women unfold their journey. This trip turns into an opportunity to mend fences, heal wounds, fall in love with themselves, combat their worst fears and celebrate life.

title: LIVE TOUR V6 groove at SAITAMA
description: “LIVE TOUR V6 groove” is the culmination of V6's 26-year long career. This footage is from their concert at Saitama Super Arena. The V6 members pulled out all the stops to make this a great performance, down to the last details. Don't miss witnessing the strong bond that the six members of V6 have built together over 26 years.

title: No Activity
description: The improbable events caused by unconventional detectives Shingo Tokita(Etsushi Toyokawa) and Asobu Shiina(Tomoya Nakamura) lead to an outrageous development. On the other hand, Misato Satomi(Yoshino Kimura) and Arira Ohira(Nana Seino) in the radio room,Isayama(Goro Kishitani), Ichijo(Amane Okayama) and Mari (Yukino Kishii) lurking in the warehouse are also unexpectedly developed ...

title: The Improvisers: Something From Nothing
description: The Improvisers feat. Kanan Gill, Abish Mathew, Kenny Sebastian and Kaneez Surka perform their first Improv Special; Something from Nothing. It's a completely improvised show where everything you see will be made up on the spot. Nothing rehearsed, nothing scripted. The show will incorporate music, theatre and comedy. It's interactive, it's fun and out of the ordinary-Have Suggestion? Will Improv!

title: V6 LIVE COLLECTION 2007~2020
description: The V6 LIVE COLLECTION 2007~2020 features footage from a total of eight different V6 concerts held from 2007 to 2017, including V6's 25th anniversary concert "For the 25th Anniversary" from 2020. Witness the group's relentless dedication through their creative performances and attention to detail. Relive the excitement of V6's sensational concerts through these handpicked scenes.

title: Christian Finnegan: Show Your Work
description: Filmed in a tiny backyard at the height of the pandemic, Christian Finnegan brings his brand of 'social autopsy' to topics that range from the dumb (pharmaceutical names, baguettes) to the super dumb (QAnon).

title: Fundamentally Cynical
description: Fast paced show that revolves around a moronic camp counselor, named Lizard Boy, and a group of highly cynical campers. LB is the main counselor at, "Camp Dingle-dork" which is owned by an eccentric and reclusive millionaire by the same name.

title: Romeo & Juliet
description: In a city rife with inter-family violence, tabloid journalism, and failing infrastructure, two teenagers defy their families and dream of a life together.

title: Sarileru Neekevvaru
description: Sarileru Neekevvaru is the story of Ajay Krishna (Mahesh Babu), a superior Army Major who is a player in handling tough tasks across the border. Soon, Ajay moves to Kurnool on a secret mission and he comes to know about a tiff of a family with the antagonist.

title: The Lord of the Rings: The Rings of Power
description: Beginning in a time of relative peace, we follow an ensemble cast of characters as they confront the re-emergence of evil to Middle-earth. From the darkest depths of the Misty Mountains, to the majestic forests of Lindon, to the breathtaking island kingdom of Númenor, to the furthest reaches of the map, these kingdoms and characters will carve out legacies that live on long after they are gone.

title: LOL: Last One Laughing Canada
description: Jay Baruchel hosts the epic six-episode series featuring 10 of Canada’s funniest comedians trying to make each other laugh for the shot at comedy glory and a $100,000 prize for charity. The only problem is if they laugh themselves, they’re oot and aboot-ed from the game.

title: The Boys Presents: Diabolical
description: From some of the most unhinged and maniacal minds in Hollywood today comes Diabolical, a collection of eight irreverent and emotionally shocking animated short films. Featuring stories by Seth Rogen, Awkwafina, Andy Samberg, Aisha Tyler, Justin Roiland, and more, each episode plunges elbow-deep into unseen crevices of The Boys Universe.

title: The Thing Inside Us
description: A husband sets cameras around his home in an effort to document his wife's sleepwalking. What he finds could not only destroy his relationship, but the world itself.

title: Playa's Ball
description: Cedric Tinsel (Allen Payne) is a 27-year-old professional basketball player. He is on a verge of signing a lucrative endorsement contract and proposing to his girlfriend Jill Hamlin (Chelsi Smith).

title: The Carmilla Movie
description: It's been 5 years since Laura & Carmilla vanquished the apocalypse & Carmilla became a mortal human. They've moved into an apartment in Toronto but their domestic bliss is ruptured when Carmilla begins to show signs of "re-vamping".

title: Treasure Chest Of Horrors
description: Join Percival Pirate on his quest to discover his Grandpappy's hidden treasure chest. What might have contained a wealth of gold, precious jewels, and doubloons ends up holding a much more valuable treasure: four never before seen short horror films guaranteed to rattle your bones. The "booty" features vampires, killer mannequins, a high school killing spree and more.

title: Treasure Chest Of Horrors 2
description: Mona Screamalot, along with her crazy family, prepares you for six short horror films from deep within her trashy treasure chest. This anthology features party killers, giant killer babies, an angry murderous child, a bacterial infection like no other, a murderous cross dresser,a killer in the woods, and Satan. Oh yeah, don't forget the buckets of blood.

title: Mio on the Shore (English Subtitled)
description: 20-year-old Mio has lost her parents early and runs a Japanese inn with her grandmother. As her grandmother gets hospitalized, Mio reluctantly comes to Tokyo to live with her father’s old friend Kyosuke. Helping him at the bathhouse he runs, she begins to find her way in everyday life. However, she learns the bathhouse is on the verge of demolition for the redevelopment in the district.

title: Sorabh Pant: Make India Great Again
description: Sorabh Pant understands nothing but wants to change everything. In his 6th standup special: he goes from trolls to drugs to Aadhar to NaMo to RG to China to US gun laws - and changes nothing.

title: SUMMER BLOOMS (English Subtitled)
description: Hatsumi, 27 years old, has a secret. Three years after her boyfriend had died, she receives a letter from him. After encountering her former student, and a young artist, she confesses her past in the night of summer.

title: Muddy (Tamil)
description: Muddy portrays the rivalry between two blood ties named Muthu and Karthy. This combines three unique mud races where a new villain Tony comes in between. Will the three of them be able to defeat each other and who will win the final race is the rest of the story.

title: NTR: Kathanayakudu
description: The journey of Nandamuri Tarakarama Rao from a government Sub-Registrar to becoming a Superstar in Telugu Cinema and his motivation to enter politics.

title: Oddball
description: An eccentric chicken farmer, with the help of his granddaughter, trains his mischievous dog Oddball to protect a penguin sanctuary from fox attacks in an attempt to reunite his family and save their seaside town.

title: Unpaused: Naya Safar
description: Unpaused: Naya Safar continues to takes the legacy of the first anthology forward and yet again brings together 5 unique filmmakers - Nupur Asthana, Ayappa KM, Ruchir Arun, Shikha Makan and Nagraj Manjule - with new stories of hope, love, connections and second chances that celebrate the resilient human spirit in these uncertain times.

title: Bach, Christmas Oratorio - Philippe Herreweghe, Collegium vocale Gent
genre: ['Arts, Entertainment, and Culture', 'Faith and Spirituality', 'Music Videos and Concerts']
description: In 2012, conductor Philippe Herreweghe recorded the famous Christmas Oratorio by Johann Sebastian Bach at the Palais des Beaux-Arts in Brussels with the Collegium Vocale Gent, a musical ensemble he founded in 1970. Composed in 1734, the Christmas Oratorio is a masterpiece of the Baroque period. It comprises six cantatas inspired by the Gospels according to St. Luke and St. Matthew.

title: Deadly Exposé
description: A sleepy beach town's citizens are at risk when a series of murders become linked to the hacking of client information from a discreet dating app. Maxine Payton, a local detective, must examine her own commitment to her boyfriend, Simon, the deeper she becomes involved in the case. Her life depends on solving it, as the killer's message seems to be directed toward her.

title: Mohalla Assi
description: Mohalla Assi is a satire on the commercialisation of the pilgrimage city, and fake gurus that the lure foreign tourists.

title: Peterloo
description: Included with your Prime membership. Internationally acclaimed and Oscar-nominated filmmaker Mike Leigh portrays one of the bloodiest episodes in British history, the infamous Peterloo Massacre of 1819, where government-backed cavalry charged into a peaceful crowd of 60,000 that gathered in Manchester, England to demand democratic reform.

title: Avalanche Sharks
description: Mammoth Mountain's annual "Bikini Ski Day" party for spring break takes a horrifying turn when the ghosts of ancient sharks awaken to defend the mountain against tourists and skiers.

title: Bhikari
description: A beautiful story of a mother and son where one day an accident leaves the mother in a state of coma and to save her life the son has to go through various sacrifises to save his mother.

title: Brotherhood of Blades
description: Three sworn brothers are tasked with annihilating a corrupt fugitive and his followers, but a mistake reveals the brothers are being used as pawns in a deadly game filled with secrets, conspiracies and lethal consequences.

title: Dhoom 2 (English Subtitled)
description: ACP Jai Dixit and his best friend Ali takes on an international thief known only as Mr. A. Will they be able to catch him?

title: Flesh
description: Brothers Alonzo and Casper run their city from different points of the spectrum with Alonzo serving as the Chief of Police and Casper the biggest street king in the city. When their youngest brother Nick returns home he's immediately drawn into the middle of the brother's feud and an even bigger threat as the seductive Eve threatens Casper's empire with her growing human trafficking business

title: HITOSHI MATSUMOTO Presents Documental
description: Hitoshi Matsumoto presents a comedic survival show. Ten comedians shoulder the participation expenses and put their pride as performers on the line for a chance to win a ten-million-yen prize. The winner will be the individual who doesn't laugh until the end. Don't miss out on the laughter of comedians driven into a corner! (C)2016 YD Creation

title: Hotel Transylvania 4: Transformania
description: When Van Helsing’s mysterious invention goes haywire, Drac and his pals are transformed into humans and Johnny becomes a monster! In their new mismatched bodies, Drac and Johnny must team up to find a cure. With help from Mavis and the Drac Pack, the heat is on to find a way to switch themselves back before their transformations become permanent.

title: Interview with a Hitman
description: Silent. Relentless. No attachments. This is Viktor's code. The mantra that took him from the slums of Romania to the pinnacle of his profession - as a killer. Viktor knows the value of life more than most, which makes him the perfect killer. But after a ruthless betrayal by his bosses, he escapes to London, joins a new "family" and finds himself caught in a vicious underworld power struggle.

title: Jab Tak Hai Jaan
description: Samar Anand (Shah Rukh Khan), a poor musician on the streets of London, becomes a bomb-disposal expert for the Indian Army after Meera(Katrina Kaif), the woman of his dreams, leaves him. While in the army, he meets a Discovery channel journalist, Akira (Anushka Sharma), who brings him back to London after 10 years. Is fate playful enough to reunite Samar with his long-lost love?

title: Jack Frost
description: The Groundhog tells the story of how, for once, Jack Frost became human, and helped a knight win his lady love.

title: Kill Zone 2
description: In this frenetic follow-up to modern martial arts epic, Kill Zone, action icons Tony Jaa and Wu Jing team up with Hong Kong megastars Simon Yam and Louis Koo for a breakneck story of dirty cops, prison riots, and black market organ transplants, all brought together by a non-stop series of inventive, bone-crunching set pieces.

title: Lies We Tell, but the Secrets We Keep
description: Roni and Bri have fallen in a forbidden love, where lies and secrets lead to the end of their relationship. Bri tries desperately to move on and forget her past love with Roni. But, she's in for an unexpected surprise when secrets are revealed and her life is now a twisted love triangle with her past.

title: Loves' Last Resort
description: A few months after dumping her boyfriend, Eric, Chloe takes a vacation – only to find him at the same resort, getting married! Convinced he’s making a huge mistake, Chloe recruits the resort manager, Hunter, to make Eric jealous. But when she starts to fall for Hunter, Chloe will have to put her history with Eric aside if she wants to give new love a chance to blossom.

title: Midnight Chronicles
description: In the world of Midnight, after three ages of war defeating the free races, the dark god Izrador now rules the world of Aryth with an iron fist.

title: Muddy (Kannada)
description: Muddy portrays the rivalry between two blood ties named Muthu and Karthy. This combines three unique mud races where a new villain Tony comes in between. Will the three of them be able to defeat each other and who will win the final race is the rest of the story.

title: Muddy (Malayalam)
description: Muddy portrays the rivalry between two blood ties named Muthu and Karthy. This combines three unique mud races where a new villain Tony comes in between. Will the three of them be able to defeat each other and who will win the final race is the rest of the story.

title: Muddy (Telugu)
description: Muddy portrays the rivalry between two blood ties named Muthu and Karthy. This combines three unique mud races where a new villain Tony comes in between. Will the three of them be able to defeat each other and who will win the final race is the rest of the story.

title: Naples '44
description: In 1943, Norman Lewis entered a war-torn Naples. He began writing notes that turned into his masterpiece, a memoir titled NAPLES '44. Francesco Patierno's new documentary imagines Lewis returning many years later to the city that charmed and seduced him.

title: Pinkfong! Christmas with Pinkfong & Hogi
description: Let's celebrate Christmas holiday with Pinkfong, Hogi, and friends! Lots of joyful holiday spirit in the Wonderville with fun presents and surprise to share with friends! Let's slide into the wintery season with Pinkfong, Hogi, and friends!

title: Pushpa: The Rise (Hindi)
description: Pushpa Raj (Allu Arjun) a coolie, volunteers to smuggle red sanders, a rare wood that only grows in Andhra, with the help of novel ideas to smuggle the red sanders. Pushpa quickly becomes leader of red sanders smuggling network. While Pushpa is at his prime, a ruthless police officer Bhanwar Singh Shekhawat (Fahadh Faasil) takes charge as SP and ridicules Pushpa for his lineage.

title: Ranangan
description: The story revolves around Shyamrao Deshmukh (Sachin Pilgaonkar) and his family. Shyamrao is an education tycoon who aims to enter politics. Things take a turn with the entry of Shlok (Swwapil Joshi) who wants to destroy Shyamrao's political dream. But why does he intent to do so? What past does the story hold? How does Shyamrao protect his family and his political dream from Shlok?

title: Shaolin
description: After ambushing and killing his rival, losing everything in the process, dispirited warlord Hou Jie turns to a Shaolin monastery seeking salvation.

title: Shockwave: Countdown to Disaster
description: When massive volcanic storms begin to spew from the Earth, geophysicist Kate Ferris tries to convince the Department of Defense that this is no natural phenomenon. They’re the result of a seismic super weapon and the shockwaves it sends out will destroy major cities across the globe, killing millions.

title: SUSO: LOVE WITH HUMOR
description: Cupid's arrow was shot by Suso the Paspi.The renowned Colombian comedian will show us how tempting situations such as gossip, envy and ego among many other things, could also be a reason to love. As a teacher of his original school of love, Suso assures that laughter will be the protagonists, showing that love must be seasoned... but with a lot of humor.

title: Tayo Color Songs
description: Let's play with the fun colors with Tayo and friends! Come on and learn together as you sing along to the Tayo Color Songs!

title: Thin Ice
description: A dishonest insurance salesman's life quickly disintegrates during a Wisconsin winter when he teams up with a psychopath to steal a rare violin at the home of a reclusive farmer.

title: Who is Harry Nilsson (And Why is Everybody Talkin' About Him)?
description: In this definitive documentary on the Grammy award winning music legend Harry Nilsson, friends, family and colleagues delve into the acclaimed singer-songwriter's music, creative process and personal demons.

title: Happy Cleaners
description: Happy Cleaners is a heartfelt story that celebrates the survival of immigrants, the experiences of the Korean American community, and the value of family.

title: Lady of the Manor (4K UHD)
description: The ghost of a Southern belle tries to teach a slacker to be a lady in this hilarious buddy comedy starring Melanie Lynskey, Judy Greer, Justin Long, and Ryan Phillippe.

title: The Legend of Vox Machina
description: They're rowdy, they're ragtag, they're misfits turned mercenaries for hire. Vox Machina is more interested in easy money and cheap ale than actually protecting the realm. But when the kingdom is threatened by evil, this boisterous crew realizes that they are the only ones capable of restoring justice. What began as a simple payday is now the origin story behind Exandria’s newest heroes.

title: A Sort of Homecoming
description: Amy is pulled back to Louisiana unexpectedly, where upon her return, she�۪s thrust down memory lane to her high school days on the debate team with her competing partner Nick, and discovers that the past still has much to teach her.

title: Bad Blood
description: Lauren's life is on a positive trajectory, until she is falsely accused of murder. Discovering that an obsessive serial killer with her exact DNA match has been knowingly implicating her in all his crimes, she is forced to fight to prove her innocence and save her life.

title: Begum Jaan
description: Begum Jaan is a story of 11 fearless women standing up against the system, amidst the changing political scenario during the partition.

title: Bharaate
description: When Jagan meets Radha, it is love at first sight for him. But finding his happily-ever-after is harder than it seems.

title: Chronology
description: Hakan and Nihal seem to have a perfect marriage. The problems of the young architect couple are started to emerge when Nihal suddenly disappears.

title: Entanglement
description: A lady with Dissociative Identity Disorder wants husbands inheritance before the side chick gets it.

title: Hawks Ridge
description: A black, grieving ex-pastor saves the life of the white man that killed his wife.

title: Noorie
description: The story of Noorie revolves around a village girl, Noorie, who falls in love with Yusuf. Their marriage is fixed. However, Bashir Khan secretly eyes Noorie. He and his crony Faulad Khan send Yusuf away for some work and try to physically assault Noorie, but she commits suicide. The incident is witnessed by her dog, Khairoo, who hunts the culprit down. Yusuf is heartbroken over the loss of Noorie.

title: SquadGoals
description: High school reporter Samantha Hodges investigates a series of deaths that her school is trying to cover-up as, one-by-one, scholarship finalists are ending up dead. Too bad she and her closest friends are next on the list.

title: Twinsanity
description: Following the death of their mother, an identical twin pulls away to establish her own independence, while the other unravels and plots to end her sister’s new beginning. Inspired by true events.

title: Avane Srimannarayana
description: In pursuit of solving a long-held mystery of Amaravati, Narayana - the quirky new cop in the town - has to get past a dreaded clan of dacoits and its fierce leader Jairam. Directed by Sachin Ravi, Avane Srimannarayana stars Rakshit Shetty in the lead role.

title: Back of the Net
description: After hopping on a bus to Harold Soccer Academy instead of Harold Academy Australian Semester at Sea, science fanatic, Cory Bailey (Sofia Wylie) has no choice but to complete a semester at the soccer academy.

title: Brother's Day (Tamil)
description: Joy runs a hotel and catering service in Fort Kochi along with Rony and Munna. One fine day Rony meets an unexpected guest called Chandy and they become very close, however Chandy does not disclose his true identity to them. A lot of unexpected events take place when Shiva comes into their lives. What happens between all these characters builds the rest of the story.

title: Deadly Inferno
description: While employees are working in a building under renovations, a janitor accidentally sets off a lethal and explosive chain reaction leaves several people injured and trapped throughout the building. It will be up to firefighter Ray Vargas to find a way to bring everyone to safety, but his rescue is complicated as the structural integrity declines.

title: Dhoom 3 (English Subtitled)
description: To avenge his father's death, Sahir, with all his acrobatic skills and wizardry, becomes a thief to take down a corrupt bank in Chicago. ACP Jay Dixit and his sidekick Ali are called upon to catch this elusive thief.

title: Girls Like Us
description: Keisha is intimately involved in two relationships, one with a man and the other is a secret affair with a woman. Keisha has been hiding her relations for months and the pressure from her relationships is leaving her torn. Feeling the pressure, Keisha must choose between the love of her life or to fit within the status quo.

title: Hindi Medium
description: Hindi Medium is a situational comedy based on social issues. It's a family-oriented story of a couple who is determined that their three year-old daughter should study in an English medium school and they leave no stone unturned to achieve this goal.

title: Jack Squad
description: Looking for some quick cash three women band together and decide to drug and jack every rich man they can find. Their plan quickly turns profitable, but the girls soon learn that even the best cons eventually unravel. Will they be able to find a way out before it is too late?

title: Jallikattu (4K UHD)
description: Set in a remote village in the hill ranges of Kerala, Jallikattu unfolds during the course of a day and night. The events are set off when a butcher’s buffalo breaks free and runs amok.

title: Kabul Express
description: Indian journalists Suhel Khan and Jai Kapoor go to Afghanistan to report about the US invasion in 2001, where they cross paths with Khyber and American journalist, Jessica Beckham. Held hostage by a Taliban official (Imran Khan) who wants to flee to Pakistan, the group of 5 set aside their differences and connect as humans. Will they succeed in accomplishing their goals before anyone interferes?

title: Lethal Seduction
description: Mark is preparing for college when he meets Carissa, a beautiful older woman who pulls him into her luxurious world. His mother, Tanya, has noticed changes in him. In confronting Carissa with concerns, Tanya is met with threats. Carissa's claws are in deep, and she refuses to let go.

title: Mayabazar 2016
description: An honest cop, a conman and a hopeless romantic form an unusual team during the days of demonetisation to pull off a scam. A scam that is bigger than demonetisation, but things go haywire.

title: Music & Murder
description: Not every rags to riches story arrives via a clean cut straight and narrow path. Sometimes long after the rags have been replaced with Versace, the stench from the counterfeit mindset lingers longer than a starlet would like.

title: Silsila
description: Amit (Amitabh Bachchan) and Shekar are brothers, both blissful in their respective relationships. However, Shekar dies in a plane crash and Amit takes pity on Shoba (Jaya Bachchan), Shekar's pregnant fiancee and decides to marry her, leaving Chandni (Rekha), his fiancee, heartbroken. Years later, when he meets Chandni, his feelings for her resurface. Will Chandni let the same flame burn her twice?

title: Ta Ra Rum Pum
description: Rajveer Singh is the most successful race car driver in his field. Soon, he marries Shona and they live as a happy family, with their two children. One day, their world turns upside down as Rajveer meets with an accident and cannot compete further. Rajveer and his family is forced to move into a small locality. The film focuses on the ups and downs that Rajveer and his family face thereafter.

title: Terror Birds
description: When Maddy's father goes missing on a birdwatching excursion, she and her friends trek into the wilderness to find him and encounter a pair of 10-foot, hungry Terror Birds believed to be extinct for centuries.

title: The Ghazi Attack (Hindi)
description: Inspired by true events, The Ghazi Attack is India's first underwater war film. The story revolves around the events that unfolded right before the Indo-Pakistan war of 1971, when the Pakistani Submarine Ghazi (Asia's most powerful fast-attack submarine at the time) attempted to destroy the Indian aircraft carrier Vikrant.

title: The Last Days of Malcolm X
description: Re-enactment of events leading to the death of the civil rights legend.

title: The Turkish Way
description: Shaped in a travelogue, Turkish Way tells the journey and experiences of the three Roca brothers in their trip across Turkey.

title: Torn
description: Delroy discovers his wife is having an affair with their son's basketball coach. In walks Jasmine, a sexy woman with everything he desires. What will he decide now that he finds himself torn between pursuing a relationship with Jasmine or mending his marriage?

title: Wine and War
description: Woven into Lebanon's ancient history is a rich tale of wine-making, resilience, and entrepreneurial spirit. Unravelling the story of the world's fist wine merchants, Wine and War is a complex testament to the Lebanese people's courage in the face of adversity, and a deep dive into the history of a nation which has bred masters of crisis management.

title: 15-Minute Sweat & Tone 4.0 Workout
description: No equipment needed. Tip: Complete Series 1.0, 2.0 and 3.0 for 4 weeks each prior to Series 4.0. A workout designed to increase muscle tone by challenging your body with combination exercises that amp up results. Find the Weekly Workout Schedule for this Series, and more, on my website (FitnessMaggie).

title: Raju Gari Gadhi 2
description: After experiencing a series of supernatural events and nightmares, three friends discover, to their horror, that their beachside resort is haunted. Their only hope is the renowned mentalist Rudra, who is famous for his strange yet effective methods. Before it is too late, Rudra must track down the hostile spirit haunting the resort and solve the mystery surrounding her.

title: Saheb
description: Malhar takes up a fight for his fellow students which brings him in direct conflict with the management. As malhar's agitation becomes stronger, he is threatened for his life by the Chief Minister, in return, Malhar challenges to dethrone him from power in 30 days. The story takes many twists and turns and keeps the audience guessing all the time.

title: 9/11 - The Myth and The Reality
description: Gathering stories from the press, reports from other countries, researchers, and the contradictory words of US government officials, this program presents a case that leaves very little doubt that the attacks of 9/11 need to be further investigated.
An emotional story of a two old school sweethearts, ram and janu meets after 20 years sharing their heartwarming unconditional hidden love.

title: Airaa (Tamil)
description: Yamuna is on holiday at her grandma's village bungalow when she strikes upon the genius idea of shooting and uploading real-ghost videos. While shooting, Yamuna chances upon real ghost experiences, incident that test her belief system and rational thinking.

title: Bharaate (4K UHD)
description: When Jagan meets Radha, it is love at first sight for him. But finding his happily-ever-after is harder than it seems.

title: Big Brother
description: Big Brother, set in the city of Bengaluru, is the story of Sachidanandan, who, at the age of 16 and 18, commits a couple of murders, albeit unwittingly, earning himself a double life sentence. After 24 long years, Sachidanandan is finally set free, but despite his family’s unflinching support, he struggles to cope with the ways of the world.

title: Consumed
description: When Sophie's son, Garrett, develops a mysterious illness, she embarks on a search for answers. This leads her into the controversial world of Genetically Modified Organisms (GMOs) where a sociopolitical battle rages between organic farmers and big biotech corporations.

title: Dia
description: Dia tells the story of a young, introvert girl whose routine life brightens up when she falls for Rohith, one of her fellow college mates. Being an introvert girl and trying to express her love becomes the biggest challenge of her life.

title: Eloise At Christmastime
description: It is Christmas at The Plaza and Eloise is up to her usual mischief. This adventure sees her "helping" in respect of the marriage of the hotel owner's marriage. What could go wrong with Eloise involved!

title: Expatriot
description: CIA analyst Riley Quinn lost everything when she blew the whistle on the US government. Hunted into exile, she escaped to Colombia. Two years later, Riley is living a loner lifestyle when suddenly CIA Agent Bill Donovan shows up with an offer. Her name will be cleared if she helps an international task force confiscate millions.

title: Faasle
description: When a young man falls in love, little does he anticipate about the struggles ahead. Chandni and Vijay are in love and wish to get married. However, Vijay goes into the bad books of Chandni's dad, Vikram. On finding out about their relationship, a furious Vikram disapproves their union and decides to get her married elsewhere. Will Vikram give his daughter and her love a second thought?

title: Fallen Queen
description: Unemployed musician Trevor (Brent Bailey)’s mundane life with his wife Renee (Emma Hamilton) and his daughter Clio (Violet Hicks) takes a sudden turn when ex-beauty queen Kaylie (Roxanna Dunlop) moves in next door.

title: Go Straight Take Left
description: Watch the mind blasting comedy duo Sumukhi Suresh and Naveen Richard slip in and out of 12 outrageous characters, in 6 absurd sketches, all in 1 dangerously funny hour of live sketch comedy! One second Naveen is playing tennis and the in next, Sumukhi is playing a mosquito. Heart patients and close minded individuals are not allowed on this ride.

title: Into Dangerous Territory
description: Pampered city girl Mia ventures into the mountains with hopes of deepening her whirlwind romance with wilderness guide Reid, but a series of animal attacks, and his jealous ex-girlfriend, are keeping Reid from properly wooing Mia. What neither Reid nor Mia know is that the grizzly bears aren't the most dangerous threats lurking in the forest.

title: Janamaithri
description: Janamaithri is a comedy film that revolves around the local police's innovative attempt to lower the rate of whee hours road accidents by serving the sleep-prone  drivers with hot coffee/tea (oru chaayakkoru Jeevan padhathi). Things get out of control when the antagonist enters and hence starts the fun ride which has its own twists and turns.

title: Jump In
description: Troy Alexander returns to her roots, to pass the bar and start her own practice. Although, her love of the law takes a back seat to her young son, Jordan. It provides an escape from realities. She's content and love is a distraction, until her friends stumble upon Malik Bond, a teacher. Sparks fly and life seems perfect... Then circumstances bring her plans to a halt.

title: Kaatrin Mozhi
description: An ambitious housewife (Jyothika) becomes a radio jockey for a late-night relationship advice show.

title: Last Hours in Suburbia (Fall From Grace)
description: Suburban mom Rachel feels lucky to have a close relationship with her teenaged daughter. Dina tells her everything... or so Rachel thinks. When Dina suddenly commits suicide, Rachel is devastated. Her search for answers leads her to some painful discoveries about the bullying that was tearing Dina apart.

title: Milan Talkies
description: Milan Talkies is set in a small town of Uttar Pradesh in the year span of 2010- 2013 where single screen theatres were still prominent and loved. It portrays a love story between an aspiring film director, Annu, and a young girl, Maithali, who belongs to a strict Panda (priest) family. Due to social prejudice they are unable to communicate easily, hence films become a means to unite them.

title: Naveen Richard: Relatively Relatable
description: Fridges, birthday parties and cockroach baba cults. In his latest special, Naveen Richard brings together some tasty observational comedy that has proven to be relatable 9 out of 12 times.

title: Pinkfong! Coloring with Hogi
description: Let's color our Wonderstar friends! Coloring with Hogi is a special series where kids can follow along and color with their favorite characters! What color would you choose?

title: Ra's Metanoia
description: Award winning "Ra's Metanoia" is a periodic drama film with fictional elements to chronicle the story based on true events of Mohandas Karamchand Gandhi's life

title: Sankashta Kara Ganapathi
description: Ganapathi, a cartoonist, is diagnosed with a neurological disorder called Alien Hand Syndrome, which poses a hindrance in his daily life. Despite the disorder, Ganapathi attempts to achieve his goal and also goes on to woo the girl he loves.

title: Sullu
description: Sullu a survival thriller Revolves around Jithu the protagonist and his relationship with his parents. Jithu a 9 year old boy is very mischievous and couldn't tolerate his moms pamperings and his father's anger issues. One day while playing hide n seek games with his cousins he accidentally get stuck in wardobe which change the life of him and the people around him.

title: The Woodsman
description: What happened to Mauro in the forest during that three day period has remained a mystery until the recent discovery of footage that was likely stolen from a government office in Belize. This is the terrifying story of a man searching for a dream, only to find a living, breathing nightmare. This is the story of Mr. Bosque's ill-fated, final adventure.

title: Varun Thakur: Vicky This Side, Varun That Side
description: Stand up comic Varun Thakur and his alter ego Vicky Malhotra go up against each other in this one of a kind stand up special.

title: Yu-Gi-Oh! Zexal
description: It's time to feel the flow as Yu-Gi-Oh! Zexal blasts off into awesome new adventures! Seven legendary number cards are hidden throughout the cosmos, each holding a key to unlocking the ultimate power of the universe. Yuma and Astral must find them before the evil Barians do for whoever wields this force can use it to save the galaxy or destroy it!

title: Pushpa: The Rise (Kannada)
description: Pushpa Raj (Allu Arjun) a coolie, volunteers to smuggle red sanders, a rare wood that only grows in Andhra, with the help of novel ideas to smuggle the red sanders. Pushpa quickly becomes leader of red sanders smuggling network. While Pushpa is at his prime, a ruthless police officer Bhanwar Singh Shekhawat (Fahadh Faasil) takes charge as SP and ridicules Pushpa for his lineage.

title: Pushpa: The Rise (Malayalam)
description: Pushpa Raj (Allu Arjun) a coolie, volunteers to smuggle red sanders, a rare wood that only grows in Andhra, with the help of novel ideas to smuggle the red sanders. Pushpa quickly becomes leader of red sanders smuggling network. While Pushpa is at his prime, a ruthless police officer Bhanwar Singh Shekhawat (Fahadh Faasil) takes charge as SP and ridicules Pushpa for his lineage.

title: Pushpa: The Rise (Tamil)
description: Pushpa Raj (Allu Arjun) a coolie, volunteers to smuggle red sanders, a rare wood that only grows in Andhra, with the help of novel ideas to smuggle the red sanders. Pushpa quickly becomes leader of red sanders smuggling network. While Pushpa is at his prime, a ruthless police officer Bhanwar Singh Shekhawat (Fahadh Faasil) takes charge as SP and ridicules Pushpa for his lineage.

title: Pushpa: The Rise (Telugu)
description: Pushpa Raj (Allu Arjun) a coolie, volunteers to smuggle red sanders, a rare wood that only grows in Andhra, with the help of novel ideas to smuggle the red sanders. Pushpa quickly becomes leader of red sanders smuggling network. While Pushpa is at his prime, a ruthless police officer Bhanwar Singh Shekhawat (Fahadh Faasil) takes charge as SP and ridicules Pushpa for his lineage.

title: The Elephants and the Rats
description: The Elephants and the Rats story for kids.Moral: Never under-estimate people by their appearance.

title: Gantumoote
description: A relatable, realistic tale of a sixteen-year-old girl and her subtle journey from the life that she thinks exists just like in the movies to the actual life that unravels to her. A story of struggles in understanding herself, the changing world, educational pressures, bullying, competition over marks - all of it wrapped up in transcending journey of first love.

title: Harpoon
description: Rivalries, dark secrets, and sexual tension emerge when three best friends find themselves stranded on a yacht in the middle of the ocean desperate for survival. With plenty of alcohol and very little food and water, emotions run high and their delusions become a reality. As the days stretch on and death seems inevitable, their terrifying truths float to the surface.

title: I don’t love you either
description: Nina and Dylan, best friends since childhood, have no secrets for one another. When Nina leaves her boyfriend and decides to go to Biarritz for a vacation with her two best friends, she finally has a click. While Dylan has just started a relationship, Nina realizes that he is the man of his life! Full of twists and turns, their love story is going to be much more complicated than expected...

title: The Magic Stick ( In Hindi )
description: The Magic Stick

title: The Tender Bar
description: ​​From director George Clooney and based on the best-selling memoir, The Tender Bar follows an aspiring writer (Tye Sheridan) pursuing his romantic and professional dreams. From a stool in his uncle’s (Ben Affleck) bar, he learns what it means to grow up from a colorful group of local characters.

title: Velle
description: Three criminals, a runaway girl, her three best friends, an aspiring director and a star cross paths due to an incident. Will they come off better for it or worse? Velle is about the journey of people like you and me, who inevitably find themselves amidst the chaos of life, only to realise that in the end, it all comes together - it all makes sense.

title: Jay Nog: Something From Nothing
description: Something From Nothing takes you on a stand-up comedy tour during the pandemic from a comedians perspective, filmed in the parking lot of a diner in Queens, NY. The film shares the story of Jay Nog and his family during the pandemic as well as the comedians and employees who performed and worked at the diner.

title: What Lies West
description: When a new college graduate takes a job babysitting a sheltered teen, the two must overcome a wide personality gap to take on a summer hiking adventure that could change both of their lives.

title: DCX MMXVI Live
description: Experience Dixie Chicks’ DCX MMXVI live from their first US tour in 10 years.

title: Girls of the Sun
description: A French journalist, Mathilde, comes to cover the attack in Kurdistan and bears witness to the story of these exceptional “Girls of the Sun” warriors.

title: Mujhse Fraaandship Karoge
description: Mujhse Fraandship Karoge is a treat to watch with young actors Saqib Saleem (Vishal), Saba Azad (Preity), Nishanth Dahiya (Rahul) and Tara D'Souza (Malvika) on board. They are a bunch of university students who initially are too prejudiced towards each other, especially Vishal and Preity but a friend request changes it all. Sometimes being fake is all that's needed in changing hatred to love.

title: No Internet
description: A group of teens must go an entire year without the internet. After their small town announces that they're shutting down all internet services for a year, this group of friends searches for a way to turn it back on. They discover a clandestine organization pulling the strings, and it's up to them to save their town.

title: Taylor Swift: America's Sweetheart
description: Taylor Swift is a true phenomenon. Through her own words and great archive footage this film takes an incredible look at the life and times of this truly amazing young artist.

title: Ana
description: Rafa, discovers nine-year-old Ana sleeping in the back of one of his car. In an attempt to both locate Ana's father and somehow settle Rafa's increasingly pressing debts, Rafa and Ana embark on an dangerous expedition together.

title: Anirban Dasgupta’s: Take It Easy
description: Nothing in life is black and white, except Take It Easy, Anirban Dasgupta's stand-up special. His material deals with hate and love in the hostile internet era, and why both these intense emotions need to be told to take it easy. In this set he comprehends events from the past year at home and at work; events he would rather forget unless he wrote jokes on them.

title: Damien
description: While making a documentary on their friend, the crew uncover a dark secret which leads to friction, betrayal and puts their lives in danger. Can you ever truly know a ginger? The recipient of multiple awards and lots of critical acclaim, this indie horror film was shot in Northern Ireland.

title: Distancing Socially
description: Composed of a series of comical vignettes that share a telecommunications application as a common thread, Distancing Socially focuses on loosely connected human interactions - from food delivery to family drama - taking place virtually across a world in lockdown.

title: I Am An Addict
description: In this terrifying horror anthology, an anachronistic public access TV channel hosts a self-help guru with one goal: to shock viewers out of their addictions and bizarre obsessions, with frightening consequences.

title: Mazinkaiser SKL
description: A mechanized robotic weapon has been sent into the barren wasteland of Kikaijima, a colossal floating island hanging above Japan. Deadly forces there, once thought dormant, have reawakened and pose a grave threat to Earth.

title: Monster Seafood Wars
description: Gigantic mutated sea monsters arise from the depths and begin to wreak havoc upon an awe-stricken Tokyo. As a last ditch effort, the government forms the "Seafood Monster Attack Team (S.M.A.T.)" and an all-new plan of attack is immediately put into action. But just as the tide appears to be turning, a colossal crab monster appears, plunging the world into culinary chaos.

title: Orange
description: Ganesh a rich dude and a happy- go- lucky lad bumps into Khushi a bubbly girl full of energy and falls in love. He gathers the courage to talk to her but loses her in the crowd. Will Ganesh be able to find Khushi again? Will he be able to profess his love to her?

title: Rustum
description: The story revolves around a super cop who is sincere, brave and deadly. He is on a mission to end nexus of the organ trading mafia across the country and to take revenge for the brutal murder of his close friend.

title: The Dark Web Tapes
description: A group of friends play online game with terrifying results.

title: Zillafoot
description: A UFO lands on Earth, unleashing a giant monster that is half lizard, half gorilla - Zillafoot! The monster rampages, decimating any military response and even awakening a strange dinosaur. Now it's up to scientists and the final member of the famed Ultrasquad to face the new threats and save humanity in this epic kaiju homage to the Toho monsters and Tsuburaya heroes!

title: Badmaash Company
description: BADMAASH COMPANY is a story set in the 1990s, of four ordinary middle class Bombay youngsters - Karan (Shahid Kapoor), Bulbul (Anushka Sharma), Zing (Meiyang) and Chandu (Vir Das) - who came together to start an import business. With their larger than life schemes, the four go on a wild roller-coaster ride into the world of sheer glitz and glamour where the stakes are high and risks even higher!

title: Barbie: Dreamtopia Festival of Fun
description: Festival of Fun is an all new animated special starring Barbie and her little sister Chelsea. With their friends, Chelsea and Barbie take us on a fantastical journey, embarking on amazing adventures and exploring new lands full of limitless possibility.

title: Burial Ground Massacre
description: College kids party at Liberty Manor, unaware that a terrifying sociopath, Damon, covets a sacred artifact inside.

title: DON JEDIONDO:DIE LAUGHING
description: Nobody is as funny as Don Jediondo. This unique peasant doesn't mince words to tell the funniest adventures, always with a lot of spice and double meaning. Don Jediondo will reveal his recognized sexual potency' secrets, what convents hide and how dangerous prostate exam can be for men.

title: Don't Touch If  You Ain't Prayed
description: After saving herself for marriage, a forty year old Christian woman finally meets her soul mate. But her hopes sour once she finds out this candidate carries extra baggage; a drunk wife and shady dealings with criminal elements. With no other takers on the horizon, she begins to doubt her faith. But good things come to those who wait and a new reformed man returns to her life.

title: Frontline: Trump's Showdown
description: Trump's fight against the investigation of his campaign and whether he obstructed justice. With the threat of impeachment growing, Trump wages an unprecedented war against the Special Counsel, the FBI, and even his own Attorney General.

title: Lea & Pop (Part 1)
description: The entire concept of Lea and Pop is based on music. The strongest kind of magic for kids. Singing and dancing while learning is at the heart of the concept. The songs teach about good habits, emotions, words, numbers, notes, colors, always in a fun and entertaining way. It's the perfect mix to live, laugh and love in the magical musical world of Lea and Pop.

title: Madhagaja
description: This is a story of a long standby feud and rivalry.

title: Mark & Russell's Wild Ride
description: Mark is excited when the most popular girl in his class asks HIM to drive her to a party. Then Mark remembers one detail - he doesn't have his driver's license! Glenn Bufferton, known for easy testing, is just the DMV instructor to give Mark his street cred.

title: No Love Lost
description: After finalizing their divorce Noah and Moriah find themselves going from lovers to roommates. Moriah has moved on already and began dating her co-worker Anthony, 6 months before the divorce was final. Noah is still in love with her but find himself falling for a waitress named Rochelle.

title: Perfume LIVE 2021 [polygon wave]
description: Day 2 of "Perfume LIVE 2021 [polygon wave]" from Aug 14 and 15, 2021 at PIA Arena MM in Kanagawa, Japan.Using the entire arena area as stage, with big LED on the floor and the back, this performance with special collaboration (ELEVENPLAY) is a must see.

title: Restoring the Shack
description: Join author Paul Young on an adventure into the world of the best-selling phenomenon. This inside look at how Paul's own life journey shaped his writing explores questions of faith, grief, wonder, and relationship with the Father, Son, and Holy Spirit.

title: The Crime Of Padre Amaro
description: Politics and sexual passions threaten to corrupt a young, newly-ordained priest in a small Mexican town.

title: The Hungover Games
description: After celebrating Doug's upcoming wedding in a in Laughlin, NV, hungover guys Bradley, Ed and Zach wake up in a futuristic dystopia, having lost their pal, Doug. With the help of Effing and Justmitch, the trio's loyal advisers, the gang must now prepare to battle their way through the districts of The Hungover Games including The Real Housewives of District 8 and Teddy from The Puppet District.

title: The Put Chutney Show
description: Chennai's very own comedy brand 'Put Chutney' is now back with a brand new live stand-up show. The funny minds behind the 2015 viral YouTube sensations. What if Batman was from Chennai? Rajiv Rajaram, Aswin Rao and Balakumaran are going back to their stand-up roots to deliver a unique experience with their quirky tongue in the cheek humour.

title: Whistle
description: Rayappan a local don lives in Chennai city slum. He does lot of social welfare for the people in his area. Rayappan’s son Michael, a Football player along with his friends Kiran and Donald participates in National Football Championship and has already reached semifinal, Michael falls in love with Angel Aasirvatham, a Physiotherapist student.

title: Zoo
description: Based on a true story, 12 year old Tom (Art Parkinson) and his misfit friends fight to save Buster the baby elephant during the air raids on Belfast in 1941.

title: 200 Pounds Beauty
description: After a drastic "head-to-toe" plastic surgery, Han-na, an overweight back-up singer, goes from shy duckling to full-on pop diva in this acclaimed Korean comedy. When Han-na finally gets the spotlight she always wanted, she realizes that fame wasn't what she thought it would be.

title: Amazon Presents Paul Weller LIVE, at The Great Escape
description: Live from Brighton, UK, Amazon Front Row presents Paul Weller at Great Escape. The award-winning and Multi-Platinum singer-songwriter performs songs from his new album Saturn's Patter, as well as classics songs.

title: America's Next Top Model
description: America's Next Top Model, hosted by Tyra Banks, will be featuring seven men and seven women, from regions all across the country, living together under one roof and battling it out to earn the prestigious title of America's Next Top Model. This is the third "Guys and Girls" edition of America's Next Top Model.

title: American Soldiers
description: A group of U.S. soldiers defy their country when they release mistreated prisoners.

title: Apocalypto
description: As the Mayan kingdom faces its decline, a young man is taken on a perilous journey to a world ruled by fear and oppression.

title: Azaad Desh Ke Ghulam
description: Bharti, a law student from a rich family, lives a comfortable life. However, her life changes when she learns from a classmate that her father makes his fortune from illegal and immoral activities.

title: Bheemante Vazhi
description: Bheeman realizes the inconvenience caused by the age old pathway when he had to take his mother to the hospital for an emergency. Everything takes an interesting turn as he decides to broaden the pathway.

title: Billions In Change
description: The world is facing some huge problems. There’s a lot of talk about how to solve them. But talk doesn’t reduce pollution, or grow food, or heal the sick. That takes doing. This film is the story about a group of doers, the elegantly simple inventions they have made to change the lives of billions of people, and the unconventional billionaire spearheading the project.

title: Blackbird
description: Lily (Susan Sarandon) summons her daughters Jennifer (Kate Winslet) and Anna (Mia Wasikowska) for one final family reunion as she looks to end her battle with a terminal illness. Amid the bittersweet farewell, unresolved feelings surface.

title: Complete Strangers
description: A recovering alcoholic returns to his hometown after a hiatus, and falls in love with a man who will turn his world upside down.

title: Deerhunter
description: Deerhunter set McCarren Park Pool ablaze to the tune of their sweaty, psychedelic, noise rock.

title: Dil Bole Hadippa
description: 'No girls' rule stops Veera, a young girl with an exceptional talent in cricket, from entering the selection process for the Indian cricket team participating in the 'Aman Cup'. She disguises herself as a man -'Veer'and gets selected in the team for her talent. Rohan, the coach of the team, falls in love with Veera while she was NOT dressed as a man. Will Rohan accept Veera when her cover's blown?

title: Lady of the Manor
description: The ghost of a Southern belle tries to teach a slacker to be a lady in this hilarious buddy comedy starring Melanie Lynskey, Judy Greer, Justin Long, and Ryan Phillippe.

title: Lamhe
description: A romantic drama of a young man Viren, who falls in love with an older woman, Pallavi. When Pallavi marries her love Siddharth, Viren heartbroken, leaves the country. However, a tragic accident kills Pallavi and her husband, orphaning their baby girl, Pooja. Years later, Pooja grows up to be a splitting image of her mother. Destiny has her meet a now older Viren, only to fall in love with him.

title: LCD Soundsystem Holiday Special
description: LCD Soundsystem performs an electric set live from Brooklyn, NY. Written and directed by Eric Wareheim, the holiday special also features Macaulay Culkin, Christine Ko, Jon Daly, and a puppet as the band in ‘All My Friends’, a 90s-style sitcom set in the suburbs.

title: Lift Me Up
description: Living with her new stepdad after her mom dies suddenly, Emma turns to dance as her comfort from grief. But as her challenges mount, Emma must decide what her next move will be. TV-PG

title: Mere Brother Ki Dulhan
description: Kush is trusted with the task of finding his brother, Luv, a suitable bride. After several unsuccessful encounters he meets Dimple, a fun-loving and eccentric woman. Finding her perfect, and after the families agree to the wedding, Luv and Dimple are engaged. But Kush realizes that he has fallen in love with Dimple. Tables turn when he finds out that she feels the same way about him.

title: Mogra Phulaalaa
description: Mogra Phulaalaa chronicles the story of a man who has dedicated all his life attending to the well-being of his family, and forgot to take care of his personal life along the way. The events that unfold after he meets the women of his dreams forms the crux of the film.

title: My Online Nightmare
description: Remarkable tales of extraordinary scammers and fraudsters from the UK and America who use the internet to lure in their victims with terrifying, and sometimes deadly, results. Each story is a glimpse into how the internet has been transforming our relationships, our desires and our darkest fantasies.

title: Natyam
description: An ancient dance village called Natyam is challenged by gradual disappearance of the true spirit of dance. Sitara (Sandhya Raju), a classical dancer tries to resurrect the art by staging a forbidden play that haunts even her master (Adithya Menon). She finds herself stuck in between an old folklore about a goddess and the dark past of the village.

title: Next Level
description: With original songs and teaching of life lessons, a group of talented teens compete for the coveted title of “Miss Next,” showcasing their best dance moves and singing voices. Starring Lauren Orlando, Emily Skinner, Hayden Summerall, Chloe East, Brooke Butler, Ellarose Kaylor and Chloe Lukasiak.

title: Not Afraid, Not Afraid
description: After being abandoned by her husband after 28 years, an overbearing, self-centered psychologist embarks on a quest to revisit her past loves, accompanied by her 6-year-old grandson, who has Down syndrome, after he turns up unexpectedly in her van.

title: Punch
description: Eighteen year old Ariel is in love with her caring father, who lives with her in the upper middle class part of Vancouver. When he starts dating again, she becomes violently jealous, fails to seduce him, and turns to female boxing.

title: Putham Pudhu Kaalai Vidiyaadhaa…
description: Putham Pudhu Kaalai Vidiyaadhaa... takes the legacy of the first anthology forward and once again brings together 5 original and inspirational voices of contemporary Tamil cinema - Halitha Shameem, Balaji Mohan, Richard Anthony, Surya Krishna and Madhumita - with new stories of hope and love that celebrate the resilient human spirit in these uncertain times

title: Rab Ne Bana Di Jodi
description: Taani (Anushka Sharma), a flamboyant girl, is circumstances force her to marry Surinder (Shahrukh Khan), a quiet and down-to-earth man. Surinder disguises himself as Raj, a fun and outgoing man and is the exact opposite of his true self. Taani is drawn to Raj and they enter a dance competition together. But on the day of the final, she is shocked to see Surinder turn up and not Raj.

title: Ripper 2: Letter From Within
description: Sequel to the hugely successful Ripper:Letter from Hell.

title: Salaam Namaste
description: Nick and Ambar fall in love but later decide to just be friends due to the clash of opinions. Both are independent and decide to live in together as friends. The platonic relationship between them is short lived as Ambar is now pregnant. Thus, starts the chaotic story of Nick who is not ready to take the responsibility of a family. Will Ambar keep the baby and save her friendship with Nick.

title: Slaughterhouse Of The Rising Sun
description: Plagued by terrifying visions on the set of her latest film, Jennifer is forced to drop out of the spotlight and check in to a mental institution. After being stranded in the desert following her release, Jennifer seeks shelter with a nomadic band of rebels.

title: Slopestyle TV
description: Slopestyle TV is the skiing and snowboarding mountain destination travel series featuring some of the world's finest alpine riders and resorts. Every episode travel to a new mountain destination and push the limits of powder and terrain park riding while exploring the region's history, local culture and exciting night life.

title: Special A (English Subtitled)
description: Hikari Hanazono has always been second to Kei Takishima. When they were six years old, their pro-wrestling loving fathers introduced them to each other.

title: Survivor
description: Short Description Not Available

title: Taken Heart
description: Kate Johnson is a single mother and a successful undercover detective. When her daughter, Nina, goes to Punta Dia in Belize, she is kidnapped by the cartel organization “La Muerte Roja”. Kate takes it upon herself to travel to Belize to find her missing daughter.

title: The Bear
description: Set in 19th-century British Columbia, The Bear follows the story of a young cub and an adult grizzly as they join forces to survive the perils inherent in their mountain habitat. With each passing obstacle, the two bears further develop a friendship that can only make them stronger - but will it be enough for them to overcome their most deadly enemy?

title: The Christmas Dragon
description: Father Christmas is a fading memory, after Christmas hasn't come for several years. A young orphan girl receives a magic crystal from a dying elf, with a warning that the North has lost its magic, and that she alone can save Christmas.

title: The Trip
description: Gautham (Gautham Raj) is a young man who is addicted to drugs to a point of no coming back. When his mother (Aamani) discovers his condition, she tries to get him out of it but in vain. Meanwhile Gautham is off to the jungles of Orissa to try something that would give him the best high in the world but something scary awaits him in the same forest.

title: Thrissur Pooram
description: Thrissur Pooram' is an action packed entertainer starring Jayasurya in lead role. Jayasurya is Pullu Giri, a Thrissur based ex-gangster, who is leading a normal life now with his family and friends. How he, his family and friends are dragged into a duel with present day and new age villains of Thrissur forms the plot of the film.

title: TIME IS UP
description: An accident will force Vivien and Roy to come to a stop and reclaim their lives, one minute at a time, and finally start living in a present that perhaps will prove to be more exciting than any predefined.

title: Vaibhav Sethia: Don’t
description: It was a bright sunny morning and Vaibhav hated it. So he slept again. He loves potential energy and hates kinetic energy. Laying in bed he scribbled what he calls ‘bookmark moments’ of life. Today he calls them jokes. See him perform them on Amazon Prime Video, in his solo show named - Don’t.

title: Welcome To Paradise
description: Preacher Debbie Laramie uproots her home in Dallas when she's transferred to a small church in the sleepy town of Paradise, Texas. Debbie and her son brave a bumpy reception from a community in need of a guide back to God. Her unique approach creates a divide until a catastrophic chain of events leaves them without a building at all. A reminder of how love and acceptance show our faith.

title: Celebrity Hunted: Germany
description: Is it possible to disappear without a trace in 2021? 10 celebrities face the impossible task: submerging for 10 days. Chased by professional investigators with only little money to live on. Dr. Wladimir Klitschko, Axel Stein, Tom Beck, Stefanie Giesinger, Vanessa Mai, Andreas Ferber, Kida Khodr Ramadan, Summer Cem, Diana Bill & Melisa Kocak are on their run through Germany. Who remains undetected?

title: Lost Outlaw
description: A Chinese gold mining camp is over-run by a group of outlaws. One of the outlaws has to question his morals after meeting the woman of his dreams.

title: Secrets in the Water
description: A grieving mother enlists the help of her deceased daughter’s friend to track down her killer and wonders if the killer is someone close to home.

title: The Nomads
description: Amidst the chaos of massive budget cuts and school closures, a young female teacher introduces men's rugby to an inner-city North Philadelphia high school.

title: Where The Land Meets The Sky
description: After eight months of separation, Eric Rodgers must deal with the sudden death of his wife and the emotional process of reconnecting with his young daughter, Rachel.

title: 15-Minute Cardio Shape-Up 4.0 Workout
description: No equipment needed. Tip: Complete Series 1.0, 2.0 and 3.0 for 4 weeks each prior to Series 4.0. Burn mega calories, work muscles to exhaustion and lose fat with this quick, challenging cardio & core-driven workout. Find the Weekly Workout Schedule for this Series, and more, on my website (FitnessMaggie).

title: A Woman Deceived
description: It’s been one year since Elizabeth’s husband, Bill, died in a tragic horseback riding accident and she is starting to move on. When she runs into Travis Brown, the cowboy she met the same weekend Bill died, the two immediately hit it off. Travis is just what Elizabeth needed to come into her life and they soon get married.

title: Aaina
description: Sisters, Roma and Reema fall in love with the same man, Ravi. But when he falls in love with an arrogant and confident Roma, Reema is left heart-broken. The marriage is fixed, but on their wedding day, Roma leaves him to accept an offer for a movie. An angry Ravi marries Reema instead. After a rocky start, they soon fall in love until Roma returns and demands to be accepted as Ravi's wife.

title: Aurangzeb
description: The action thriller film of two twins Ajay and Vishal, separated by a set of adamant parents-Yashwardhan Singh and Veera. By a twist of fate, the twins find their lives entwined with that of the cops. The dishonest bunch of policemen plans to kill Yashwardhan, his estranged wife, their twins and take over their empire. So they plant one of the twins as an infiltrator.

title: Christmas Crush
description: A woman makes a Christmas wish for her neighbor to fall in love with her but must enlist the help of her crush when her Christmas wish applies to the wrong neighbor.

title: Commando 2: The Black Money Trail
description: India's most wanted Black Money agent Vicky Chaddha gets arrested in Malaysia and is kept in a safe house by the authorities along with his wife. A team of four is being sent to Malaysia to bring them to India. Apart from the growth of inter-personal relationships, the mission comprising major action sequences, has quite a few twists and turns on it's way.

title: Cowboys vs. Dinosaurs
description: After an accidental explosion at a local mine, dinosaurs emerge from the rubble to terrorize a small western town. Now, a band of gunslingers must defend their home in an all-out battle of cowboys versus dinosaurs.

title: Cradles for Cash
description: After her newborn baby is stolen from the hospital, a woman must go to great lengths to get her child back.

title: Dilwale Dulhania Le Jayenge (English Subtitled)
description: A young man and woman - both of Indian descent but born and raised in Britain - fall in love during a trip to Switzerland. However, the girl's traditional father takes her back to India to fulfill a betrothal promise.

title: Dum Laga Ke Haisha (English Subtitled)
description: Dum Laga Ke Haisha is a 2015 Indian Hindi romantic comedy film directed by Sharat Katariya dealing with an arranged marriage between a slim guy (Ayushmann Khurana) and an over-weight girl (Bhumi Pednekar)

title: Family Feud with John O'Hurley
description: John O'Hurley hosts this updated edition where two families compete to guess the answers to various surveys. The winning family gets a chance to win $20,000 in the "Fast Money"bonus round.

title: Fatal Flip
description: Starring AsStarring Dominique Swain, Mike Faiola, Michael Steger, and Tatyana Ali. Jeff and Alex are eager to flip houses, but when they partner with Nate, a handsome contractor with a dark past, they get more than they bargained for.

title: Freeway
description: In this twisted take on 'Little Red Riding Hood,' a teenage juvenile delinquent (Reese Witherspoon) on the run from a social worker, travels to her grandmother's house while being hounded by a charming, but sadistic, serial killer (Kiefer Sutherland).

title: Gone Missing
description: When her daughter disappears on a family vacation and the police seem at a loss, a mother must trust her instincts to rescue her... before it's too late.

title: Gonjiam: Haunted Asylum
description: The crew of a horror web show plan to stream live from inside an asylum. To attract more viewers, the show's host arranges fake scares, but as they move deeper into the building, they find much more than expected.

title: Hit (The First Case)
description: Vikram is a 30-year-old cop. While he is battling with his own traumatic past, the stakes get high when a girl called Preethi mysteriously disappears in Hyderabad and Vikram has to solve the case at any cost.

title: Hum Tum
description: Karan (Saif Ali Khan) and Rhea (Rani Mukherjee) can't get along even if their lives depended on it. So when they meet for the 1st time, they are determined to make it their last. But 3 years later, when they meet at her wedding he starts to realise that she may not be half as bad. Too late Karan! 4 years pass and fate brings the two together yet again, but a lot has changed since they last met.

title: Imaikkaa Nodigal
description: A suave CBI officer (Nayanthara), is in search of a serial killer who kidnaps and kills the children of important people. The killer, however, is targeting his nemesis next.

title: Initial D Legend 1: Awakening (English Subtitled)
description: Koichiro of the Akina Speedstars witnesses a mysterious driver outmaneuver rival Keisuke of the Akagi RedSuns. The race, he later discovers, was won by none other than his own co-worker, Takumi. What happens next is the stuff of street racing legend!

title: Jawaani Jaaneman
description: A care free middle aged single man, who is high on life and spends most of his time at parties with beautiful women suddenly finds himself the father of a young girl who is also pregnant. Will he rise up to the occasion or continue to live his free-spirited life in denial? Jawaani Jaaneman is a coming of age film and a comic take on how a man confronts the harsh reality of his life.

title: Junooniyat
description: Captain Jahan Bakshi rescues a Punjabi girl, Suhani. This starts a friendship that evolves into a passionate love affair.

title: Katheyondu Shuruvagide
description: A young resort owner, Tarun, is going through a rough time and tries to deal with disappointments, failures, and struggles of his life. In the process of doing so, he strikes up a great bond with a resort guest, Tanya. Will this bond help them to find a new meaning of love and life?

title: Kavaludaari
description: The accidental discovery of human bones during a road-widening project leads a local traffic cop into the mystery of a 40-year-old case. His investigation leads him across trails that will put his wit, resolve and morals to the test.

title: Lafangey Parindey
description: Pinky, a talented skater has the dream of becoming the winner of the tv show, 'Hunar Hi Winner.' After an unfortunate accident, she loses her eyesight. Her life takes a turn when Nandan, an underground boxer decides to pay for her medical treatments. But everything changes when Pinky finds out that Nandan is responsible for her accident. Can she ever forgive him?

title: Los Angeles
description: "Los Angeles" is the story of Jojo, a young mute who hears God calling her to save the Baby Jesus, so she packs five angels in a shoe shine kit and hits the road with an escaped felon and accidental sidekick named Cash.

title: MAD
description: Maddy(Madhav Chilukuri) is a playboy by nature. On the other hand, Madhuri(Spandana) is a girl who believes in true love. What happens when people with such different ideologies get married. What problems do they face?

title: Maraikkayar Arabikkadalin Singam
description: The movie is a biopic on the real-life character, Kunjali Marakkar who is till date considered one of the greatest naval chiefs of India. An epic tale, set in the late 15th century and early16th century, the film is  based on the fearless seafarer of the Malabar Coast, Kunjali Marakkar.

title: Marakkar Arabikkadalinte Simham
description: The movie is a biopic on the real-life character, Kunjali Marakkar who is till date considered one of the greatest naval chiefs of India. An epic tale, set in the late 15th century and early16th century, the film is  based on the fearless seafarer of the Malabar Coast, Kunjali Marakkar.

title: Mexico's Bravest Man
description: This doc chronicles the life of Julian Leyzaola Perez, a former police chief who made it his life's duty to take down powerful drug cartels in Tijuana and Juarez, Mexico. Perez survived eight assassination attempts, the eighth of which opens this doc. However, Perez's tactics drew controversy and dark allegations in a world of violence.

title: Mouse and Mole at Christmas Time
description: Join Mouse and Mole at their Twelfth Night party! After the two have an argument, Mole spends the night outside in his armchair. He dreams that his new snow-mole comes to life and transports him to a land where his wishes are granted!

title: New York
description: The tale of three friends, whose lives completely change after the terrorist attacks in the US on 9/11. The investigation that follows the 9/11 incident impacts the trio harshly. They are tortured and forced, to be in the police detention for allegedly causing the massacre and are labelled as terrorists. Amidst all odds, will these friends fight and come out victorious?

title: No Tears for the Dead
description: Abandoned by his mother shortly after immigrating to America, Gon is raised by the mafia and grows up to become a cold-blooded hitman. While on a job, Gon makes the mistake of killing an innocent young girl. Guilt takes over his life and things become worse when his boss orders him to kill the young girl's mother, whom he falls in love with. Korean Language film with English subtitles.

title: Not Alone
description: An unsuspecting family buys a mansion for a bargain but discovers a presence in the home and must fight to save their lives.

title: Phillip Kopczynski: Live at Spokane Comedy Club
description: In "Phillip Kopczynski: Live at Spokane Comedy Club" he talks about the transition from small town kid to medium city family man.

title: Prassthanam
description: The film revolves around a politician Baldev Pratap Singh (Sanjay Dutt) and his family. When it comes to choosing his heir, Baldev chooses his stepson because he's a thinking man, eventually angering his own son and in the process triggering violence.

title: Republic of Doyle
description: Jake Doyle and his father Malachy run a private investigations agency in St. John's, Newfoundland. Their cases involve them in all sorts of dealings - not all of them on the right side of the law.

title: Rocket Singh Salesman of the Year
description: Harpreet's (Ranbir Kapoor) graduation grades are too low for him to land a job similar to his friends. Forced to choose between a rock and a hard place, he adopts a career in sales. However, he never gives up on his true passion of becoming a successful businessman. And one day, the disillusioned salesman starts a business based on a model which has several heads turned.

title: Rodgers and Hammerstein's Flower Drum Song
description: In this adaptation of the 1958 Rodgers and Hammerstein Broadway musical, Chinese immigrant Mei Li is betrothed to nightclub boss Sammy Fong, but he wants to marry showgirl Linda Low. To get out of the arrangement, Sammy pawns her off to wealthy Master Wang as a fiancée for his son, Wang Ta. Mei Li falls in love with Wang, but he wants to pursue Linda, who uses his affections to test Sammy's love.

title: Sawaal
description: Sawaal is the story of a powerful choice between love and morale. Seth Dhanpat Rai is the country's mafia kingpin . His daughter Sonia falls in love with Ravi Malhotra, a police inspector. Dhanpat Rai must decide on whether to choose his daughter's happiness over an issue of power and status. Sawaal is the victory of self-righteousness over all materialistic desires.

title: Shuddh Desi Romance
description: When commitment phobic Raghu, runs away from his wedding to be with the independent and open-minded Gayatri, they decide to live in together. But when Gayatri walks out on him, he finds love again in Tara, who is ironically the girl he was earlier arranged to get married to. So when he meets Gayatri again years later, mixed feelings emerge and we have a story of a man who is confused.

title: SpongeBob As Told By
description: The cast of SpongeBob is asked to tell the story of iconic episodes as best as they can. SpongeBob cast members recount episodes and clips from the original show, and IRL Puppet reenactments embrace all of the nautical nonsense SpongeBob has to offer!

title: The Assent
description: A widower reluctantly seeks the help of a disgraced priest to save his son, whom he believes is possessed by the Devil. Starring Robert Kazinsky (Pacific Rim, Warcraft, "True Blood") and Peter Jason (Escape from LA, Mortal Kombat, Jurassic World).

title: The Bay
description: The multiple Daytime Emmy Award-winning digital drama series The Bay returns for it's fifth season. In a town cursed by the spirit of a dead Senator, the privileged and often times dysfunctional Bay City residents fight for redemption, true love and new beginnings in a town where murder, betrayal, heartbreak, and vengeance must be in the water.

title: Thoda Pyaar Thoda Magic
description: Ranbeer Talwar is a wealthy but lonely businessman who ends up taking care of four children of the couple he accidentally killed in a car crash. The children despise him and seek revenge for their parent's death. They just don't get along and pray to God for help. God decides to send them his most charming angel, Geeta. Will she be able to help them lead a happy life?

title: Tubelight
